            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>Release Date: November 5, 2008 [EBook #27166]</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>Language: Chinese</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">*** START OF THIS PROJECT GUTENBERG EBOOK NA HAN ***</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Produced by Han Huei Haung</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">《魯迅︰吶喊》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\"> 《吶喊》自序</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    《吶喊》自序</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我在年青時候也曾經做過許多夢，後來大半忘卻了，但自己也並不以為可惜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    所謂回憶者，雖說可以使人歡欣，有時也不免使人寂寞，使精神的絲縷還牽著己逝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的寂寞的時光，又有什麼意味呢，而我偏苦于不能全忘卻，這不能全忘的一部分，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    到現在便成了《吶喊》的來由。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我有四年多，曾經常常，——幾乎是每天，出入于質鋪和藥店里，年紀可是忘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻了，總之是藥店的櫃台正和我一樣高，質鋪的是比我高一倍，我從一倍高的櫃台</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    外送上衣服或首飾去，在侮蔑里接了錢，再到一樣高的櫃台上給我久病的父親去買</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    藥。回家之後，又須忙別的事了，因為開方的醫生是最有名的，以此所用的藥引也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    奇特︰冬天的蘆根，經霜三年的甘蔗，蟋蟀要原對的，結子的平地木，……多不是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    容易辦到的東西。然而我的父親終于日重一日的亡故了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    有誰從小康人家而墜入困頓的麼，我以為在這途路中，大概可以看見世人的真</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    面目；我要到N進K學堂去了ヾ，仿佛是想走異路，逃異地，去尋求別樣的人們。我</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的母親沒有法，辦了八元的川資，說是由我的自便；然而伊哭了，這正是情理中的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    事，因為那時讀書應試是正路，所謂學洋務，社會上便以為是一種走投無路的人，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    只得將靈魂賣給鬼子，要加倍的奚落而且排斥的，而況伊又看不見自己的兒子了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    然而我也顧不得這些事，終于到N去進了K學堂了，在這學堂里，我才知道世上還有</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    所謂格致，算學，地理，歷史，繪圖和體操。生理學並不教，但我們卻看到些木版</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的《全體新論》和《化學衛生論》之類了。我還記得先前的醫生的議論和方藥，和</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    現在所知道的比較起來，便漸漸的悟得中醫不過是一種有意的或無意的騙子，同</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    時又很起了對于被騙的病人和他的家族的同情；而且從譯出的歷史上，又知道了日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    本維新是大半發端于西方醫學的事實。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    因為這些幼稚的知識，後來便使我的學籍列在日本一個鄉間的醫學專門學校里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了。我的夢很美滿，預備卒業回來，救治象我父親似的被誤的病人的疾苦，戰爭時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    候便去當軍醫，一面又促進了國人對于維新的信仰。我已不知道教授微生物學的方</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    法，現在又有了怎樣的進步了，總之那時是用了電影，來顯示微生物的形狀的，因</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    此有時講義的一段落已完，而時間還沒有到，教師便映些風景或時事的畫片給學生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    看，以用去這多余的光陰。其時正當日俄戰爭的時候，關于戰事的畫片自然也就比</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    較的多了，我在這一個講堂中，便須常常隨喜我那同學們的拍手和喝采。有一回，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我竟在畫片上忽然會見我久違的許多中國人了，一個綁在中間，許多站在左右，一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    樣是強壯的體格，而顯出麻木的神情。據解說，則綁著的是替俄國做了軍事上的偵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    探，正要被日軍砍下頭顱來示眾，而圍著的便是來賞鑒這示眾的盛舉的人們。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    這一學年沒有完畢，我已經到了東京了，因為從那一回以後，我便覺得醫學並</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    非一件緊要事，凡是愚弱的國民，即使體格如何健全，如何茁壯，也只能做毫無意</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    義的示眾的材料和看客，病死多少是不必以為不幸的。所以我們的第一要著，是在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    改變他們的精神，而善于改變精神的是，我那時以為當然要推文藝，于是想提倡文</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    藝運動了。在東京的留學生很有學法政理化以至警察工業的，但沒有人治文學和美</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    術；可是在冷淡的空氣中，也幸而尋到幾個同志了，此外又邀集了必須的幾個人，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    商量之後，第一步當然是出雜志，名目是取“新的生命”的意思，因為我們那時大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    抵帶些復古的傾向，所以只謂之《新生》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    《新生》的出版之期接近了，但最先就隱去了若干擔當文字的人，接著又逃走</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了資本，結果只剩下不名一錢的三個人。創始時候既己背時，失敗時候當然無可告</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    語，而其後卻連這三個人也都為各自的運命所驅策，不能在一處縱談將來的好夢了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這就是我們的並未產生的《新生》的結局。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我感到未嘗經驗的無聊，是自此以後的事。我當初是不知其所以然的；後來想，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    凡有一人的主張，得了贊和，是促其前進的，得了反對，是促其奮斗的，獨有叫喊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    于生人中，而生人並無反應，既非贊同，也無反對，如置身毫無邊際的荒原，無可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    措手的了，這是怎樣的悲哀呵，我于是以我所感到者為寂寞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    這寂寞又一天一天的長大起來，如大毒蛇，纏住了我的靈魂了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    然而我雖然自有無端的悲哀，卻也並不憤懣，因為這經驗使我反省，看見自己</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了︰就是我決不是一個振臂一呼應者雲集的英雄。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    只是我自己的寂寞是不可不驅除的，因為這于我太痛苦。我于是用了種種法，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來麻醉自己的靈魂，使我沉入于國民中，使我回到古代去，後來也親歷或旁觀過幾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    樣更寂寞更悲哀的事，都為我所不願追懷，甘心使他們和我的腦一同消滅在泥土里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的，但我的麻醉法卻也似乎已經奏了功，再沒有青年時候的慷慨激昂的意思了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">    S會館里有三間屋，相傳是往昔曾在院子里的槐樹上縊死過一個女人的，現在</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    槐樹已經高不可攀了，而這屋還沒有人住；許多年，我便寓在這屋里鈔古碑。客</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    中少有人來，古碑中也遇不到什麼問題和主義，而我的生命卻居然暗暗的消去了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這也就是我惟一的願望。夏夜，蚊子多了，便搖著蒲扇坐在槐樹下，從密葉縫里看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那一點一點的青天，晚出的槐蠶又每每冰冷的落在頭頸上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    那時偶或來談的是一個老朋友金心異ぁ，將手提的大皮夾放在破桌上，脫下長</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    衫，對面坐下了，因為怕狗，似乎心房還在怦怦的跳動。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “你鈔了這些有什麼用？”有一夜，他翻著我那古碑的鈔本，發了研究的質問</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “沒有什麼用。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “那麼，你鈔他是什麼意思呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “沒有什麼意思。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我想，你可以做點文章……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我懂得他的意思了，他們正辦《新青年》，然而那時仿佛不特沒有人來贊同，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    並且也還沒有人來反對，我想，他們許是感到寂寞了，但是說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “假如一間鐵屋子，是絕無窗戶而萬難破毀的，里面有許多熟睡的人們，不久</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都要悶死了，然而是從昏睡入死滅，並不感到就死的悲哀。現在你大嚷起來，驚起</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了較為清醒的幾個人，使這不幸的少數者來受無可挽救的臨終的苦楚，你倒以為對</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    得起他們麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “然而幾個人既然起來，你不能說決沒有毀壞這鐵屋的希望。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    是的，我雖然自有我的確信，然而說到希望，卻是不能抹殺的，因為希望是在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    于將來，決不能以我之必無的證明，來折服了他之所謂可有，于是我終于答應他也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    做文章了，這便是最初的一篇《狂人日記》。從此以後，便一發而不可收，每寫些</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    小說模樣的文章，以敷衍朋友們的囑托，積久了就有了十余篇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    在我自己，本以為現在是已經並非一個切迫而不能已于言的人了，但或者也還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    未能忘懷于當日自己的寂寞的悲哀罷，所以有時候仍不免吶喊幾聲，聊以慰藉那在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    寂寞里奔馳的猛士，使他不憚于前驅。至于我的喊聲是勇猛或是悲哀，是可憎或是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    可笑，那倒是不暇顧及的；但既然是吶喊，則當然須听將令的了，所以我往往不恤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    用了曲筆，在《藥》的瑜兒的墳上平空添上一個花環，在《明天》里也不敘單四嫂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    子竟沒有做到看見兒子的夢，因為那時的主將是不主張消極的。至于自己，卻也並</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不願將自以為苦的寂寞，再來傳染給也如我那年青時候似的正做著好夢的青年。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    這樣說來，我的小說和藝術的距離之遠，也就可想而知了，然而到今日還能蒙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    著小說的名，甚而至于且有成集的機會，無論如何總不能不說是一件僥幸的事，但</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    僥幸雖使我不安于心，而懸揣人間暫時還有讀者，則究竟也仍然是高興的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    所以我竟將我的短篇小說結集起來，而且付印了，又因為上面所說的緣由，便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    稱之為《吶喊》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    一九二二年十二月三日，魯迅記于北京。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    注釋︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    ヾN指南京，K學堂指江南水師學堂。作者于1898年到南京江南水師學堂肄業，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第二年改入江南陸師學堂附設的礦務鐵路學堂，1902年畢業後即由清政府派赴日本</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    留學，1904年進仙台的醫學專門學校，1906年中止學醫，回東京準備從事文藝運動。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    參看《朝花夕拾》中《瑣記》及《藤野先生》二文。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ゝ作者對中醫的看法，可參看《朝花夕拾》中《父親的病》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    ゞS會館指紹興縣館，在北京宣武門外。從1912年5月到1919年11月，作者住在</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這會館里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    々魯迅寓居紹興縣館時，常于公余﹝當時他在教育部工作﹞薈集和研究中國古</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    代的造像及墓志等金石拓本，後來輯成《六朝造像目錄》和《六朝墓志目錄》兩種</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ﹝後者未完成﹞。在寓居縣館期間，他還曾經從事中國文學古籍的纂輯和校勘工作，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    成書的有謝承《後漢書》、《嵇康集》等。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぁ金心異指錢玄同，當時《新青年》的編輯委員之一。《新青年》提倡文化革</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    命後不久，林紓曾寫過一篇筆記體小說《荊生》，痛罵文化革命的提倡者，其中有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一個人物叫“金心異”，即影射錢玄同。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">一件小事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我從鄉下跑到京城里，一轉眼已經六年了。其間耳聞目睹的所謂國家大事，算</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    起來也很不少；但在我心里，都不留什麼痕跡，倘要我尋出這些事的影響來說，便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    只是增長了我的壞脾氣，——老實說，便是教我一天比一天的看不起人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    但有一件小事，卻于我有意義，將我從壞脾氣里拖開，使我至今忘記不得。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    這是民國六年的冬天，大北風刮得正猛，我因為生計關系，不得不一早在路上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    走。一路幾乎遇不見人，好容易才雇定了一輛人力車，教他拉到S門去。不一會，北</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    風小了，路上浮塵早已刮淨，剩下一條潔白的大道來，車夫也跑得更快。剛近S門，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    忽而車把上帶著一個人，慢慢地倒了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    跌倒的是一個女人，花白頭發，衣服都很破爛。伊從馬路上突然向車前橫截過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來；車夫已經讓開道，但伊的破棉背心沒有上扣，微風吹著，向外展開，所以終于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    兜著車把。幸而車夫早有點停步，否則伊定要栽一個大斤斗，跌到頭破血出了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    伊伏在地上；車夫便也立住腳。我料定這老女人並沒有傷，又沒有別人看見，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便很怪他多事，要自己惹出是非，也誤了我的路。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我便對他說，“沒有什麼的。走你的罷！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    車夫毫不理會，——或者並沒有听到，——卻放下車子，扶那老女人慢慢起來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    攙著臂膊立定，問伊說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你怎麼啦？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我摔壞了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我想，我眼見你慢慢倒地，怎麼會摔壞呢，裝腔作勢罷了，這真可憎惡。車夫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    多事，也正是自討苦吃，現在你自己想法去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    車夫听了這老女人的話，卻毫不躊躇，仍然攙著伊的臂膊，便一步一步的向前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    走。我有些詫異，忙看前面，是一所巡警分駐所，大風之後，外面也不見人。這車</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    夫扶著那老女人，便正是向那大門走去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我這時突然感到一種異樣的感覺，覺得他滿身灰塵的後影，剎時高大了，而且</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    愈走愈大，須仰視才見。而且他對于我，漸漸的又幾乎變成一種威壓，甚而至于要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    榨出皮袍下面藏著的“小”來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我的活力這時大約有些凝滯了，坐著沒有動，也沒有想，直到看見分駐所里走</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    出一個巡警，才下了車。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    巡警走近我說，“你自己雇車罷，他不能拉你了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我沒有思索的從外套袋里抓出一大把銅元，交給巡警，說，“請你給他……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    風全住了，路上還很靜。我走著，一面想，幾乎怕敢想到自己。以前的事姑且</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    擱起，這一大把銅元又是什麼意思？獎他麼？我還能裁判車夫麼？我不能回答自己。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這事到了現在，還是時時記起。我因此也時時煞了苦痛，努力的要想到我自己。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    幾年來的文治武力，在我早如幼小時候所讀過的“子曰詩雲”え一般，背不上半句</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了。獨有這一件小事，卻總是浮在我眼前，有時反更分明，教我慚愧，催我自新，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    並且增長我的勇氣和希望。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    一九二○年七月。ぉ</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九一九年十二月一日北京《晨報•周年紀念增刊》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え“子曰詩雲”︰“子曰”即“夫子說”；“詩雲”即“《詩經》上說”。泛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    指儒家古籍。這里指舊時學塾的初級讀物。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ據報刊發表的年月及《魯迅日記》，本篇寫作時間當在一九一九年十一月。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">狂人日記</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    某君昆仲，今隱其名，皆余昔日在中學時良友；分隔多年，消息漸闕。日前偶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    聞其一大病；適歸故鄉，迂道往訪，則僅晤一人，言病者其弟也。勞君遠道來視，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然已早愈，赴某地候補え矣。因大笑，出示日記二冊，謂可見當日病狀，不妨獻諸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    舊友。持歸閱一過，知所患蓋“迫害狂”之類。語頗錯雜無倫次，又多荒唐之言；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    亦不著月日，惟墨色字體不一，知非一時所書。間亦有略具聯絡者，今撮錄一篇，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    以供醫家研究。記中語誤，一字不易；惟人名雖皆村人，不為世間所知，無關大體，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然亦悉易去。至于書名，則本人愈後所題，不復改也。七年四月二日識。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    今天晚上，很好的月光。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我不見他，已是三十多年；今天見了，精神分外爽快。才知道以前的三十多年，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    全是發昏；然而須十分小心。不然，那趙家的狗，何以看我兩眼呢？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我怕得有理。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    今天全沒月光，我知道不妙。早上小心出門，趙貴翁的眼色便怪︰似乎怕我，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    似乎想害我。還有七八個人，交頭接耳的議論我，張著嘴，對我笑了一笑；我便從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    頭直冷到腳根，曉得他們布置，都已妥當了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我可不怕，仍舊走我的路。前面一伙小孩子，也在那里議論我；眼色也同趙貴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    翁一樣，臉色也鐵青。我想我同小孩子有什麼仇，他也這樣。忍不住大聲說，“你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    告訴我！”他們可就跑了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我想︰我同趙貴翁有什麼仇，同路上的人又有什麼仇；只有廿年以前，把古久</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    先生的陳年流水簿子ぉ，踹了一腳，古久先生很不高興。趙貴翁雖然不認識他，一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    定也听到風聲，代抱不平；約定路上的人，同我作冤對。但是小孩子呢？那時候，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們還沒有出世，何以今天也睜著怪眼楮，似乎怕我，似乎想害我。這真教我怕，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    教我納罕而且傷心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我明白了。這是他們娘老子教的！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    晚上總是睡不著。凡事須得研究，才會明白。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們——也有給知縣打枷過的，也有給紳士掌過嘴的，也有衙役佔了他妻子的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也有老子娘被債主逼死的；他們那時候的臉色，全沒有昨天這麼怕，也沒有這麼凶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    最奇怪的是昨天街上的那個女人，打他兒子，嘴里說道，“老子呀！我要咬你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    幾口才出氣！”他眼楮卻看著我。我出了一驚，遮掩不住；那青面獠牙的一伙人，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便都哄笑起來。陳老五趕上前，硬把我拖回家中了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    拖我回家，家里的人都裝作不認識我；他們的臉色，也全同別人一樣。進了書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    房，便反扣上門，宛然是關了一只雞鴨。這一件事，越教我猜不出底細。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    前幾天，狼子村的佃戶來告荒，對我大哥說，他們村里的一個大惡人，給大家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    打死了；幾個人便挖出他的心肝來，用油煎炒了吃，可以壯壯膽子。我插了一句嘴，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    佃戶和大哥便都看我幾眼。今天才曉得他們的眼光，全同外面的那伙人一模一樣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    想起來，我從頂上直冷到腳跟。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們會吃人，就未必不會吃我。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    你看那女人“咬你幾口”的話，和一伙青面獠牙人的笑，和前天佃戶的話，明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    明是暗號。我看出他話中全是毒，笑中全是刀。他們的牙齒，全是白厲厲的排著，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這就是吃人的家伙。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    照我自己想，雖然不是惡人，自從踹了古家的簿子，可就難說了。他們似乎別</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有心思，我全猜不出。況且他們一翻臉，便說人是惡人。我還記得大哥教我做論，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    無論怎樣好人，翻他幾句，他便打上幾個圈；原諒壞人幾句，他便說“翻天妙手，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    與眾不同”。我那里猜得到他們的心思，究竟怎樣；況且是要吃的時候。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    凡事總須研究，才會明白。古來時常吃人，我也還記得，可是不甚清楚。我翻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    開歷史一查，這歷史沒有年代，歪歪斜斜的每葉上都寫著“仁義道德”幾個字。我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    橫豎睡不著，仔細看了半夜，才從字縫里看出字來，滿本都寫著兩個字是“吃人”！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    書上寫著這許多字，佃戶說了這許多話，卻都笑吟吟的睜著怪眼看我。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我也是人，他們想要吃我了！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    四</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    早上，我靜坐了一會兒。陳老五送進飯來，一碗菜，一碗蒸魚；這魚的眼楮，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    白而且硬，張著嘴，同那一伙想吃人的人一樣。吃了幾筷，滑溜溜的不知是魚是人，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便把他兜肚連腸的吐出。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我說“老五，對大哥說，我悶得慌，想到園里走走。”老五不答應，走了；停</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一會，可就來開了門。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我也不動，研究他們如何擺布我；知道他們一定不肯放松。果然！我大哥引了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一個老頭子，慢慢走來；他滿眼凶光，怕我看出，只是低頭向著地，從眼鏡橫邊暗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    暗看我。大哥說，“今天你仿佛很好。”我說“是的。”大哥說，“今天請何先生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來，給你診一診。”我說“可以！”其實我豈不知道這老頭子是劊子手扮的！無非</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    借了看脈這名目，揣一揣肥瘠︰因這功勞，也分一片肉吃。我也不怕；雖然不吃人，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    膽子卻比他們還壯。伸出兩個拳頭，看他如何下手。老頭子坐著，閉了眼楮，摸了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    好一會，呆了好一會；便張開他鬼眼楮說，“不要亂想。靜靜的養幾天，就好了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不要亂想，靜靜的養！養肥了，他們是自然可以多吃；我有什麼好處，怎麼會</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “好了”？他們這群人，又想吃人，又是鬼鬼祟祟，想法子遮掩，不敢直截下手，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    真要令我笑死。我忍不住，便放聲大笑起來，十分快活。自己曉得這笑聲里面，有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的是義勇和正氣。老頭子和大哥，都失了色，被我這勇氣正氣鎮壓住了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但是我有勇氣，他們便越想吃我，沾光一點這勇氣。老頭子跨出門，走不多遠，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便低聲對大哥說道，“趕緊吃罷！”大哥點點頭。原來也有你！這一件大發見，雖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    似意外，也在意中︰合伙吃我的人，便是我的哥哥！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    吃人的是我哥哥！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我是吃人的人的兄弟！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我自己被人吃了，可仍然是吃人的人的兄弟！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    五</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這幾天是退一步想︰假使那老頭子不是劊子手扮的，真是醫生，也仍然是吃人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的人。他們的祖師李時珍做的“本草什麼”お上，明明寫著人肉可以煎吃；他還能</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    說自己不吃人麼？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    至于我家大哥，也毫不冤枉他。他對我講書的時候，親口說過可以“易子而食”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か；又一回偶然議論起一個不好的人，他便說不但該殺，還當“食肉寢皮”が。我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那時年紀還小，心跳了好半天。前天狼子村佃戶來說吃心肝的事，他也毫不奇怪，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不住的點頭。可見心思是同從前一樣狠。既然可以“易子而食”，便什麼都易得，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    什麼人都吃得。我從前單听他講道理，也胡涂過去；現在曉得他講道理的時候，不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但唇邊還抹著人油，而且心里滿裝著吃人的意思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    六</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    黑漆漆的，不知是日是夜。趙家的狗又叫起來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    獅子似的凶心，兔子的怯弱，狐狸的狡猾，……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    七</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我曉得他們的方法，直捷殺了，是不肯的，而且也不敢，怕有禍祟。所以他們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大家連絡，布滿了羅網，逼我自戕。試看前幾天街上男女的樣子，和這幾天我大哥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的作為，便足可悟出八九分了。最好是解下腰帶，掛在梁上，自己緊緊勒死；他們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    沒有殺人的罪名，又償了心願，自然都歡天喜地的發出一種嗚嗚咽咽的笑聲。否則</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    驚嚇憂愁死了，雖則略瘦，也還可以首肯幾下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們是只會吃死肉的！——記得什麼書上說，有一種東西，叫“海乙那”き的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    眼光和樣子都很難看；時常吃死肉，連極大的骨頭，都細細嚼爛，咽下肚子去，想</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    起來也教人害怕。“海乙那”是狼的親眷，狼是狗的本家。前天趙家的狗，看我幾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    眼，可見他也同謀，早已接洽。老頭子眼看著地，豈能瞞得我過。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    最可憐的是我的大哥，他也是人，何以毫不害怕；而且合伙吃我呢？還是歷來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    慣了，不以為非呢？還是喪了良心，明知故犯呢？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我詛咒吃人的人，先從他起頭；要勸轉吃人的人，也先從他下手。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    八</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    其實這種道理，到了現在，他們也該早已懂得，……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    忽然來了一個人；年紀不過二十左右，相貌是不很看得清楚，滿面笑容，對了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我點頭，他的笑也不像真笑。我便問他，“吃人的事，對麼？”他仍然笑著說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “不是荒年，怎麼會吃人。”我立刻就曉得，他也是一伙，喜歡吃人的；便自勇氣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    百倍，偏要問他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “對麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這等事問他什麼。你真會……說笑話。……今天天氣很好。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    天氣是好，月色也很亮了。可是我要問你，“對麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他不以為然了。含含胡胡的答道，“不……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “不對？他們何以竟吃？！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “沒有的事……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “沒有的事？狼子村現吃；還有書上都寫著，通紅斬新！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他便變了臉，鐵一般青。睜著眼說，“有許有的，這是從來如此……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “從來如此，便對麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我不同你講這些道理；總之你不該說，你說便是你錯！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我直跳起來，張開眼，這人便不見了。全身出了一大片汗。他的年紀，比我大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    哥小得遠，居然也是一伙；這一定是他娘老子先教的。還怕已經教給他兒子了；所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    以連小孩子，也都惡狠狠的看我。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    九</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    自己想吃人，又怕被別人吃了，都用著疑心極深的眼光，面面相覷。……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    去了這心思，放心做事走路吃飯睡覺，何等舒服。這只是一條門檻，一個關頭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們可是父子兄弟夫婦朋友師生仇敵和各不相識的人，都結成一伙，互相勸勉，互</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    相牽掣，死也不肯跨過這一步。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大清早，去尋我大哥；他立在堂門外看天，我便走到他背後，攔住門，格外沉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    靜，格外和氣的對他說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “大哥，我有話告訴你。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你說就是，”他趕緊回過臉來，點點頭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我只有幾句話，可是說不出來。大哥，大約當初野蠻的人，都吃過一點人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    後來因為心思不同，有的不吃人了，一味要好，便變了人，變了真的人。有的卻還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    吃，——也同蟲子一樣，有的變了魚鳥猴子，一直變到人。有的不要好，至今還是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    蟲子。這吃人的人比不吃人的人，何等慚愧。怕比蟲子的慚愧猴子，還差得很遠很</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    遠。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “易牙ぎ蒸了他兒子，給桀紂吃，還是一直從前的事。誰曉得從盤古開闢天地</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    以後，一直吃到易牙的兒子；從易牙的兒子，一直吃到徐錫林く；從徐錫林，又一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    直吃到狼子村捉住的人。去年城里殺了犯人，還有一個生癆病的人，用饅頭蘸血舐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “他們要吃我，你一個人，原也無法可想；然而又何必去入伙。吃人的人，什</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    麼事做不出；他們會吃我，也會吃你，一伙里面，也會自吃。但只要轉一步，只要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    立刻改了，也就是人人太平。雖然從來如此，我們今天也可以格外要好，說是不能！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大哥，我相信你能說，前天佃戶要減租，你說過不能。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    當初，他還只是冷笑，隨後眼光便凶狠起來，一到說破他們的隱情，那就滿臉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都變成青色了。大門外立著一伙人，趙貴翁和他的狗，也在里面，都探頭探腦的挨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    進來。有的是看不出面貌，似乎用布蒙著；有的是仍舊青面獠牙，抿著嘴笑。我認</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    識他們是一伙，都是吃人的人。可是也曉得他們心思很不一樣，一種是以為從來如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    此，應該吃的；一種是知道不該吃，可是仍然要吃，又怕別人說破他，所以听了我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的話，越發氣憤不過，可是抿著嘴冷笑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這時候，大哥也忽然顯出凶相，高聲喝道，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “都出去！瘋子有什麼好看！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這時候，我又懂得一件他們的巧妙了。他們豈但不肯改，而且早已布置；預備</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    下一個瘋子的名目罩上我。將來吃了，不但太平無事，怕還會有人見情。佃戶說的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大家吃了一個惡人，正是這方法。這是他們的老譜！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    陳老五也氣憤憤的直走進來。如何按得住我的口，我偏要對這伙人說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你們可以改了，從真心改起！要曉得將來容不得吃人的人，活在世上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你們要不改，自己也會吃盡。即使生得多，也會給真的人除滅了，同獵人打</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    完狼子一樣！——同蟲子一樣！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那一伙人，都被陳老五趕走了。大哥也不知那里去了。陳老五勸我回屋子里去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    屋里面全是黑沉沉的。橫梁和椽子都在頭上發抖；抖了一會，就大起來，堆在我身</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    萬分沉重，動彈不得；他的意思是要我死。我曉得他的沉重是假的，便掙扎出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來，出了一身汗。可是偏要說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你們立刻改了，從真心改起！你們要曉得將來是容不得吃人的人，……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    十一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    太陽也不出，門也不開，日日是兩頓飯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我捏起筷子，便想起我大哥；曉得妹子死掉的緣故，也全在他。那時我妹子才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    五歲，可愛可憐的樣子，還在眼前。母親哭個不住，他卻勸母親不要哭；大約因為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    自己吃了，哭起來不免有點過意不去。如果還能過意不去，……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    妹子是被大哥吃了，母親知道沒有，我可不得而知。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    母親想也知道；不過哭的時候，卻並沒有說明，大約也以為應當的了。記得我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    四五歲時，坐在堂前乘涼，大哥說爺娘生病，做兒子的須割下一片肉來，煮熟了請</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他吃，ぐ才算好人；母親也沒有說不行。一片吃得，整個的自然也吃得。但是那天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的哭法，現在想起來，實在還教人傷心，這真是奇極的事！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    十二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不能想了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    四千年來時時吃人的地方，今天才明白，我也在其中混了多年；大哥正管著家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    務，妹子恰恰死了，他未必不和在飯菜里，暗暗給我們吃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我未必無意之中，不吃了我妹子的幾片肉，現在也輪到我自己，……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有了四千年吃人履歷的我，當初雖然不知道，現在明白，難見真的人！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    十三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    沒有吃過人的孩子，或者還有？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    救救孩子……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一九一八年四月。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九一八年五月《新青年》第四卷第五號。作者首次采用了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “魯迅”這一筆名。它是我國現代文學史上第一篇猛烈抨擊“吃人”的封建禮教的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    小說。作者除在本書（《吶喊》）《自序》中提及它產生的緣由外，又在《〈中國</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    新文學大系〉小說二集序》中指出它“意在暴露家族制度和禮教的弊害”，可以參</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    看。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え候補︰清代官制，通過科舉或捐納等途徑取得官餃，但還沒有實際職務的中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    下級官員，由吏部抽簽分發到某部或某省，听候委用，稱為候補。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ古久先生的陳年流水簿子︰這里比喻我國封建主義統治的長久歷史。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お“本草什麼”︰指《本草綱目》，明代醫學家李時珍（1518—1593）的藥物</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    學著作，共五十二卷。該書曾經提到唐代陳藏器《本草拾遺》中以人肉醫治癆的記</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    載，並表示了異議。這里說李時珍的書“明明寫著人肉可以煎吃”，當是“狂人”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的“記中語誤”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か“易子而食”︰語見《左傳》宣公十五年，是宋將華元對楚將子反敘說宋國</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都城被楚軍圍困時的慘狀︰“敝邑易子而食，析骸而爨。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    が“食肉寢皮”︰語出《左傳》襄公二十一年，晉國州綽對齊莊公說︰“然二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    子者，譬于禽獸，臣食其肉而寢處其皮矣。”（按︰“二子”指齊國的殖綽和郭最，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們曾被州綽俘虜過。）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    き“海乙那”︰英語hyena的音譯，即鬣狗（又名土狼），一種食肉獸，常跟在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    獅虎等猛獸之後，以它們吃剩的獸類的殘尸為食。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぎ易牙︰春秋時齊國人，善于調味。據《管子•小稱》︰“夫易牙以調和事公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （按︰指齊桓公），公曰‘惟蒸嬰兒之未嘗’，于是蒸其首子而獻之公。”桀、紂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    各為我國夏朝和商朝的最後一代君主，易牙和他們不是同時代人。這里說的“易牙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    蒸了他兒子，給桀紂吃”，也是“狂人”“語頗錯雜無倫次”的表現。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    く徐錫林︰隱指徐錫麟（1873—1907），字伯蓀，浙江紹興人，清末革命團體</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    光復會的重要成員。一九○七年與秋瑾準備在浙、皖兩省同時起義。七月六日，他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    以安徽巡警處會辦兼巡警學堂監督身份為掩護，乘學堂舉行畢業典禮之機刺死安徽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    巡撫恩銘，率領學生攻佔軍械局，彈盡被捕，當日慘遭殺害，心肝被恩銘的衛隊挖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    出炒食。ぐ指“割股療親”，即割取自己的股肉煎藥，以醫治父母的重病。這是封</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    建社會的一種愚孝行為。《宋史•選舉志一》︰“上以孝取人，則勇者割股，怯者</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    廬墓。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">鴨的喜劇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    俄國的盲詩人愛羅先珂え君帶了他那六弦琴到北京之後不久，便向我訴苦說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “寂寞呀，寂寞呀，在沙漠上似的寂寞呀！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">這應該是真實的，但在我卻未曾感得；我住得久了，“入芝蘭之室，久而不聞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    其香”，只以為很是嚷嚷罷了。然而我之所謂嚷嚷，或者也就是他之所謂寂寞罷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我可是覺得在北京仿佛沒有春和秋。老于北京的人說，地氣北轉了，這里在先</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是沒有這麼和暖。只是我總以為沒有春和秋；冬末和夏初餃接起來，夏才去，冬又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    開始了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    一日就是這冬末夏初的時候，而且是夜間，我偶而得了閑暇，去訪問愛羅先珂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    君。他一向寓在仲密君的家里；這時一家的人都睡了覺了，天下很安靜。他獨自靠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在自己的臥榻上，很高的眉稜在金黃色的長發之間微蹙了，是在想他舊游之地的緬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    甸，緬甸的夏夜。“這樣的夜間，”他說，“在緬甸是遍地是音樂。房里，草間，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    樹上，都有昆蟲吟叫，各種聲音，成為合奏，很神奇。其間時時夾著蛇鳴︰‘嘶嘶！’</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    可是也與蟲聲相和協……”他沉思了，似乎想要追想起那時的情景來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我開不得口。這樣奇妙的音樂，我在北京確乎未曾听到過，所以即使如何愛國，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也辯護不得，因為他雖然目無所見，耳朵是沒有聾的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “北京卻連蛙鳴也沒有……”他又嘆息說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “蛙鳴是有的！”這嘆息，卻使我勇猛起來了，于是抗議說，“到夏天，大雨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    之後，你便能听到許多蝦蟆叫，那是都在溝里面的，因為北京到處都有溝。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “哦……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    過了幾天，我的話居然證實了，因為愛羅先珂君已經買到了十幾個科斗子。他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    買來便放在他窗外的院子中央的小池里。那池的長有三尺，寬有二尺，是仲密所掘，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    以種荷花的荷池。從這荷池里，雖然從來沒有見過養出半朵荷花來，然而養蝦蟆卻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    實在是一個極合式的處所。科斗成群結隊的在水里面游泳；愛羅先珂君也常常踱來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    訪他們。有時候，孩子告訴他說，“愛羅先珂先生，他們生了腳了。”他便高興的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    微笑道，“哦！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    然而養成池沼的音樂家卻只是愛羅先珂君的一件事。他是向來主張自食其力的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    常說女人可以畜牧，男人就應該種田。所以遇到很熟的友人，他便要勸誘他就在院</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    子里種白菜；也屢次對仲密夫人勸告，勸伊養蜂，養雞，養豬，養牛，養駱駝。後</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來仲密家果然有了許多小雞，滿院飛跑，啄完了鋪地錦的嫩葉，大約也許就是這勸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    告的結果了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    從此賣小雞的鄉下人也時常來，來一回便買幾只，因為小雞是容易積食，發痧，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    很難得長壽的；而且有一匹還成了愛羅先珂君在北京所作唯一的小說《小雞的悲劇》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お里的主人公。有一天的上午，那鄉下人竟意外的帶了小鴨來了，咻咻的叫著；但</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是仲密夫人說不要。愛羅先珂君也跑出來，他們就放一個在他兩手里，而小鴨便在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他兩手里咻咻的叫。他以為這也很可愛，于是又不能不買了，一共買了四個，每個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    八十文。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    小鴨也誠然是可愛，遍身松花黃，放在地上，便蹣跚的走，互相招呼，總是在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一處。大家都說好，明天去買泥鰍來喂他們罷。愛羅先珂君說，“這錢也可以歸我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    出的。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    他于是教書去了；大家也走散。不一會，仲密夫人拿冷飯來喂他們時，，在遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    處已听得潑水的聲音，跑到一看，原來那四個小鴨都在荷池里洗澡了，而且還翻筋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    斗，吃東西呢。等到攔他們上了岸，全池已經是渾水，過了半天，澄清了，只見泥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    里露出幾條細藕來；而且再也尋不出一個已經生了腳的科斗了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “伊和希珂先，沒有了，蝦蟆的兒子。”傍晚時候，孩子們一見他回來，最小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的一個便趕緊說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “唔，蝦蟆？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    仲密夫人也出來了，報告了小鴨吃完科斗的故事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “唉，唉！……”他說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    待到小鴨褪了黃毛，愛羅先珂君卻忽而渴念著他的“俄羅斯母親”か了，便匆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    匆的向赤塔去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    待到四處蛙鳴的時候，小鴨也已經長成，兩個白的，兩個花的，而且不復咻咻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的叫，都是“鴨鴨”的叫了。荷花池也早已容不下他們盤桓了，幸而仲密的住家的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    地勢是很低的，夏雨一降，院子里滿積了水，他們便欣欣然，游水，鑽水，拍翅子，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “鴨鴨”的叫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    現在又從夏末交了冬初，而愛羅先珂君還是絕無消息，不知道究竟在那里了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    只有四個鴨，卻還在沙漠上“鴨鴨”的叫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一九二二年十月。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九二二年十二月上海《婦女雜志》第八卷第十二號。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え愛羅先珂（1889—1952）︰俄國詩人和童話作家。童年時因病雙目失明。曾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    先後到過日本、泰國、緬甸、印度。一九二一年在日本因參加“五一”游行被驅逐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    出境，後輾轉來到我國。一九二二年從上海到北京，曾在北京大學、北京世界語專</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    門學校任教。一九二三年回國。他用世界語和日語寫作，魯迅曾譯過他的作品《桃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    色的雲》、《愛羅先珂童話集》等。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ“入芝蘭之室，久而不聞其香”︰語見《孔子家語•六本》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お《小雞的悲劇》︰童話。魯迅于一九二二年七月譯出，發表于同年九月上海</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    《婦女雜志》第八卷第九號，後收入《愛羅先珂童話集》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か“俄羅斯母親”︰俄羅斯人民對祖國的愛稱。﹝《吶喊》﹞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">端午節</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    方玄綽近來愛說“差不多”這一句話，幾乎成了“口頭禪”似的；而且不但說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的確也盤據在他腦里了。他最初說的是“都一樣”，後來大約覺得欠穩當了，便改</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    為“差不多”，一直使用到現在。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    他自從發見了這一句平凡的警句以後，雖然引起了不少的新感慨，同時卻也到</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    許多新慰安。譬如看見老輩威壓青年，在先是要憤憤的，但現在卻就轉念道，將來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這少年有了兒孫時，大抵也要擺這架子的罷，便再沒有什麼不平了。又如看見兵士</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    打車夫，在先也要憤憤的，但現在也就轉念道，倘使這車夫當了兵，這兵拉了車，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大抵也就這麼打，便再也不放在心上了。他這樣想著的時候，有時也疑心是因為自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    己沒有和惡社會奮斗的勇氣，所以瞞心昧己的故意造出來的一條逃路，很近于“無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是非之心”え，遠不如改正了好。然而這意見總反而在他腦里生長起來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    他將這“差不多說”最初公表的時候是在北京首善學校的講堂上，其時大概是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    提起關于歷史上的事情來，于是說到“古今人不相遠”，說到各色人等的“性相近”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ，終于牽扯到學生和官僚身上，大發其議論道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “現在社會上時髦的都通行罵官僚，而學生罵得尤利害。然而官僚並不是天生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的特別種族，就是平民變就的。現在學生出身的官僚就不少，和老官僚有什麼兩樣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    呢？‘易地則皆然’お，思想言論舉動豐采都沒有什麼大區別……便是學生團體新</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    辦的許多事業，不是也已經難免出弊病，大半煙消火滅了麼？差不多的。但中國將</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來之可慮就在此……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    散坐在講堂里的二十多個听講者，有的悵然了，或者是以為這話對；有的勃然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了，大約是以為侮辱了神聖的青年；有幾個卻對他微笑了，大約以為這是他替自己</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的辯解︰因為方玄綽就是兼做官僚的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    而其實卻是都錯誤。這不過是他的一種新不平；雖說不平，又只是他的一種安</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    分的空論。他自己雖然不知道是因為懶，還是因為無用，總之覺得是一個不肯運動，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    十分安分守己的人。總長冤他有神經病，只要地位還不至于動搖，他決不開一開口；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    教員的薪水欠到大半年了，只要別有官俸支持，他也決不開一開口。不但不開口，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    當教員聯合索薪的時候，他還暗地里以為欠斟酌，太嚷嚷；直到听得同寮過分的奚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    落他們了，這才略有些小感慨，後來一轉念，這或者因為自己正缺錢，而別的官並</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不兼做教員的緣故罷，于是就釋然了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    他雖然也缺錢，但從沒有加入教員的團體內，大家議決罷課，可是不去上課了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    政府說“上了課才給錢”，他才略恨他們的類乎用果子耍猴子；一個大教育家か說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    道“教員一手挾書包一手要錢不高尚”，他才對于他的太太正式的發牢騷了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “喂，怎麼只有兩盤？”听了“不高尚說”這一日的晚餐時候，他看著菜蔬說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    他們是沒有受過新教育的，太太並無學名或雅號，所以也就沒有什麼稱呼了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    照老例雖然也可以叫“太太”但他又不願意太守舊，于是就發明了一個“喂”字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    太太對他卻連“喂”字也沒有，只要臉向著他說話，依據習慣法，他就知道這話是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    對他而發的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “可是上月領來的一成半都完了……昨天的米，也還是好容易才賒來的呢。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    伊站在桌旁臉對著他說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “你看，還說教書的要薪水是卑鄙哩。這種東西似乎連人要吃飯，飯要米做，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    米要錢買這一點粗淺事情都不知道……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “對啦。沒有錢怎麼買米，沒有米怎麼煮……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    他兩頰都鼓起來了，仿佛氣惱這答案正和他的議論“差不多”，近乎隨聲附和</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    模樣；接著便將頭轉向別一面去了，依據習慣法，這是宣告討論中止的表示。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    待到淒風冷雨這一天，教員們因為向政府去索欠薪が，在新華門前爛泥里被國</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    軍打得頭破血出之後，倒居然也發了一點薪水。方玄綽不費舉手之勞的領了錢，酌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    還些舊債，卻還缺一大筆款，這是因為官俸也頗有些拖欠了。當是時，便是廉吏清</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    官們也漸以為薪之不可不索，而況兼做教員的方玄綽，自然更表同情于學界起來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    所以大家主張繼續罷課的時候，他雖然仍未到場，事後卻尤其心悅誠服的確守了公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    共的決議。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    然而政府竟又付錢，學校也就開課了。但在前幾天，卻有學生總會上一個呈文</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    給政府，說“教員倘若不上課，便要付欠薪。”這雖然並無效，而方玄綽卻忽而記</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    起前回政府所說的“上了課才給錢”的話來，“差不多”這一個影子在他眼前又一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    幌，而且並不消滅，于是他便在講堂上公表了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    準此，可見如果將“差不多說”鍛煉羅織起來，自然也可以判作一種挾帶私心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的不平，但總不能說是專為自己做官的辯解。只是每到這些時，他又常常喜歡拉上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    中國將來的命運之類的問題，一不小心，便連自己也以為是一個憂國的志士；人們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是每苦于沒有“自知之明”的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    但是“差不多”的事實又發生了，政府當初雖只不理那些招人頭痛的教員，後</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來竟不理到無關痛癢的官吏，欠而又欠，終于逼得先前鄙薄教員要錢的好官，也很</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有幾員化為索薪大會里的驍將了。惟有幾種日報上卻很發了些鄙薄譏笑他們的文字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    方玄綽也毫不為奇，毫不介意，因為他根據了他的“差不多說”，知道這是新聞記</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    者還未缺少潤筆き的緣故，萬一政府或是闊人停了津貼，他們多半也要開大會的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他既已表同情于教員的索薪，自然也贊成同寮的索俸，然而他仍安坐在衙門中，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    照例的並不一同去討債。至于有人疑心他孤高，那可也不過是一種誤解罷了。他自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    己說，他是自從出世以來，只有人向他來要債，他從沒有向人去討過債，所以這一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    端是“非其所長”。而且他是不敢見手握經經濟之權的人物，這種人待到失了權勢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    之後，捧著一本《大乘起信論》ぎ講佛學的時候，固然也很是“藹然可親”的了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但還在寶座上時，卻總是一副閻王臉，將別人都當奴才看，自以為手操著你們這些</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    窮小子們的生殺之權。他因此不敢見，也不願見他們。這種脾氣，雖然有時連自己</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也覺得是孤高，但往往同時也疑心這其實是沒本領。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    大家左索右索，總自一節一節的挨過去了，但比起先前來，方玄綽究竟是萬分</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的拮據，所以使用的小廝和交易的店家不消說，便是方太太對于他也漸漸的缺了敬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    意，只要看伊近來不很附和，而且常常提出獨創的意見，有些唐突的舉動，也就可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    以了然了。到了陰歷五月初四的午前，他一回來，伊便將一疊賬單塞在他的鼻子跟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    前，這也是往常所沒有的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “一總總得一百八十塊錢才夠開消……發了麼？”伊並不對著他看的說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “哼，我明天不做官了。錢的支票是領來的了，可是索薪大會的代表不發放，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    先說是沒有同去的人都不發，後來又說是要到他們跟前去親領。他們今天單捏著支</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    票，就變了閻王臉了，我實在怕看見……我錢也不要了，官也不做了，這樣無限量</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的卑屈……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    方太太見了這少見的義憤，倒有些愕然了，但也就沉靜下來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “我想，還不如去親領罷，這算什麼呢。”伊看著他的臉說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “我不去！這是官俸，不是賞錢，照例應該由會計科送來的。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “可是不送來又怎麼好呢……哦，昨夜忘記說了，孩子們說那學費，學校里已</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    經催過好幾次了，說是倘若再不繳……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “胡說！做老子的辦事教書都不給錢，兒子去念幾句書倒要錢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    伊覺得他已經不很顧忌道理，似乎就要將自己當作校長來出氣，犯不上，便不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    再言語了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    兩個默默的吃了午飯。他想了一會，又懊惱的出去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    照舊例，近年是每逢節根或年關的前一天，他一定須在夜里的十二點鐘才回家，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一面走，一面掏著懷中，一面大聲的叫道，“喂，領來了！”于是遞給伊一疊簇新</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的中交票く，臉上很有些得意的形色。誰知道初四這一天卻破了例，他不到七點鐘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便回家來。方太太很驚疑，以為他竟已辭了職了，但暗暗地察看他臉上，卻也並不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    見有什麼格外倒運的神情。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “怎麼了？……這樣早？……”伊看定了他說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “發不及了，領不出了，銀行已經關了門，得等初八。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “親領？……”伊惴惴的問。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “親領這一層也已經取消了，听說仍舊由會計科分送。可是銀行今天已經關了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    門，休息三天，得等到初八的上午。”他坐下，眼楮看著地面了，喝過一口茶，才</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    又慢慢的開口說，“幸而衙門里也沒有什麼問題了，大約到初八就準有錢……向不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    相干的親戚朋友去借錢，實在是一件煩難事。我午後硬著頭皮去尋金永生，談了一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    會，他先恭維我不去索薪，不肯親領，非常之清高，一個人正應該這樣做；待到知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    道我想要向他通融五十元，就像我在他嘴里塞了一大把鹽似的，凡有臉上可以打皺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的地迫都打起皺來，說房租怎樣的收不起，買賣怎樣的賠本，在同事面前親身領款，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也不算什麼的，即刻將我支使出來了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “這樣緊急的節根，誰還肯借出錢去呢。”方太太卻只淡淡的說，並沒有什麼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    慨然。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    方玄綽低下頭來了，覺得這也無怪其然的，況且自己和金永生本來很疏遠。他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    接著就記起去年年關的事來，那時有一個同鄉來借十塊錢，他其時明明已經收到了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    衙門的領款憑單的了，因為死怕這人將來未必會還錢，便裝了副為難的神色，說道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    衙門里既然領不到俸錢，學校里又不發薪水，實在“愛莫能助”，將他空手送走了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他雖然自已並不看見裝了怎樣的臉，但此時卻覺得很局促，嘴唇微微一動，又搖一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    搖頭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    然而不多久，他忽而恍然大悟似的發命令了︰叫小廝即刻上街去賒一瓶蓮花白。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他知道店家希圖明天多還帳，大抵是不敢不賒的，假如不賒，則明天分文不還，正</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是他們應得的懲罰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    蓮花白竟賒來了，他喝了兩杯，青白色的臉上泛了紅，吃完飯，又頗有些高興</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了，他點上一枝大號哈德門香煙，從桌上抓起一本《嘗試集》ぐ來，躺在床上就要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    看。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “那麼明天怎麼對付店家呢？”方太太追上去，站在床面前看著他的臉說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “店家？……教他們初八的下半天來。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “我可不能這麼說。他們不相信，不答應的。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “有什麼不相信。他們可以問去，全衙門里什麼人也沒有領到，都得初八！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他戟著第二個指頭在帳子里的空中畫了一個半圓，方太太跟著指頭也看了一個半圓，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    只見這手便去翻開了《嘗試集》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    方太太見他強橫到出乎情理之外了，也暫時開不得口。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “我想，這模樣是鬧不下去的，將來總得想點法，做點什麼別的事……”伊終</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    于尋到了別的路，說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “什麼法呢？我‘文不像謄錄生，武不像救火兵’，別的做什麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你不是給上海的書鋪子做過文章麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “上海的書鋪子？買稿要一個一個的算字，空格不算數。你看我做在那里的白</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    話詩去，空白有多少，怕只值三百大錢一本罷。收版權稅又半年六月沒消息，‘遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    水救不得近火’，誰耐煩。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “那麼，給這里的報館里……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “給報館里？便在這里很大的報館里，我靠著一個學生在那里做編輯的大情面，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一千字也就是這幾個錢，即使一早做到夜，能夠養活你們麼？況且我肚子里也沒有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這許多文章。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “那麼，過了節怎麼辦呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “過了節麼？——仍舊做官……明天店家來要錢，你只要說初八的下午。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他又要看《嘗試集》了。方太太怕失了機會，連忙吞吞吐吐的說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我想，過了節，到了初八，我們……倒不如去買一張彩票　……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “胡說！會說這樣無教育的……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這時候，他忽而又記起被金永生支使出來以後的事了。那時他惘惘的走過稻香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    村，看店門口豎著許多斗大的字的廣告道“頭彩幾萬元”，仿佛記得心里也一動，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    或者也許放慢了腳步的罷，但似乎因為舍不得皮夾里僅存的六角錢，所以竟也毅然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    決然的走遠了。他臉色一變，方太太料想他是在惱著伊的無教育，便趕緊退開，沒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有說完話。方玄綽也沒有說完話，將腰一伸，咿咿嗚嗚的就念《嘗試集》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一九二二年六月。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九二二年九月上海《小說月報》第十三卷第九號。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え“無是非之心”︰語見《孟子•公孫丑》︰“無是非之心，非人也。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ“性相近”︰語見《論語•陽貨》︰“性相近也，習相遠也。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お“易地則皆然”︰語見《孟子•離婁》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か大教育家︰指範源濂。據北京《語絲》周刊第十四期《理想中的教師》一文</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    追述︰“前教育總長……範靜生先生（按︰即範源濂）也曾非難過北京各校的教員，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    說他們一手拿錢，一手拿書包上課。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    が指當時曾發生的索薪事件。一九二一年六月三日，國立北京專門以上八校辭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    職教職員代表聯席會，聯合全市各校教職員工和學生群眾一萬多人舉行示威游行，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    向以徐世昌為首的北洋軍閥政府索取欠薪，遭到鎮壓，多人受傷。下文的新華門，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在北京西長安街，當時曾是北洋軍閥政府總統府的大門。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    き潤筆︰原指給撰作詩文或寫字、畫畫的人的報酬，後來也用作稿酬的別稱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぎ《大乘起信論》︰佛經名。印度馬鳴菩薩作。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    く中交票︰中國銀行和交通銀行（都是當時的國家銀行）發行的鈔票。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぐ《嘗試集》︰胡適作的白話詩集，一九二○年三月上海亞東圖書館出版。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　彩票︰一種帶有賭博性質的證券。大多由官方發行，編有號碼，以一定的價</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    格出售，從售得的款中提出一小部分作獎金；用抽簽的辦法定出各級中獎號碼，凡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    彩票號碼與中獎號碼相同的，按等級領獎，未中的作廢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">故鄉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我冒了嚴寒，回到相隔二千余里，別了二十余年的故鄉去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    時候既然是深冬；漸近故鄉時，天氣又陰晦了，冷風吹進船艙中，嗚嗚的響，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    從蓬隙向外一望，蒼黃的天底下，遠近橫著幾個蕭索的荒村，沒有一些活氣。我的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    心禁不住悲涼起來了。阿！這不是我二十年來時時記得的故鄉？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我所記得的故鄉全不如此。我的故鄉好得多了。但要我記起他的美麗，說出他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的佳處來，卻又沒有影像，沒有言辭了。仿佛也就如此。于是我自己解釋說︰故鄉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    本也如此，——雖然沒有進步，也未必有如我所感的悲涼，這只是我自己心情的改</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    變罷了，因為我這次回鄉，本沒有什麼好心緒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我這次是專為了別他而來的。我們多年聚族而居的老屋，已經公同賣給別姓了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    交屋的期限，只在本年，所以必須趕在正月初一以前，永別了熟識的老屋，而且遠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    離了熟識的故鄉，搬家到我在謀食的異地去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    第二日清早晨我到了我家的門口了。瓦楞上許多枯草的斷睫當風抖著，正在說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    明這老屋難免易主的原因。幾房的本家大約已經搬走了，所以很寂靜。我到了自家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的房外，我的母親早已迎著出來了，接著便飛出了八歲的佷兒宏兒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我的母親很高興，但也藏著許多淒涼的神情，教我坐下，歇息，喝茶，且不談</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    搬家的事。宏兒沒有見過我，遠遠的對面站著只是看。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    但我們終于談到搬家的事。我說外間的寓所已經租定了，又買了幾件家具，此</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    外須將家里所有的木器賣去，再去增添。母親也說好，而且行李也略已齊集，木器</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不便搬運的，也小半賣去了，只是收不起錢來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “你休息一兩天，去拜望親戚本家一回，我們便可以走了。”母親說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “是的。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “還有閏土，他每到我家來時，總問起你，很想見你一回面。我已經將你到家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的大約日期通知他，他也許就要來了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    這時候，我的腦里忽然閃出一幅神異的圖畫來︰深藍的天空中掛著一輪金黃的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    圓月，下面是海邊的沙地，都種著一望無際的碧綠的西瓜，其間有一個十一二歲的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    少年，項帶銀圈，手捏一柄鋼叉，向一匹　え盡力的刺去，那　卻將身一扭，反從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他的胯下逃走了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    這少年便是閏土。我認識他時，也不過十多歲，離現在將有三十年了；那時我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的父親還在世，家景也好，我正是一個少爺。那一年，我家是一件大祭祀的值年ぉ。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這祭祀，說是三十多年才能輪到一回，所以很鄭重；正月里供祖像，供品很多，祭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    器很講究，拜的人也很多，祭器也很要防偷去。我家只有一個忙月（我們這里給人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    做工的分三種︰整年給一定人家做工的叫長工；按日給人做工的叫短工；自己也種</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    地，只在過年過節以及收租時候來給一定人家做工的稱忙月），忙不過來，他便對</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    父親說，可以叫他的兒子閏土來管祭器的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我的父親允許了；我也很高興，因為我早听到閏土這名字，而且知道他和我仿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    佛年紀，閏月生的，五行缺土お，所以他的父親叫他閏土。他是能裝﹝弓京﹞捉小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    鳥雀的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我于是日日盼望新年，新年到，閏土也就到了。好容易到了年末，有一日，母</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    親告訴我，閏土來了，我便飛跑的去看。他正在廚房里，紫色的圓臉，頭戴一頂小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    氈帽，頸上套一個明晃晃的銀項圈，這可見他的父親十分愛他，怕他死去，所以在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    神佛面前許下願心，用圈子將他套住了。他見人很怕羞，只是不怕我，沒有旁人的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    時候，便和我說話，于是不到半日，我們便熟識了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我們那時候不知道談些什麼，只記得閏土很高興，說是上城之後，見了許多沒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有見過的東西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    第二日，我便要他捕鳥。他說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這不能。須大雪下了才好。我們沙地上，下了雪，我掃出一塊空地來，用短</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    棒支起一個大竹匾，撒下秕谷，看鳥雀來吃時，我遠遠地將縛在棒上的繩子只一拉，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那鳥雀就罩在竹匾下了。什麼都有︰稻雞，角雞，鵓鴣，藍背……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我于是又很盼望下雪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    閏土又對我說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “現在太冷，你夏天到我們這里來。我們日里到海邊撿貝殼去，紅的綠的都有，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    鬼見怕也有，觀音手か也有。晚上我和爹管西瓜去，你也去。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “管賊麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “不是。走路的人口渴了摘一個瓜吃，我們這里是不算偷的。要管的是獾豬，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    刺蝟，　。月亮底下，你听，啦啦的響了，　在咬瓜了。你便捏了胡叉，輕輕地走</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    去……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我那時並不知道這所謂　的是怎麼一件東西——便是現在也沒有知道——只是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    無端的覺得狀如小狗而很凶猛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “他不咬人麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “有胡叉呢。走到了，看見　了，你便刺。這畜生很伶俐，倒向你奔來，反從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    胯下竄了。他的皮毛是油一般的滑……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我素不知道天下有這許多新鮮事︰海邊有如許五色的貝殼；西瓜有這樣危險的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    經歷，我先前單知道他在水果電里出賣罷了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “我們沙地里，潮汛要來的時候，就有許多跳魚兒只是跳，都有青蛙似的兩個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    腳……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    阿！閏土的心里有無窮無盡的希奇的事，都是我往常的朋友所不知道的。他們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不知道一些事，閏土在海邊時，他們都和我一樣只看見院子里高牆上的四角的天空。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    可惜正月過去了，閏土須回家里去，我急得大哭，他也躲到廚房里，哭著不肯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    出門，但終于被他父親帶走了。他後來還托他的父親帶給我一包貝殼和幾支很好看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的鳥毛，我也曾送他一兩次東西，但從此沒有再見面。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    現在我的母親提起了他，我這兒時的記憶，忽而全都閃電似的甦生過來，似乎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    看到了我的美麗的故鄉了。我應聲說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這好極！他，——怎樣？……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “他？……他景況也很不如意……”母親說著，便向房外看，“這些人又來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    說是買木器，順手也就隨便拿走的，我得去看看。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    母親站起身，出去了。門外有幾個女人的聲音。我便招宏兒走近面前，和他閑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    話︰問他可會寫字，可願意出門。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “我們坐火車去麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我們坐火車去。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “船呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “先坐船，……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “哈！這模樣了！胡子這麼長了！”一種尖利的怪聲突然大叫起來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我吃了一嚇，趕忙抬起頭，卻見一個凸顴骨，薄嘴唇，五十歲上下的女人站在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我面前，兩手搭在髀間，沒有系裙，張著兩腳，正像一個畫圖儀器里細腳伶仃的圓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    規。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我愕然了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “不認識了麼？我還抱過你咧！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我愈加愕然了。幸而我的母親也就進來，從旁說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “他多年出門，統忘卻了。你該記得罷，”便向著我說，“這是斜對門的楊二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    嫂，……開豆腐店的。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    哦，我記得了。我孩子時候，在斜對門的豆腐店里確乎終日坐著一個楊二嫂，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    人都叫伊“豆腐西施”が。但是擦著白粉，顴骨沒有這麼高，嘴唇也沒有這麼薄，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而且終日坐著，我也從沒有見過這圓規式的姿勢。那時人說︰因為伊，這豆腐店的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    買賣非常好。但這大約因為年齡的關系，我卻並未蒙著一毫感化，所以竟完全忘卻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了。然而圓規很不平，顯出鄙夷的神色，仿佛嗤笑法國人不知道拿破侖き，美國人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不知道華盛頓ぎ似的，冷笑說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “忘了？這真是貴人眼高……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “那有這事……我……”我惶恐著，站起來說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “那麼，我對你說。迅哥兒，你闊了，搬動又笨重，你還要什麼這些破爛木器，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    讓我拿去罷。我們小戶人家，用得著。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    “我並沒有闊哩。我須賣了這些，再去……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “阿呀呀，你放了道台く了，還說不闊？你現在有三房姨太太；出門便是八抬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的大轎，還說不闊？嚇，什麼都瞞不過我。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我知道無話可說了，便閉了口，默默的站著。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “阿呀阿呀，真是愈有錢，便愈是一毫不肯放松，愈是一毫不肯放松，便愈有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    錢……”圓規一面憤憤的回轉身，一面絮絮的說，慢慢向外走，順便將我母親的一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    副手套塞在褲腰里，出去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    此後又有近處的本家和親戚來訪問我。我一面應酬，偷空便收拾些行李，這樣</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的過了三四天。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    一日是天氣很冷的午後，我吃過午飯，坐著喝茶，覺得外面有人進來了，便回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    頭去看。我看時，不由的非常出驚，慌忙站起身，迎著走去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    這來的便是閏土。雖然我一見便知道是閏土，但又不是我這記憶上的閏土了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他身材增加了一倍；先前的紫色的圓臉，已經變作灰黃，而且加上了很深的皺紋；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    眼楮也像他父親一樣，周圍都腫得通紅，這我知道，在海邊種地的人，終日吹著海</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    風，大抵是這樣的。他頭上是一頂破氈帽，身上只一件極薄的棉衣，渾身瑟索著；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    手里提著一個紙包和一支長煙管，那手也不是我所記得的紅活圓實的手，卻又粗又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    笨而且開裂，像是松樹皮了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    我這時很興奮，但不知道怎麼說才好，只是說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “阿！閏土哥，——你來了？……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我接著便有許多話，想要連珠一般涌出︰角雞，跳魚兒，貝殼，　，……但又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    總覺得被什麼擋著似的，單在腦里面回旋，吐不出口外去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">    他站住了，臉上現出歡喜和淒涼的神情；動著嘴唇，卻沒有作聲。他的態度終</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    于恭敬起來了，分明的叫道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “老爺！……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我似乎打了一個寒噤；我就知道，我們之間已經隔了一層可悲的厚障壁了。我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也說不出話。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他回過頭去說，“水生，給老爺磕頭。”便拖出躲在背後的孩子來，這正是一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    個廿年前的閏土，只是黃瘦些，頸子上沒有銀圈罷了。“這是第五個孩子，沒有見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    過世面，躲躲閃閃……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    母親和宏兒下樓來了，他們大約也听到了聲音。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “老太太。信是早收到了。我實在喜歡的不得了，知道老爺回來……”閏土說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “阿，你怎的這樣客氣起來。你們先前不是哥弟稱呼麼？還是照舊︰迅哥兒。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    母親高興的說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “阿呀，老太太真是……這成什麼規矩。那時是孩子，不懂事……”閏土說著，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    又叫水生上來打拱，那孩子卻害羞，緊緊的只貼在他背後。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “他就是水生？第五個？都是生人，怕生也難怪的；還是宏兒和他去走走。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    母親說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    宏兒听得這話，便來招水生，水生卻松松爽爽同他一路出去了。母親叫閏土坐，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他遲疑了一回，終于就了坐，將長煙管靠在桌旁，遞過紙包來，說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “冬天沒有什麼東西了。這一點干青豆倒是自家曬在那里的，請老爺……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我問問他的景況。他只是搖頭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “非常難。第六個孩子也會幫忙了，卻總是吃不夠……又不太平……什麼地方</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都要錢，沒有規定……收成又壞。種出東西來，挑去賣，總要捐幾回錢，折了本；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不去賣，又只能爛掉……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他只是搖頭；臉上雖然刻著許多皺紋，卻全然不動，仿佛石像一般。他大約只</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是覺得苦，卻又形容不出，沉默了片時，便拿起煙管來默默的吸煙了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    母親問他，知道他的家里事務忙，明天便得回去；又沒有吃過午飯，便叫他自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    己到廚下炒飯吃去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他出去了；母親和我都嘆息他的景況︰多子，饑荒，苛稅，兵，匪，官，紳，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都苦得他像一個木偶人了。母親對我說，凡是不必搬走的東西，盡可以送他，可以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    听他自己去揀擇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    下午，他揀好了幾件東西︰兩條長桌，四個椅子，一副香爐和燭台，一桿抬秤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他又要所有的草灰（我們這里煮飯是燒稻草的，那灰，可以做沙地的肥料），待我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    們啟程的時候，他用船來載去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    夜間，我們又談些閑天，都是無關緊要的話；第二天早晨，他就領了水生回去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    又過了九日，是我們啟程的日期。閏土早晨便到了，水生沒有同來，卻只帶著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一個五歲的女兒管船只。我們終日很忙碌，再沒有談天的工夫。來客也不少，有送</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    行的，有拿東西的，有送行兼拿東西的。待到傍晚我們上船的時候，這老屋里的所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有破舊大小粗細東西，已經一掃而空了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我們的船向前走，兩岸的青山在黃昏中，都裝成了深黛顏色，連著退向船後梢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    宏兒和我靠著船窗，同看外面模糊的風景，他忽然問道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “大伯！我們什麼時候回來？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “回來？你怎麼還沒有走就想回來了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “可是，水生約我到他家玩去咧……”他睜著大的黑眼楮，痴痴的想。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我和母親也都有些惘然，于是又提起閏土來。母親說，那豆腐西施的楊二嫂，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    自從我家收拾行李以來，本是每日必到的，前天伊在灰堆里，掏出十多個碗碟來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    議論之後，便定說是閏土埋著的，他可以在運灰的時候，一齊搬回家里去；楊二嫂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    發見了這件事，自己很以為功，便拿了那狗氣殺（這是我們這里養雞的器具，木盤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    上面有著柵欄，內盛食料，雞可以伸進頸子去啄，狗卻不能，只能看著氣死），飛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也似的跑了，虧伊裝著這麼高低的小腳，竟跑得這樣快。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老屋離我愈遠了；故鄉的山水也都漸漸遠離了我，但我卻並不感到怎樣的留戀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我只覺得我四面有看不見的高牆，將我隔成孤身，使我非常氣悶；那西瓜地上的銀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    項圈的小英雄的影像，我本來十分清楚，現在卻忽地模糊了，又使我非常的悲哀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    母親和宏兒都睡著了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我躺著，听船底潺潺的水聲，知道我在走我的路。我想︰我竟與閏土隔絕到這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    地步了，但我們的後輩還是一氣，宏兒不是正在想念水生麼。我希望他們不再像我，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    又大家隔膜起來……然而我又不願意他們因為要一氣，都如我的辛苦展轉而生活，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也不願意他們都如閏土的辛苦麻木而生活，也不願意都如別人的辛苦恣睢而生活。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們應該有新的生活，為我們所未經生活過的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我想到希望，忽然害怕起來了。閏土要香爐和燭台的時候，我還暗地里笑他，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    以為他總是崇拜偶像，什麼時候都不忘卻。現在我所謂希望，不也是我自己手制的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    偶像麼？只是他的願望切近，我的願望茫遠罷了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我在朦朧中，眼前展開一片海邊碧綠的沙地來，上面深藍的天空中掛著一輪金</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    黃的圓月。我想︰希望本是無所謂有，無所謂無的。這正如地上的路；其實地上本</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    沒有路，走的人多了，也便成了路。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一九二一年一月。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九二一年五月《新青年》第九卷第一號。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え?︰作者在一九二九年五月四日致舒新城的信中說︰“‘　’字是我據鄉下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    人所說的聲音，生造出來的，讀如‘查’。……現在想起來，也許是獾罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ大祭祀的值年︰封建社會中的大家族，每年都有祭祀祖先的活動，費用從族</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    中“祭產”收入支取，由各房按年輪流主持，輪到的稱為“值年”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お五行缺土︰舊社會所謂算“八字”的迷信說法。即用天干（甲乙丙丁戊己庚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    辛壬癸）和地支（子丑寅卯辰巳午未申酉戌亥）相配，來記一個人出生的年、月、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    日、時，各得兩字，合為“八字”；又認為它們在五行（金、木、水、火、土）中</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    各有所屬，如甲乙寅卯屬木，丙丁巳午屬火等等，如八個字能包括五者，就是五行</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    俱全。“五行缺土”，就是這八個字中沒有屬土的字，需用土或土作偏旁的字取名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    等辦法來彌補。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か鬼見怕和觀音手，都是小貝殼的名稱。舊時浙江沿海的人把這種小貝殼用線</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    串在一起，戴在孩子的手腕或腳踝上，認為可以“避邪”。這類名稱多是根據“避</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    邪”的意思取的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    が西施︰春秋時越國的美女，後來用以泛稱一般美女。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    き拿破侖（1769—1821）︰即拿破侖•波拿巴，法國資產階級革命時期的軍事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    家、政治家。一七九九年擔任共和國執政。一八○四年建立法蘭西第一帝國，自稱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    拿破侖一世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぎ華盛頓（1732—1799）︰即喬治•華盛頓，美國政治家。他曾領導一七七五</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    年至一七八三年美國反對英國殖民統治的獨立戰爭，勝利後任美國第一任總統。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    く道台︰清朝官職道員的俗稱，分總管一個區域行政職務的道員和專掌某一特</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    定職務的道員。前者是省以下、府州以上的行政長官；後者掌管一省特定事務，如</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    督糧道、兵備道等。辛亥革命後，北洋軍閥政府也曾沿用此制，改稱道尹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p> 孔乙己</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    魯鎮的酒店的格局，是和別處不同的︰都是當街一個曲尺形的大櫃台，櫃里面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    預備著熱水，可以隨時溫酒。做工的人，傍午傍晚散了工，每每花四文銅錢，買一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    碗酒，——這是二十多年前的事，現在每碗要漲到十文，——靠櫃外站著，熱熱的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    喝了休息；倘肯多花一文，便可以買一碟鹽煮筍，或者茴香豆，做下酒物了，如果</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    出到十幾文，那就能買一樣葷菜，但這些顧客，多是短衣幫，大抵沒有這樣闊綽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    只有穿長衫的，才踱進店面隔壁的房子里，要酒要菜，慢慢地坐喝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我從十二歲起，便在鎮口的咸亨酒店里當伙計，掌櫃說，樣子太傻，怕侍候不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了長衫主顧，就在外面做點事罷。外面的短衣主顧，雖然容易說話，但嘮嘮叨叨纏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    夾不清的也很不少。他們往往要親眼看著黃酒從壇子里舀出，看過壺子底里有水沒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有，又親看將壺子放在熱水里，然後放心︰在這嚴重兼督下，羼水也很為難。所以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    過了幾天，掌櫃又說我干不了這事。幸虧薦頭的情面大，辭退不得，便改為專管溫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    酒的一種無聊職務了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我從此便整天的站在櫃台里，專管我的職務。雖然沒有什麼失職，但總覺得有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    些單調，有些無聊。掌櫃是一副凶臉孔，主顧也沒有好聲氣，教人活潑不得；只有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    孔乙己到店，才可以笑幾聲，所以至今還記得。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    孔乙己是站著喝酒而穿長衫的唯一的人。他身材很高大；青白臉色，皺紋間時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    常夾些傷痕；一部亂蓬蓬的花白的胡子。穿的雖然是長衫，可是又髒又破，似乎十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    多年沒有補，也沒有洗。他對人說話，總是滿口之乎者也，教人半懂不懂的。因為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他姓孔，別人便從描紅紙え上的“上大人孔乙己”這半懂不懂的話里，替他取下一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    個綽號，叫作孔乙己。孔乙己一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看著他笑，有的叫道，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “孔乙己，你臉上又添上新傷疤了！”他不回答，對櫃里說，“溫兩碗酒，要一碟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    茴香豆。”便排出九文大錢。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，“你一定又偷了人家的東西</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了！”孔乙己睜大眼楮說，“你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白……”“什麼清白？我前天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    親眼見你偷了何家的書，吊著打。”孔乙己便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    辯道，“竊書不能算偷……竊書！……讀書人的事，能算偷麼？”接連便是難懂的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    話，什麼“君子固窮”ぉ，什麼“者乎”之類，引得眾人都哄笑起來︰店內外充滿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了快活的空氣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    听人家背地里談論，孔乙己原來也讀過書，但終于沒有進學お，又不會營生；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    于是愈過愈窮，弄到將要討飯了。幸而寫得一筆好字，便替人家鈔鈔書，換一碗飯</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    吃。可惜他又有一樣壞脾氣，便是好吃懶做。坐不到幾天，便連人和書籍紙張筆硯，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一齊失蹤。如是幾次，叫他鈔書的人也沒有了。孔乙己沒有法，便免不了偶然做些</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    偷竊的事。但他在我們店里，品行卻比別人都好，就是從不拖欠；雖然間或沒有現</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    錢，暫時記在粉板上，但不出一月，定然還清，從粉板上拭去了孔乙己的名字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    孔乙己喝過半碗酒，漲紅的臉色漸漸復了原，旁人便又問道，“孔乙己，你當</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    真認識字麼？”孔乙己看著問他的人，顯出不屑置辯的神氣。他們便接著說道，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你怎的連半個秀才也撈不到呢？”孔乙己立刻顯出頹唐不安模樣，臉上籠上了一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    層灰色，嘴里說些話；這回可是全是之乎者也之類，一些不懂了。在這時候，眾人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也都哄笑起來︰店內外充滿了快活的空氣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在這些時候，我可以附和著笑，掌櫃是決不責備的。而且掌櫃見了孔乙己，也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    每每這樣問他，引人發笑。孔乙己自己知道不能和他們談天，便只好向孩子說話。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有一回對我說道，“你讀過書麼？”我略略點一點頭。他說，“讀過書，……我便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    考你一考。茴香豆的茴字，怎樣寫的？”我想，討飯一樣的人，也配考我麼？便回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    過臉去，不再理會。孔乙己等了許久，很懇切的說道，“不能寫罷？……我教給你，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    記著！這些字應該記著。將來做掌櫃的時候，寫賬要用。”我暗想我和掌櫃的等級</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    還很遠呢，而且我們掌櫃也從不將茴香豆上賬；又好笑，又不耐煩，懶懶的答他道，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “誰要你教，不是草頭底下一個來回的回字麼？”孔乙己顯出極高興的樣子，將兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    個指頭的長指甲敲著櫃台，點頭說，“對呀對呀！……回字有四樣寫法か，你知道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    麼？”我愈不耐煩了，努著嘴走遠。孔乙己剛用指甲蘸了酒，想在櫃上寫字，見我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    毫不熱心，便又嘆一口氣，顯出極惋惜的樣子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有幾回，鄰居孩子听得笑聲，也趕熱鬧，圍住了孔乙己。他便給他們吃茴香豆，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一人一顆。孩子吃完豆，仍然不散，眼楮都望著碟子。孔乙己著了慌，伸開五指將</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    碟子罩住，彎腰下去說道，“不多了，我已經不多了。”直起身又看一看豆，自己</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    搖頭說，“不多不多！多乎哉？不多也。”が于是這一群孩子都在笑聲里走散了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    孔乙己是這樣的使人快活，可是沒有他，別人也便這麼過。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有一天，大約是中秋前的兩三天，掌櫃正在慢慢的結賬，取下粉板，忽然說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “孔乙己長久沒有來了。還欠十九個錢呢！”我才也覺得他的確長久沒有來了。一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    個喝酒的人說道，“他怎麼會來？……他打折了腿了。”掌櫃說，“哦！”“他總</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    仍舊是偷。這一回，是自己發昏，竟偷到丁舉人家里去了。他家的東西，偷得的麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “後來怎麼樣？”“怎麼樣？先寫服辯き，後來是打，打了大半夜，再打折了腿。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “後來呢？”“後來打折了腿了。”“打折了怎樣呢？”“怎樣？……誰曉得？許</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是死了。”掌櫃也不再問，仍然慢慢的算他的賬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    中秋之後，秋風是一天涼比一天，看看將近初冬；我整天的靠著火，也須穿上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    棉襖了。一天的下半天，沒有一個顧客，我正合了眼坐著。忽然間听得一個聲音，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “溫一碗酒。”這聲音雖然極低，卻很耳熟。看時又全沒有人。站起來向外一望，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那孔乙己便在櫃台下對了門檻坐著。他臉上黑而且瘦，已經不成樣子；穿一件破夾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    襖，盤著兩腿，下面墊一個蒲包，用草繩在肩上掛住；見了我，又說道，“溫一碗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    酒。”掌櫃也伸出頭去，一面說，“孔乙己麼？你還欠十九個錢呢！”孔乙己很頹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    唐的仰面答道，“這……下回還清罷。這一回是現錢，酒要好。”掌櫃仍然同平常</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一樣，笑著對他說，“孔乙己，你又偷了東西了！”但他這回卻不十分分辯，單說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了一句“不要取笑！”“取笑？要是不偷，怎麼會打斷腿？”孔乙己低聲說道，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “跌斷，跌，跌……”他的眼色，很像懇求掌櫃，不要再提。此時已經聚集了幾個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    人，便和掌櫃都笑了。我溫了酒，端出去，放在門檻上。他從破衣袋里摸出四文大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    錢，放在我手里，見他滿手是泥，原來他便用這手走來的。不一會，他喝完酒，便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    又在旁人的說笑聲中，坐著用這手慢慢走去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    自此以後，又長久沒有看見孔乙己。到了年關，掌櫃取下粉板說，“孔乙己還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    欠十九個錢呢！”到第二年的端午，又說“孔乙己還欠十九個錢呢！”到中秋可是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    沒有說，再到年關也沒有看見他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我到現在終于沒有見——大約孔乙己的確死了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一九一九年三月。ぎ</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九一九年四月《新青年》第六卷第四號。發表時篇末有作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    者的附記如下︰“這一篇很拙的小說，還是去年冬天做成的。那時的意思，單在描</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    寫社會上的或一種生活，請讀者看看，並沒有別的深意。但用活字排印了發表，卻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    已在這時候，——便是忽然有人用了小說盛行人身攻擊的時候。大抵著者走入暗路，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    每每能引讀者的思想跟他墮落︰以為小說是一種潑穢水的器具，里面糟蹋的是誰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這實在是一件極可嘆可憐的事。所以我在此聲明，免得發生猜度，害了讀者的人格。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一九一九年三月二十六日記。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え描紅紙︰一種印有紅色楷字，供兒童摹寫毛筆字用的字帖。舊時最通行的一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    種，印有“上大人孔（明代以前作丘）乙己化三千七十士爾小生八九子佳作仁可知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    禮也”這樣一些筆劃簡單、三字一句和似通非通的文字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ“君子固窮”︰語見《論語•衛靈公》。“固窮”即“固守其窮”，不以窮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    困而改便操守的意思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お進學︰明清科舉制度，童生經過縣考初試，府考復試，再參加由學政主持的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    院考（道考），考取的列名府、縣學籍，叫進學，也就成了秀才。又規定每三年舉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    行一次鄉試（省一級考試），由秀才或監生應考，取中的就是舉人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か回字有四樣寫法︰回字通常只有三種寫法︰回、﹝外“た”內“巳”﹞、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ﹝“面”之下部﹞。第四種寫作﹝外“囗”內“目”﹞（見《康熙字典•備考》），</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    極少見。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    が“多乎哉？不多也”︰語見《論語•子罕》︰“大宰問于子貢曰︰‘夫子聖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    者與？何其多能也！’子貢曰︰‘固天縱之將聖，又多能也。’子聞之，曰︰‘大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    宰知我乎？吾少也賤，故多能鄙事。’君子多乎哉？不多也。”這里與原意無關。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    き服辯︰又作伏辯，即認罪書。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぎ據本篇發表時的作者《附記》（見注1），本文當作于一九一八年冬天。按︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    本書各篇最初發表時都未署寫作日期，現在篇末的日期為作者在編集時所補記。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p> 藥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    秋天的後半夜，月亮下去了，太陽還沒有出，只剩下一片烏藍的天；除了夜游</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的東西，什麼都睡著。華老栓忽然坐起身，擦著火柴，點上遍身油膩的燈盞，茶館</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的兩間屋子里，便彌滿了青白的光。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “小栓的爹，你就去麼？”是一個老女人的聲音。里邊的小屋子里，也發出一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    陣咳嗽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “唔。”老栓一面听，一面應，一面扣上衣服；伸手過去說，“你給我罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    華大媽在枕頭底下掏了半天，掏出一包洋錢え，交給老栓，老栓接了，抖抖的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    裝入衣袋，又在外面按了兩下；便點上燈籠，吹熄燈盞，走向里屋子去了。那屋子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    里面，正在        的響，接著便是一通咳嗽。老栓候他平靜下去，才低低的叫道，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “小栓……你不要起來。……店麼？你娘會安排的。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老栓听得兒子不再說話，料他安心睡了；便出了門，走到街上。街上黑沉沉的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一無所有，只有一條灰白的路，看得分明。燈光照著他的兩腳，一前一後的走。有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    時也遇到幾只狗，可是一只也沒有叫。天氣比屋子里冷多了；老栓倒覺爽快，仿佛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一旦變了少年，得了神通，有給人生命的本領似的，跨步格外高遠。而且路也愈走</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    愈分明，天也愈走愈亮了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老栓正在專心走路，忽然吃了一驚，遠遠里看見一條丁字街，明明白白橫著。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他便退了幾步，尋到一家關著門的鋪子，蹩進檐下，靠門立住了。好一會，身上覺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    得有些發冷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “哼，老頭子。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “倒高興……。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老栓又吃一驚，睜眼看時，幾個人從他面前過去了。一個還回頭看他，樣子不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    甚分明，但很像久餓的人見了食物一般，眼里閃出一種攫取的光。老栓看看燈籠，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    已經熄了。按一按衣袋，硬硬的還在。仰起頭兩面一望，只見許多古怪的人，三三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    兩兩，鬼似的在那里徘徊；定楮再看，卻也看不出什麼別的奇怪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    沒有多久，又見幾個兵，在那邊走動；衣服前後的一個大白圓圈，遠地里也看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    得清楚，走過面前的，並且看出號衣ぉ上暗紅的瓖邊。——一陣腳步聲響，一眨眼，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    已經擁過了一大簇人。那三三兩兩的人，也忽然合作一堆，潮一般向前進；將到丁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    字街口，便突然立住，簇成一個半圓。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老栓也向那邊看，卻只見一堆人的後背；頸項都伸得很長，仿佛許多鴨，被無</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    形的手捏住了的，向上提著。靜了一會，似乎有點聲音，便又動搖起來，轟的一聲，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都向後退；一直散到老栓立著的地方，幾乎將他擠倒了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “喂！一手交錢，一手交貨！”一個渾身黑色的人，站在老栓面前，眼光正像</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    兩把刀，刺得老栓縮小了一半。那人一只大手，向他攤著；一只手卻撮著一個鮮紅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的饅頭お，那紅的還是一點一點的往下滴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老栓慌忙摸出洋錢，抖抖的想交給他，卻又不敢去接他的東西。那人便焦急起</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來，嚷道，“怕什麼？怎的不拿！”老栓還躊躇著；黑的人便搶過燈籠，一把扯下</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    紙罩，裹了饅頭，塞與老栓；一手抓過洋錢，捏一捏，轉身去了。嘴里哼著說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這老東西……。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這給誰治病的呀？”老栓也似乎听得有人問他，但他並不答應；他的精神，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    現在只在一個包上，仿佛抱著一個十世單傳的嬰兒，別的事情，都已置之度外了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他現在要將這包里的新的生命，移植到他家里，收獲許多幸福。太陽也出來了；在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他面前，顯出一條大道，直到他家中，後面也照見丁字街頭破匾上“古□亭口”這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    四個黯淡的金字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老栓走到家，店面早經收拾干淨，一排一排的茶桌，滑溜溜的發光。但是沒有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    客人；只有小栓坐在里排的桌前吃飯，大粒的汗，從額上滾下，夾襖也帖住了脊心，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    兩塊肩胛骨高高凸出，印成一個陽文的“八”字。老栓見這樣子，不免皺一皺展開</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的眉心。他的女人，從灶下急急走出，睜著眼楮，嘴唇有些發抖。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “得了麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “得了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    兩個人一齊走進灶下，商量了一會；華大媽便出去了，不多時，拿著一片老荷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    葉回來，攤在桌上。老栓也打開燈籠罩，用荷葉重新包了那紅的饅頭。小栓也吃完</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    飯，他的母親慌忙說︰“小栓——你坐著，不要到這里來。”一面整頓了灶火，老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    栓便把一個碧綠的包，一個紅紅白白的破燈籠，一同塞在灶里；一陣紅黑的火焰過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    去時，店屋里散滿了一種奇怪的香味。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “好香！你們吃什麼點心呀？”這是駝背五少爺到了。這人每天總在茶館里過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    日，來得最早，去得最遲，此時恰恰蹩到臨街的壁角的桌邊，便坐下問話，然而沒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有人答應他。“炒米粥麼？”仍然沒有人應。老栓匆匆走出，給他泡上茶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “小栓進來罷！”華大媽叫小栓進了里面的屋子，中間放好一條凳，小栓坐了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他的母親端過一碟烏黑的圓東西，輕輕說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “吃下去罷，——病便好了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    小栓撮起這黑東西，看了一會，似乎拿著自己的性命一般，心里說不出的奇怪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    十分小心的拗開了，焦皮里面竄出一道白氣，白氣散了，是兩半個白面的饅頭。—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    —不多工夫，已經全在肚里了，卻全忘了什麼味；面前只剩下一張空盤。他的旁邊，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一面立著他的父親，一面立著他的母親，兩人的眼光，都仿佛要在他身上注進什麼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    又要取出什麼似的；便禁不住心跳起來，按著胸膛，又是一陣咳嗽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “睡一會罷，——便好了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    小栓依他母親的話，咳著睡了。華大媽候他喘氣平靜，才輕輕的給他蓋上了滿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    幅補釘的夾被。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    店里坐著許多人，老栓也忙了，提著大銅壺，一趟一趟的給客人沖茶；兩個眼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    眶，都圍著一圈黑線。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “老栓，你有些不舒服麼？——你生病麼？”一個花白胡子的人說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “沒有。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “沒有？——我想笑嘻嘻的，原也不像……”花白胡子便取消了自己的話。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “老栓只是忙。要是他的兒子……”駝背五少爺話還未完，突然闖進了一個滿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    臉橫肉的人，披一件玄色布衫，散著紐扣，用很寬的玄色腰帶，胡亂捆在腰間。剛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    進門，便對老栓嚷道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “吃了麼？好了麼？老栓，就是運氣了你！你運氣，要不是我信息靈……。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老栓一手提了茶壺，一手恭恭敬敬的垂著；笑嘻嘻的听。滿座的人，也都恭恭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    敬敬的听。華大媽也黑著眼眶，笑嘻嘻的送出茶碗茶葉來，加上一個橄欖，老栓便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    去沖了水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這是包好！這是與眾不同的。你想，趁熱的拿來，趁熱的吃下。”橫肉的人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    只是嚷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “真的呢，要沒有康大叔照顧，怎麼會這樣……”華大媽也很感激的謝他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “包好，包好！這樣的趁熱吃下。這樣的人血饅頭，什麼癆病都包好！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    華大媽听到“癆病”這兩個字，變了一點臉色，似乎有些不高興；但又立刻堆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    上笑，搭訕著走開了。這康大叔卻沒有覺察，仍然提高了喉嚨只是嚷，嚷得里面睡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    著的小栓也合伙咳嗽起來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “原來你家小栓踫到了這樣的好運氣了。這病自然一定全好；怪不得老栓整天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的笑著呢。”花白胡子一面說，一面走到康大叔面前，低聲下氣的問道，“康大叔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ——听說今天結果的一個犯人，便是夏家的孩子，那是誰的孩子？究竟是什麼事？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “誰的？不就是夏四奶奶的兒子麼？那個小家伙！”康大叔見眾人都聳起耳朵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    听他，便格外高興，橫肉塊塊飽綻，越發大聲說，“這小東西不要命，不要就是了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我可是這一回一點沒有得到好處；連剝下來的衣服，都給管牢的紅眼楮阿義拿去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ——第一要算我們栓叔運氣；第二是夏三爺賞了二十五兩雪白的銀子，獨自落腰包，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一文不花。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    小栓慢慢的從小屋子里走出，兩手按了胸口，不住的咳嗽；走到灶下，盛出一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    碗冷飯，泡上熱水，坐下便吃。華大媽跟著他走，輕輕的問道，“小栓，你好些麼？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ——你仍舊只是肚餓？……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “包好，包好！”康大叔瞥了小栓一眼，仍然回過臉，對眾人說，“夏三爺真</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是乖角兒，要是他不先告官，連他滿門抄斬。現在怎樣？銀子！——這小東西也真</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不成東西！關在勞里，還要勸勞頭造反。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “阿呀，那還了得。”坐在後排的一個二十多歲的人，很現出氣憤模樣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你要曉得紅眼楮阿義是去盤盤底細的，他卻和他攀談了。他說︰這大清的天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    下是我們大家的。你想︰這是人話麼？紅眼楮原知道他家里只有一個老娘，可是沒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有料到他竟會這麼窮，榨不出一點油水，已經氣破肚皮了。他還要老虎頭上搔癢，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便給他兩個嘴巴！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “義哥是一手好拳棒，這兩下，一定夠他受用了。”壁角的駝背忽然高興起來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “他這賤骨頭打不怕，還要說可憐可憐哩。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    花白胡子的人說，“打了這種東西，有什麼可憐呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    康大叔顯出看他不上的樣子，冷笑著說，“你沒有听清我的話；看他神氣，是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    說阿義可憐哩！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    听著的人的眼光，忽然有些板滯；話也停頓了。小栓已經吃完飯，吃得滿頭流</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    汗，頭上都冒出蒸氣來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “阿義可憐——瘋話，簡直是發了瘋了。”花白胡子恍然大悟似的說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “發了瘋了。”二十多歲的人也恍然大悟的說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    店里的坐客，便又現出活氣，談笑起來。小栓也趁著熱鬧，拚命咳嗽；康大叔</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    走上前，拍他肩膀說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “包好！小栓——你不要這麼咳。包好！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “瘋了。”駝背五少爺點著頭說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    四</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    西關外靠著城根的地面，本是一塊官地；中間歪歪斜斜一條細路，是貪走便道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的人，用鞋底造成的，但卻成了自然的界限。路的左邊，都埋著死刑和瘐斃的人，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    右邊是窮人的叢冢。兩面都已埋到層層疊疊，宛然闊人家里祝壽時的饅頭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這一年的清明，分外寒冷；楊柳才吐出半粒米大的新芽。天明未久，華大媽已</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在右邊的一坐新墳前面，排出四碟菜，一碗飯，哭了一場。化過紙か，呆呆的坐在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    地上；仿佛等候什麼似的，但自己也說不出等候什麼。微風起來，吹動他短發，確</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    乎比去年白得多了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    小路上又來了一個女人，也是半白頭發，襤褸的衣裙；提一個破舊的朱漆圓籃，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    外掛一串紙錠，三步一歇的走。忽然見華大媽坐在地上看他，便有些躊躇，慘白的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    臉上，現出些羞愧的顏色；但終于硬著頭皮，走到左邊的一坐墳前，放下了籃子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那墳與小栓的墳，一字兒排著，中間只隔一條小路。華大媽看他排好四碟菜，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一碗飯，立著哭了一通，化過紙錠；心里暗暗地想，“這墳里的也是兒子了。”那</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老女人徘徊觀望了一回，忽然手腳有些發抖，蹌蹌踉踉退下幾步，瞪著眼只是發怔。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    華大媽見這樣子，生怕他傷心到快要發狂了；便忍不住立起身，跨過小路，低</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    聲對他說，“你這位老奶奶不要傷心了，——我們還是回去罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那人點一點頭，眼楮仍然向上瞪著；也低聲吃吃的說道，“你看，——看這是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    什麼呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    華大媽跟了他指頭看去，眼光便到了前面的墳，這墳上草根還沒有全合，露出</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一塊一塊的黃土，煞是難看。再往上仔細看時，卻不覺也吃一驚；——分明有一圈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    紅白的花，圍著那尖圓的墳頂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們的眼楮都已老花多年了，但望這紅白的花，卻還能明白看見。花也不很多，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    圓圓的排成一個圈，不很精神，倒也整齊。華大媽忙看他兒子和別人的墳，卻只有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不怕冷的幾點青白小花，零星開著；便覺得心里忽然感到一種不足和空虛，不願意</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    根究。那老女人又走近幾步，細看了一遍，自言自語的說，“這沒有根，不像自己</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    開的。——這地方有誰來呢？孩子不會來玩；——親戚本家早不來了。——這是怎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    麼一回事呢？”他想了又想，忽又流下淚來，大聲說道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “瑜兒，他們都冤枉了你，你還是忘不了，傷心不過，今天特意顯點靈，要我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    知道麼？”他四面一看，只見一只烏鴉，站在一株沒有葉的樹上，便接著說，“我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    知道了。——瑜兒，可憐他們坑了你，他們將來總有報應，天都知道；你閉了眼楮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    就是了。——你如果真在這里，听到我的話，——便教這烏鴉飛上你的墳頂，給我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    看罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    微風早經停息了；枯草支支直立，有如銅絲。一絲發抖的聲音，在空氣中愈顫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    愈細，細到沒有，周圍便都是死一般靜。兩人站在枯草叢里，仰面看那烏鴉；那烏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    鴉也在筆直的樹枝間，縮著頭，鐵鑄一般站著。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    許多的工夫過去了；上墳的人漸漸增多，幾個老的小的，在土墳間出沒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    華大媽不知怎的，似乎卸下了一挑重擔，便想到要走；一面勸著說，“我們還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是回去罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那老女人嘆一口氣，無精打采的收起飯菜；又遲疑了一刻，終于慢慢地走了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    嘴里自言自語的說，“這是怎麼一回事呢？……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們走不上二三十步遠，忽听得背後“啞——”的一聲大叫；兩個人都悚然的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    回過頭，只見那烏鴉張開兩翅，一挫身，直向著遠處的天空，箭也似的飛去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一九一九年四月。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九一九年五月《新青年》第六卷第五號。按︰篇中人物夏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    瑜隱喻清末女革命黨人秋瑾。秋瑾在徐錫麟被害後不久，也于一九○七年七月十五</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    日遭清政府殺害，就義的地點在紹興軒亭口。軒亭口是紹興城內的大街，街旁有一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    牌樓，匾上題有“古軒亭口”四字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え洋錢︰指銀元。銀元最初是從外國流入我國的，所以俗稱洋錢；我國自清代</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    後期開始自鑄銀元，但民間仍沿用這個舊稱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ號衣︰指清朝士兵的軍衣，前後胸都綴有一塊圓形白布，上有“兵”或“勇”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    字樣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お鮮紅的饅頭︰即蘸有人血的饅頭。舊時迷信，以為人血可以醫治肺癆，劊子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    手便借此騙取錢財。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か化過紙︰紙指紙錢，一種迷信用品，舊俗認為把它火化後可供死者在“陰間”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    使用。下文說的紙錠，是用紙或錫箔折成的元寶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5> 阿Q正傳</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第一章序</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    我要給阿Q做正傳，已經不止一兩年了。但一面要做，一面又往回想，這足見我</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不是一個“立言”え的人，因為從來不朽之筆，須傳不朽之人，于是人以文傳，文</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    以人傳——究竟誰靠誰傳，漸漸的不甚了然起來，而終于歸接到傳阿Q，仿佛思想里</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有鬼似的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然而要做這一篇速朽的文章，才下筆，便感到萬分的困難了。第一是文章的名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    目。孔子曰，“名不正則言不順”ぉ。這原是應該極注意的。傳的名目很繁多︰列</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    傳，自傳，內傳お，外傳，別傳，家傳，小傳……，而可惜都不合。“列傳”麼，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    這一篇並非和許多闊人排在“正史”か里；“自傳”麼，我又並非就是阿Q。說是</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “外傳”，“內傳”在那里呢？倘用“內傳”，阿Q又決不是神仙。“別傳”呢，阿</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    Q實在未曾有大總統上諭宣付國史館立“本傳”が——雖說英國正史上並無“博徒列</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    傳”，而文豪迭更司き也做過《博徒別傳》這一部書，但文豪則可，在我輩卻不可。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    其次是“家傳”，則我既不知與阿Q是否同宗，也未曾受他子孫的拜托；或“小傳”，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    則阿Q又更無別的“大傳”了。總而言之，這一篇也便是“本傳”，但從我的文章著</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    想，因為文體卑下，是“引車賣漿者流”所用的話ぎ，所以不敢僭稱，便從不入三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    教九流的小說家く所謂“閑話休題言歸正傳”這一句套話里，取出“正傳”兩個字</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來，作為名目，即使與古人所撰《書法正傳》ぐ的“正傳”字面上很相混，也顧不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    得了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第二，立傳的通例，開首大抵該是“某，字某，某地人也”，而我並不知道阿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    Q姓什麼。有一回，他似乎是姓趙，但第二日便模糊了。那是趙太爺的兒子進了秀才</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    的時候，鑼聲鏜鏜的報到村里來，阿Q正喝了兩碗黃酒，便手舞足蹈的說，這于他也</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    很光采，因為他和趙太爺原來是本家，細細的排起來他還比秀才長三輩呢。其時幾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    個旁听人倒也肅然的有些起敬了。那知道第二天，地保便叫阿Q到趙太爺家里去；太</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    爺一見，滿臉濺朱，喝道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “阿Q，你這渾小子！你說我是你的本家麼？”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q不開口。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    趙太爺愈看愈生氣了，搶進幾步說︰“你敢胡說！我怎麼會有你這樣的本家？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    你姓趙麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q不開口，想往後退了；趙太爺跳過去，給了他一個嘴巴。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你怎麼會姓趙！——你那里配姓趙！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q並沒有抗辯他確鑿姓趙，只用手摸著左頰，和地保退出去了；外面又被地保</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    訓斥了一番，謝了地保二百文酒錢。知道的人都說阿Q太荒唐，自己去招打；他大約</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    未必姓趙，即使真姓趙，有趙太爺在這里，也不該如此胡說的。此後便再沒有人提</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    起他的氏族來，所以我終于不知道阿Q究竟什麼姓。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第三，我又不知道阿Q的名字是怎麼寫的。他活著的時候，人都叫他阿Quei，死</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了以後，便沒有一個人再叫阿Quei了，那里還會有“著之竹帛”　的事。若論“著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    之竹帛”，這篇文章要算第一次，所以先遇著了這第一個難關。我曾仔細想︰阿Qu</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ei，阿桂還是阿貴呢？倘使他號月亭，或者在八月間做過生日，那一定是阿桂了；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而他既沒有號——也許有號，只是沒有人知道他，——又未嘗散過生日征文的帖子︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    寫作阿桂，是武斷的。又倘使他有一位老兄或令弟叫阿富，那一定是阿貴了；而他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    又只是一個人︰寫作阿貴，也沒有佐證的。其余音Quei的偏僻字樣，更加湊不上了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    先前，我也曾問過趙太爺的兒子茂才　先生，誰料博雅如此公，竟也茫然，但據結</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    論說，是因為陳獨秀辦了《新青年》提倡洋字　，所以國粹淪亡，無可查考了。我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    的最後的手段，只有托一個同鄉去查阿Q犯事的案卷，八個月之後才有回信，說案卷</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    里並無與阿Quei的聲音相近的人。我雖不知道是真沒有，還是沒有查，然而也再沒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有別的方法了。生怕注音字母還未通行，只好用了“洋字”，照英國流行的拼法寫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他為阿Quei，略作阿Q。這近于盲從《新青年》，自己也很抱歉，但茂才公尚且不知，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我還有什麼好辦法呢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    第四，是阿Q的籍貫了。倘他姓趙，則據現在好稱郡望的老例，可以照《郡名百</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    家姓》　上的注解，說是“隴西天水人也”，但可惜這姓是不甚可靠的，因此籍貫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也就有些決不定。他雖然多住未莊，然而也常常宿在別處，不能說是未莊人，即使</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    說是“未莊人也”，也仍然有乖史法的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我所聊以自慰的，是還有一個“阿”字非常正確，絕無附會假借的缺點，頗可</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    以就正于通人。至于其余，卻都非淺學所能穿鑿，只希望有“歷史癖與考據癖”的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    胡適之　先生的門人們，將來或者能夠尋出許多新端緒來，但是我這《阿Q正傳》到</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那時卻又怕早經消滅了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    以上可以算是序。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第二章優勝記略</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q不獨是姓名籍貫有些渺茫，連他先前的“行狀”　也渺茫。因為未莊的人們</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    之于阿Q，只要他幫忙，只拿他玩笑，從來沒有留心他的“行狀”的。而阿Q自己也</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不說，獨有和別人口角的時候，間或瞪著眼楮道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我們先前——比你闊的多啦！你算是什麼東西！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q沒有家，住在未莊的土谷祠　里；也沒有固定的職業，只給人家做短工，割</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    麥便割麥，舂米便舂米，撐船便撐船。工作略長久時，他也或住在臨時主人的家里，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    但一完就走了。所以，人們忙碌的時候，也還記起阿Q來，然而記起的是做工，並不</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    是“行狀”；一閑空，連阿Q都早忘卻，更不必說“行狀”了。只是有一回，有一個</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    老頭子頌揚說︰“阿Q真能做！”這時阿Q赤著膊，懶洋洋的瘦伶仃的正在他面前，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    別人也摸不著這話是真心還是譏笑，然而阿Q很喜歡。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q又很自尊，所有未莊的居民，全不在他眼神里，甚而至于對于兩位“文童”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　也有以為不值一笑的神情。夫文童者，將來恐怕要變秀才者也；趙太爺錢太爺大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    受居民的尊敬，除有錢之外，就因為都是文童的爹爹，而阿Q在精神上獨不表格外的</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    崇奉，他想︰我的兒子會闊得多啦！加以進了幾回城，阿Q自然更自負，然而他又很</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    鄙薄城里人，譬如用三尺三寸寬的木板做成的凳子，未莊人叫“長凳”，他也叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “長凳”，城里人卻叫“條凳”，他想︰這是錯的，可笑！油煎大頭魚，未莊都加</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    上半寸長的蔥葉，城里卻加上切細的蔥絲，他想︰這也是錯的，可笑！然而未莊人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    真是不見世面的可笑的鄉下人呵，他們沒有見過城里的煎魚！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q“先前闊”，見識高，而且“真能做”，本來幾乎是一個“完人”了，但可</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    惜他體質上還有一些缺點。最惱人的是在他頭皮上，頗有幾處不知于何時的癩瘡疤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    這雖然也在他身上，而看阿Q的意思，倒也似乎以為不足貴的，因為他諱說“癩”以</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    及一切近于“賴”的音，後來推而廣之，“光”也諱，“亮”也諱，再後來，連</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “燈”“燭”都諱了。一犯諱，不問有心與無心，阿Q便全疤通紅的發起怒來，估量</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    了對手，口訥的他便罵，氣力小的他便打；然而不知怎麼一回事，總還是阿Q吃虧的</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    時候多。于是他漸漸的變換了方針，大抵改為怒目而視了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    誰知道阿Q采用怒目主義之後，未莊的閑人們便愈喜歡玩笑他。一見面，他們便</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    假作吃驚的說︰噲，亮起來了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q照例的發了怒，他怒目而視了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “原來有保險燈在這里！”他們並不怕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q沒有法，只得另外想出報復的話來︰</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你還不配……”這時候，又仿佛在他頭上的是一種高尚的光容的癩頭瘡，並</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    非平常的癩頭瘡了；但上文說過，阿Q是有見識的，他立刻知道和“犯忌”有點抵觸，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便不再往底下說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    閑人還不完，只撩他，于是終而至于打。阿Q在形式上打敗了，被人揪住黃辮子，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    在壁上踫了四五個響頭，閑人這才心滿意足的得勝的走了，阿Q站了一刻，心里想，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我總算被兒子打了，現在的世界真不像樣……”于是也心滿意足的得勝的走了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q想在心里的，後來每每說出口來，所以凡是和阿Q玩笑的人們，幾乎全知道</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他有這一種精神上的勝利法，此後每逢揪住他黃辮子的時候，人就先一著對他說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “阿Q，這不是兒子打老子，是人打畜生。自己說︰人打畜生！”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q兩只手都捏住了自己的辮根，歪著頭，說道︰</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “打蟲豸，好不好？我是蟲豸——還不放麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但雖然是蟲豸，閑人也並不放，仍舊在就近什麼地方給他踫了五六個響頭，這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    才心滿意足的得勝的走了，他以為阿Q這回可遭了瘟。然而不到十秒鐘，阿Q也心滿</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    意足的得勝的走了，他覺得他是第一個能夠自輕自賤的人，除了“自輕自賤”不算</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    外，余下的就是“第一個”。狀元　不也是“第一個”麼？“你算是什麼東西”呢！？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q以如是等等妙法克服怨敵之後，便愉快的跑到酒店里喝幾碗酒，又和別人調</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    笑一通，口角一通，又得了勝，愉快的回到土谷祠，放倒頭睡著了。假使有錢，他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    便去押牌寶　，一推人蹲在地面上，阿Q即汗流滿面的夾在這中間，聲音他最響︰</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “青龍四百！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “咳……開……啦！”樁家揭開盒子蓋，也是汗流滿面的唱。“天門啦……角</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    回啦……！人和穿堂空在那里啦……！阿Q的銅錢拿過來……！”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “穿堂一百——一百五十！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q的錢便在這樣的歌吟之下，漸漸的輸入別個汗流滿面的人物的腰間。他終于</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    只好擠出堆外，站在後面看，替別人著急，一直到散場，然後戀戀的回到土谷祠，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第二天，腫著眼楮去工作。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    但真所謂“塞翁失馬安知非福”ヾ罷，阿Q不幸而贏了一回，他倒幾乎失敗了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這是未莊賽神ゝ的晚上。這晚上照例有一台戲，戲台左近，也照例有許多的賭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    攤。做戲的鑼鼓，在阿Q耳朵里仿佛在十里之外；他只听得樁家的歌唱了。他贏而又</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    贏，銅錢變成角洋，角洋變成大洋，大洋又成了疊。他興高采烈得非常︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “天門兩塊！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他不知道誰和誰為什麼打起架來了。罵聲打聲腳步聲，昏頭昏腦的一大陣，他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    才爬起來，賭攤不見了，人們也不見了，身上有幾處很似乎有些痛，似乎也挨了幾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    拳幾腳似的，幾個人詫異的對他看。他如有所失的走進土谷祠，定一定神，知道他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的一堆洋錢不見了。趕賽會的賭攤多不是本村人，還到那里去尋根柢呢？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    很白很亮的一堆洋錢！而且是他的——現在不見了！說是算被兒子拿去了罷，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    總還是忽忽不樂；說自己是蟲豸罷，也還是忽忽不樂︰他這回才有些感到失敗的苦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    痛了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但他立刻轉敗為勝了。他擎起右手，用力的在自己臉上連打了兩個嘴巴，熱剌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    剌的有些痛；打完之後，便心平氣和起來，似乎打的是自己，被打的是別一個自己，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不久也就仿佛是自己打了別個一般，——雖然還有些熱剌剌，——心滿意足的得勝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的躺下了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他睡著了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第三章續優勝記略</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    然而阿Q雖然常優勝，卻直待蒙趙太爺打他嘴巴之後，這才出了名。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他付過地保二百文酒錢，憤憤的躺下了，後來想︰“現在的世界太不成話，兒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    子打老子……”于是忽而想到趙太爺的威風，而現在是他的兒子了，便自己也漸漸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的得意起來，爬起身，唱著《小孤孀上墳》ゞ到酒店去。這時候，他又覺得趙太爺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    高人一等了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    說也奇怪，從此之後，果然大家也仿佛格外尊敬他。這在阿Q，或者以為因為他</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是趙太爺的父親，而其實也不然。未莊通例，倘如阿七打阿八，或者李四打張三，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    向來本不算口碑。一上口碑，則打的既有名，被打的也就托庇有了名。至于錯在阿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    Q，那自然是不必說。所以者何？就因為趙太爺是不會錯的。但他既然錯，為什麼大</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    家又仿佛格外尊敬他呢？這可難解，穿鑿起來說，或者因為阿Q說是趙太爺的本家，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    雖然挨了打，大家也還怕有些真，總不如尊敬一些穩當。否則，也如孔廟里的太牢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    々一般，雖然與豬羊一樣，同是畜生，但既經聖人下箸，先儒們便不敢妄動了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q此後倒得意了許多年。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有一年的春天，他醉醺醺的在街上走，在牆根的日光下，看見王胡在那里赤著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    膊捉虱子，他忽然覺得身上也癢起來了。這王胡，又癩又胡，別人都叫他王癩胡，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q卻刪去了一個癩字，然而非常渺視他。阿Q的意思，以為癩是不足為奇的，只有</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這一部絡腮胡子，實在太新奇，令人看不上眼。他于是並排坐下去了。倘是別的閑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    人們，阿Q本不敢大意坐下去。但這王胡旁邊，他有什麼怕呢？老實說︰他肯坐下去，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    簡直還是抬舉他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q也脫下破夾襖來，翻檢了一回，不知道因為新洗呢還是因為粗心，許多工夫，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    只捉到三四個。他看那王胡，卻是一個又一個，兩個又三個，只放在嘴里畢畢剝剝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的響。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q最初是失望，後來卻不平了︰看不上眼的王胡尚且那麼多，自己倒反這樣少，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這是怎樣的大失體統的事呵！他很想尋一兩個大的，然而竟沒有，好容易才捉到一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    個中的，恨恨的塞在厚嘴唇里，狠命一咬，劈的一聲，又不及王胡的響。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他癩瘡疤塊塊通紅了，將衣服摔在地上，吐一口唾沫，說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這毛蟲！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “癩皮狗，你罵誰？”王胡輕蔑的抬起眼來說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q近來雖然比較的受人尊敬，自己也更高傲些，但和那些打慣的閑人們見面還</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    膽怯，獨有這回卻非常武勇了。這樣滿臉胡子的東西，也敢出言無狀麼？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “誰認便罵誰！”他站起來，兩手叉在腰間說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你的骨頭癢了麼？”王胡也站起來，披上衣服說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q以為他要逃了，搶進去就是一拳。這拳頭還未達到身上，已經被他抓住了，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    只一拉，阿Q蹌蹌踉踉的跌進去，立刻又被王胡扭住了辮子，要拉到牆上照例去踫頭。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “‘君子動口不動手’！”阿Q歪著頭說。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    王胡似乎不是君子，並不理會，一連給他踫了五下，又用力的一推，至于阿Q跌</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    出六尺多遠，這才滿足的去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    在阿Q的記憶上，這大約要算是生平第一件的屈辱，因為王胡以絡腮胡子的缺點，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    向來只被他奚落，從沒有奚落他，更不必說動手了。而他現在竟動手，很意外，難</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    道真如市上所說，皇帝已經停了考ぁ，不要秀才和舉人了，因此趙家減了威風，因</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    此他們也便小覷了他麼？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q無可適從的站著。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    遠遠的走來了一個人，他的對頭又到了。這也是阿Q最厭惡的一個人，就是錢太</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    爺的大兒子。他先前跑上城里去進洋學堂，不知怎麼又跑到東洋去了，半年之後他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    回到家里來，腿也直了，辮子也不見了，他的母親大哭了十幾場，他的老婆跳了三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    回井。後來，他的母親到處說，“這辮子是被壞人灌醉了酒剪去了。本來可以做大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    官，現在只好等留長再說了。”然而阿Q不肯信，偏稱他“假洋鬼子”，也叫作“里</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    通外國的人”，一見他，一定在肚子里暗暗的咒罵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q尤其“深惡而痛絕之”的，是他的一條假辮子。辮子而至于假，就是沒了做</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    人的資格；他的老婆不跳第四回井，也不是好女人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這“假洋鬼子”近來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    禿兒。驢……”阿Q歷來本只在肚子里罵，沒有出過聲，這回因為正氣忿，因為</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    要報仇，便不由的輕輕的說出來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    不料這禿兒卻拿著一支黃漆的棍子——就是阿Q所謂哭喪棒あ——大蹋步走了過</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    來。阿Q在這剎那，便知道大約要打了，趕緊抽緊筋骨，聳了肩膀等候著，果然，拍</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的一聲，似乎確鑿打在自己頭上了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “我說他！”阿Q指著近旁的一個孩子，分辯說。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    拍！拍拍！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    在阿Q的記憶上，這大約要算是生平第二件的屈辱。幸而拍拍的響了之後，于他</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    倒似乎完結了一件事，反而覺得輕松些，而且“忘卻”這一件祖傳的寶貝也發生了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    效力，他慢慢的走，將到酒店門口，早已有些高興了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    但對面走來了靜修庵里的小尼姑。阿Q便在平時，看見伊也一定要唾罵，而況在</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    屈辱之後呢？他于是發生了回憶，又發生了敵愾了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我不知道我今天為什麼這樣晦氣，原來就因為見了你！”他想。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他迎上去，大聲的吐一口唾沫︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “咳，呸！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    小尼姑全不睬，低了頭只是走。阿Q走近伊身旁，突然伸出手去摩著伊新剃的頭</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    皮，呆笑著，說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “禿兒！快回去，和尚等著你……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你怎麼動手動腳……”尼姑滿臉通紅的說，一面趕快走。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    酒店里的人大笑了。阿Q看見自己的勛業得了賞識，便愈加興高采烈起來︰</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “和尚動得，我動不得？”他扭住伊的面頰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    酒店里的人大笑了。阿Q更得意，而且為了滿足那些賞鑒家起見，再用力的一擰，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    才放手。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他這一戰，早忘卻了王胡，也忘卻了假洋鬼子，似乎對于今天的一切“晦氣”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都報了仇；而且奇怪，又仿佛全身比拍拍的響了之後輕松，飄飄然的似乎要飛去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “這斷子絕孫的阿Q！”遠遠地听得小尼姑的帶哭的聲音。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “哈哈哈！”阿Q十分得意的笑。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “哈哈哈！”酒店里的人也九分得意的笑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第四章戀愛的悲劇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有人說︰有些勝利者，願意敵手如虎，如鷹，他才感得勝利的歡喜；假使如羊，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    如小雞，他便反覺得勝利的無聊。又有些勝利者，當克服一切之後，看見死的死了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    降的降了，“臣誠惶誠恐死罪死罪”，他于是沒有了敵人，沒有了對手，沒有了朋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    友，只有自己在上，一個，孤另另，淒涼，寂寞，便反而感到了勝利的悲哀。然而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    我們的阿Q卻沒有這樣乏，他是永遠得意的︰這或者也是中國精神文明冠于全球的一</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    個證據了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    看哪，他飄飄然的似乎要飛去了！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然而這一次的勝利，卻又使他有些異樣。他飄飄然的飛了大半天，飄進土谷祠，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    照例應該躺下便打鼾。誰知道這一晚，他很不容易合眼，他覺得自己的大拇指和第</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    二指有點古怪︰仿佛比平常滑膩些。不知道是小尼姑的臉上有一點滑膩的東西粘在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他指上，還是他的指頭在小尼姑臉上磨得滑膩了？……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “斷子絕孫的阿Q！”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q的耳朵里又听到這句話。他想︰不錯，應該有一個女人，斷子絕孫便沒有人</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    供一碗飯，……應該有一個女人。夫“不孝有三無後為大”ぃ，而“若敖之鬼餒而”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    い，也是一件人生的大哀，所以他那思想，其實是樣樣合于聖經賢傳的，只可惜後</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來有些“不能收其放心”ぅ了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “女人，女人！……”他想。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “……和尚動得……女人，女人！……女人！”他又想。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    我們不能知道這晚上阿Q在什麼時候才打鼾。但大約他從此總覺得指頭有些滑膩，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    所以他從此總有些飄飄然；“女……”他想。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    即此一端，我們便可以知道女人是害人的東西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    中國的男人，本來大半都可以做聖賢，可惜全被女人毀掉了。商是妲己う鬧亡</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的；周是褒姒弄壞的；秦……雖然史無明文，我們也假定他因為女人，大約未必十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    分錯；而董卓可是的確給貂蟬害死了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q本來也是正人，我們雖然不知道他曾蒙什麼明師指授過，但他對于“男女之</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大防”　卻歷來非常嚴；也很有排斥異端——如小尼姑及假洋鬼子之類——的正氣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他的學說是︰凡尼姑，一定與和尚私通；一個女人在外面走，一定想引誘野男人；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一男一女在那里講話，一定要有勾當了。為懲治他們起見，所以他往往怒目而視，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    或者大聲說幾句“誅心”　話，或者在冷僻處，便從後面擲一塊小石頭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    誰知道他將到“而立”　之年，竟被小尼姑害得飄飄然了。這飄飄然的精神，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    在禮教上是不應該有的，——所以女人真可惡，假使小尼姑的臉上不滑膩，阿Q便不</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    至于被蠱，又假使小尼姑的臉上蓋一層布，阿Q便也不至于被蠱了，——他五六年前，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    曾在戲台下的人叢中擰過一個女人的大腿，但因為隔一層褲，所以此後並不飄飄然，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ——而小尼姑並不然，這也足見異端之可惡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “女……”阿Q想。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他對于以為“一定想引誘野男人”的女人，時常留心看，然而伊並不對他笑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他對于和他講話的女人，也時常留心听，然而伊又並不提起關于什麼勾當的話來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    哦，這也是女人可惡之一節︰伊們全都要裝“假正經”的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    這一天，阿Q在趙太爺家里舂了一天米，吃過晚飯，便坐在廚房里吸旱煙。倘在</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    別家，吃過晚飯本可以回去的了，但趙府上晚飯早，雖說定例不準掌燈，一吃完便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    睡覺，然而偶然也有一些例外︰其一，是趙大爺未進秀才的時候，準其點燈讀文章；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    其二，便是阿Q來做短工的時候，準其點燈舂米。因為這一條例外，所以阿Q在動手</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    舂米之前，還坐在廚房里吸煙旱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    吳媽，是趙太爺家里唯一的女僕，洗完了碗碟，也就在長凳上坐下了，而且和</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q談閑天︰</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “太太兩天沒有吃飯哩，因為老爺要買一個小的……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “女人……吳媽……這小孤孀……”阿Q想。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我們的少奶奶是八月里要生孩子了……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    女人……”阿Q想。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q放下煙管，站了起來。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我們的少奶奶……”吳媽還嘮叨說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “我和你困覺，我和你困覺！”阿Q忽然搶上去，對伊跪下了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一剎時中很寂然。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “阿呀！”吳媽楞了一息，突然發抖，大叫著往外跑，且跑且嚷，似乎後來帶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    哭了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q對了牆壁跪著也發楞，于是兩手扶著空板凳，慢慢的站起來，仿佛覺得有些</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    糟。他這時確也有些忐忑了，慌張的將煙管插在褲帶上，就想去舂米。蓬的一聲，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    頭上著了很粗的一下，他急忙回轉身去，那秀才便拿了一支大竹杠站在他面前。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你反了，……你這……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    大竹杠又向他劈下來了。阿Q兩手去抱頭，拍的正打在指節上，這可很有些痛。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他沖出廚房門，仿佛背上又著了一下似的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “忘八蛋！”秀才在後面用了官話這樣罵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q奔入舂米場，一個人站著，還覺得指頭痛，還記得“忘八蛋”，因為這話是</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    未莊的鄉下人從來不用，專是見過官府的闊人用的，所以格外怕，而印象也格外深。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但這時，他那“女……”的思想卻也沒有了。而且打罵之後，似乎一件事也已經收</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    束，倒反覺得一無掛礙似的，便動手去舂米。舂了一會，他熱起來了，又歇了手脫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    衣服。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    脫下衣服的時候，他听得外面很熱鬧，阿Q生平本來最愛看熱鬧，便即尋聲走出</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    去了。尋聲漸漸的尋到趙太爺的內院里，雖然在昏黃中，卻辨得出許多人，趙府一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    家連兩日不吃飯的太太也在內，還有間壁的鄒七嫂，真正本家的趙白眼，趙司晨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    少奶奶正拖著吳媽走出下房來，一面說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你到外面來，……不要躲在自己房里想……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “誰不知道你正經，……短見是萬萬尋不得的。”鄒七嫂也從旁說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    吳媽只是哭，夾些話，卻不甚听得分明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q想︰“哼，有趣，這小孤孀不知道鬧著什麼玩意兒了？”他想打听，走近趙</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    司晨的身邊。這時他猛然間看見趙大爺向他奔來，而且手里捏著一支大竹杠。他看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    見這一支大竹杠，便猛然間悟到自己曾經被打，和這一場熱鬧似乎有點相關。他翻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    身便走，想逃回舂米場，不圖這支竹杠阻了他的去路，于是他又翻身便走，自然而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然的走出後門，不多工夫，已在土谷祠內了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q坐了一會，皮膚有些起粟，他覺得冷了，因為雖在春季，而夜間頗有余寒，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    尚不宜于赤膊。他也記得布衫留在趙家，但倘若去取，又深怕秀才的竹杠。然而地</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    保進來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “阿Q，你的媽媽的！你連趙家的用人都調戲起來，簡直是造反。害得我晚上沒</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有覺睡，你的媽媽的！……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    如是雲雲的教訓了一通，阿Q自然沒有話。臨末，因為在晚上，應該送地保加倍</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    酒錢四百文，Q正沒有現錢，便用一頂氈帽做抵押，並且訂定了五條件︰</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一明天用紅燭——要一斤重的——一對，香一封，到趙府上去賠罪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    二趙府上請道士祓除縊鬼，費用由阿Q負擔。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    三阿Q從此不準踏進趙府的門檻。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    四吳媽此後倘有不測，惟阿Q是問。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    五阿Q不準再去索取工錢和布衫。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q自然都答應了，可惜沒有錢。幸而已經春天，棉被可以無用，便質了二千大</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    錢，履行條約。赤膊磕頭之後，居然還剩幾文，他也不再贖氈帽，統統喝了酒了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但趙家也並不燒香點燭，因為太太拜佛的時候可以用，留著了。那破布衫是大半做</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了少奶奶八月間生下來的孩子的襯尿布，那小半破爛的便都做了吳媽的鞋底。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第五章生計問題</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q禮畢之後，仍舊回到土谷祠，太陽下去了，漸漸覺得世上有些古怪。他仔細</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一想，終于省悟過來︰其原因蓋在自己的赤膊。他記得破夾襖還在，便披在身上，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    躺倒了，待張開眼楮，原來太陽又已經照在西牆上頭了。他坐起身，一面說道，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “媽媽的……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他起來之後，也仍舊在街上逛，雖然不比赤膊之有切膚之痛，卻又漸漸的覺得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    世上有些古怪了。仿佛從這一天起，未莊的女人們忽然都怕了羞，伊們一見阿Q走來，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便個個躲進門里去。甚而至于將近五十歲的鄒七嫂，也跟著別人亂鑽，而且將十一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    的女兒都叫進去了。阿Q很以為奇，而且想︰“這些東西忽然都學起小姐模樣來了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這娼婦們……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但他更覺得世上有些古怪，卻是許多日以後的事。其一，酒店不肯賒欠了；其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    二，管土谷祠的老頭子說些廢話，似乎叫他走；其三，他雖然記不清多少日，但確</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    乎有許多日，沒有一個人來叫他做短工。酒店不賒，熬著也罷了；老頭子催他走，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    嚕甦一通也就算了；只是沒有人來叫他做短工，卻使阿Q肚子餓︰這委實是一件非常</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “媽媽的”的事情。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q忍不下去了，他只好到老主顧的家里去探問，——但獨不許踏進趙府的門檻，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ——然而情形也異樣︰一定走出一個男人來，現了十分煩厭的相貌，像回復乞丐一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    般的搖手道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “沒有沒有！你出去！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q愈覺得稀奇了。他想，這些人家向來少不了要幫忙，不至于現在忽然都無事，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這總該有些蹊蹺在里面了。他留心打听，才知道他們有事都去叫小Don　。這小D，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    是一個窮小子，又瘦又乏，在阿Q的眼楮里，位置是在王胡之下的，誰料這小子竟謀</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    了他的飯碗去。所以阿Q這一氣，更與平常不同，當氣憤憤的走著的時候，忽然將手</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一揚，唱道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我手執鋼鞭將你打！　……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    幾天之後，他竟在錢府的照壁前遇見了小D。“仇人相見分外眼明”，阿Q便迎</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    上去，小D也站住了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “畜生！”阿Q怒目而視的說，嘴角上飛出唾沫來。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “我是蟲豸，好麼？……”小D說。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    這謙遜反使阿Q更加憤怒起來，但他手里沒有鋼鞭，于是只得撲上去，伸手去拔</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    小D的辮子。小D一手護住了自己的辮根，一手也來拔阿Q的辮子，阿Q便也將空著的</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    一只手護住了自己的辮根。從先前的阿Q看來，，小D本來是不足齒數的，但他近來</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    挨了餓，又瘦又乏已經不下于小D，所以便成了勢均力敵的現象，四只手拔著兩顆頭，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都彎了腰，在錢家粉牆上映出一個藍色的虹形，至于半點鐘之久了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “好了，好了！”看的人們說，大約是解勸的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “好，好！”看的人們說，不知道是解勸，是頌揚，還是煽動。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    然而他們都不听。阿Q進三步，小D便退三步，都站著；小D進三步，阿Q便退三</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    步，又都站著。大約半點鐘，——未莊少有自鳴鐘，所以很難說，或者二十分，—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    —他們的頭發里便都冒煙，額上便都流汗，阿Q的手放松了，在同一瞬間，小D的手</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也正放松了，同時直起，同時退開，都擠出人叢去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “記著罷，媽媽的……”阿Q回過頭去說。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “媽媽的，記著罷……”小D也回過頭來說。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這一場“龍虎斗”似乎並無勝敗，也不知道看的人可滿足，都沒有發什麼議論，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    而阿Q卻仍然沒有人來叫他做短工。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    有一日很溫和，微風拂拂的頗有些夏意了，阿Q卻覺得寒冷起來，但這還可擔當，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第一倒是肚子餓。棉被，氈帽，布衫，早已沒有了，其次就賣了棉襖；現在有褲子，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻萬不可脫的；有破夾襖，又除了送人做鞋底之外，決定賣不出錢。他早想在路上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    拾得一注錢，但至今還沒有見；他想在自己的破屋里忽然尋到一注錢，慌張的四顧，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但屋內是空虛而且了然。于是他決計出門求食去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他在路上走著要“求食”，看見熟識的酒店，看見熟識的饅頭，但他都走過了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不但沒有暫停，而且並不想要。他所求的不是這類東西了；他求的是什麼東西，他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    自己不知道。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    未莊本不是大村鎮，不多時便走盡了。村外多是水田，滿眼是新秧的嫩綠，夾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    著幾個圓形的活動的黑點，便是耕田的農夫。阿Q並不賞鑒這田家樂，卻只是走，因</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    為他直覺的知道這與他的“求食”之道是很遼遠的。但他終于走到靜修庵的牆外了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    庵周圍也是水田，粉牆突出在新綠里，後面的低土牆里是菜園。阿Q遲疑了一會，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    四面一看，並沒有人。他便爬上這矮牆去，扯著何首烏藤，但泥土仍然簌簌的掉，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q的腳也索索的抖；終于攀著桑樹枝，跳到里面了。里面真是郁郁蔥蔥，但似乎並</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    沒有黃酒饅頭，以及此外可吃的之類。靠西牆是竹叢，下面許多筍，只可惜都是並</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    未煮熟的，還有油菜早經結子，芥菜已將開花，小白菜也很老了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q仿佛文童落第似的覺得很冤屈，他慢慢走近園門去，忽而非常驚喜了，這分</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    明是一畦老蘿卜。他于是蹲下便拔，而門口突然伸出一個很圓的頭來，又即縮回去</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    了，這分明是小尼姑。小尼姑之流是阿Q本來視若草芥的，但世事須“退一步想”，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    所以他便趕緊拔起四個蘿卜，擰下青葉，兜在大襟里。然而老尼姑已經出來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “阿彌陀佛，阿Q，你怎麼跳進園里來偷蘿卜！……阿呀，罪過呵，阿唷，阿彌</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    陀佛！……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “我什麼時候跳進你的園里來偷蘿卜？”阿Q且看且走的說。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “現在……這不是？”老尼姑指著他的衣兜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這是你的？你能叫得他答應你麼？你……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q沒有說完話，拔步便跑；追來的是一匹很肥大的黑狗。這本來在前門的，不</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    知怎的到後園來了。黑狗哼而且追，已經要咬著阿Q的腿，幸而從衣兜里落下一個蘿</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    卜來，那狗給一嚇，略略一停，阿Q已經爬上桑樹，跨到土牆，連人和蘿卜都滾出牆</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    外面了。只剩著黑狗還在對著桑樹嗥，老尼姑念著佛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q怕尼姑又放出黑狗來，拾起蘿卜便走，沿路又撿了幾塊小石頭，但黑狗卻並</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    不再現。阿Q于是拋了石塊，一面走一面吃，而且想道，這里也沒有什麼東西尋，不</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    如進城去……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    待三個蘿卜吃完時，他已經打定了進城的主意了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第六章從中興到末路</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    在未莊再看見阿Q出現的時候，是剛過了這年的中秋。人們都驚異，說是阿Q回</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    來了，于是又回上去想道，他先前那里去了呢？阿Q前幾回的上城，大抵早就興高采</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    烈的對人說，但這一次卻並不，所以也沒有一個人留心到。他或者也曾告訴過管土</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    谷祠的老頭子，然而未莊老例，只有趙太爺錢太爺和秀才大爺上城才算一件事。假</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    洋鬼子尚且不足數，何況是阿Q︰因此老頭子也就不替他宣傳，而未莊的社會上也就</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    無從知道了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    但阿Q這回的回來，卻與先前大不同，確乎很值得驚異。天色將黑，他睡眼蒙朧</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的在酒店門前出現了，他走近櫃台，從腰間伸出手來，滿把是銀的和銅的，在櫃上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一扔說，“現錢！打酒來！”穿的是新夾襖，看去腰間還掛著一個大搭連，沉鈿鈿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的將褲帶墜成了很彎很彎的弧線。未莊老例，看見略有些醒目的人物，是與其慢也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    寧敬的，現在雖然明知道是阿Q，但因為和破夾襖的阿Q有些兩樣了，古人雲，“士</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    別三日便當刮目相待”　，所以堂倌，掌櫃，酒客，路人，便自然顯出一種凝而且</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    敬的形態來。掌櫃既先之以點頭，又繼之以談話︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “豁，阿Q，你回來了！”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “回來了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “發財發財，你是——在……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “上城去了！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    這一件新聞，第二天便傳遍了全未莊。人人都願意知道現錢和新夾襖的阿Q的中</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    興史，所以在酒店里，茶館里，廟檐下，便漸漸的探听出來了。這結果，是阿Q得了</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    新敬畏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    據阿Q說，他是在舉人老爺家里幫忙。這一節，听的人都肅然了。這老爺本姓白，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但因為合城里只有他一個舉人，所以不必再冠姓，說起舉人來就是他。這也不獨在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    未莊是如此，便是一百里方圓之內也都如此，人們幾乎多以為他的姓名就叫舉人老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    爺的了。在這人的府上幫忙，那當然是可敬的。但據阿Q又說，他卻不高興再幫忙了，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    因為這舉人老爺實在太“媽媽的”了。這一節，听的人都嘆息而且快意，因為阿Q本</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不配在舉人老爺家里幫忙，而不幫忙是可惜的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    據阿Q說，他的回來，似乎也由于不滿意城里人，這就在他們將長凳稱為條凳，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而且煎魚用蔥絲，加以最近觀察所得的缺點，是女人的走路也扭得不很好。然而也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    偶有大可佩服的地方，即如未莊的鄉下人不過打三十二張的竹牌　，只有假洋鬼子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    能夠叉“麻醬”，城里卻連小烏龜子都叉得精熟的。什麼假洋鬼子，只要放在城里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的十幾歲的小烏龜子的手里，也就立刻是“小鬼見閻王”。這一節，听的人都赧然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “你們可看見過殺頭麼？”阿Q說，“咳，好看。殺革命黨。唉，好看好看，……”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    他搖搖頭，將唾沫飛在正對面的趙司晨的臉上。這一節，听的人都凜然了。但阿Q又</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    四面一看，忽然揚起右手，照著伸長脖子听得出神的王胡的後項窩上直劈下去道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “嚓！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    王胡驚得一跳，同時電光石火似的趕快縮了頭，而听的人又都悚然而且欣然了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    從此王胡瘟頭瘟腦的許多日，並且再不敢走近阿Q的身邊；別的人也一樣。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q這時在未莊人眼楮里的地位，雖不敢說超過趙太爺，但謂之差不多，大約也</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    就沒有什麼語病的了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    然而不多久，這阿Q的大名忽又傳遍了未莊的閨中。雖然未莊只有錢趙兩姓是大</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    屋，此外十之九都是淺閨，但閨中究竟是閨中，所以也算得一件神異。女人們見面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    時一定說，鄒七嫂在阿Q那里買了一條藍綢裙，舊固然是舊的，但只化了九角錢。還</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有趙白眼的母親，——一說是趙司晨的母親，待考，——也買了一件孩子穿的大紅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    洋紗衫，七成新，只用三百大錢九二串　。于是伊們都眼巴巴的想見阿Q，缺綢裙的</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    想問他買綢裙，要洋紗衫的想問他買洋紗衫，不但見了不逃避，有時阿Q已經走過了，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也還要追上去叫住他，問道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “阿Q，你還有綢裙麼？沒有？紗衫也要的，有罷？”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    後來這終于從淺閨傳進深閨里去了。因為鄒七嫂得意之余，將伊的綢裙請趙太</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    太去鑒賞，趙太太又告訴了趙太爺而且著實恭維了一番。趙太爺便在晚飯桌上，和</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    秀才大爺討論，以為阿Q實在有些古怪，我們門窗應該小心些；但他的東西，不知道</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    可還有什麼可買，也許有點好東西罷。加以趙太太也正想買一件價廉物美的皮背心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    于是家族決議，便托鄒七嫂即刻去尋阿Q，而且為此新闢了第三種的例外︰這晚上也</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    姑且特準點油燈。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    油燈干了不少了，阿Q還不到。趙府的全眷都很焦急，打著呵欠，或恨阿Q太飄</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    忽，或怨鄒七嫂不上緊。趙太太還怕他因為春天的條件不敢來，而趙太爺以為不足</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    慮︰因為這是“我”去叫他的。果然，到底趙太爺有見識，阿Q終于跟著鄒七嫂進來</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “他只說沒有沒有，我說你自己當面說去，他還要說，我說……”鄒七嫂氣喘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    吁吁的走著說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “太爺！”阿Q似笑非笑的叫了一聲，在檐下站住了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “阿Q，听說你在外面發財，”趙太爺踱開去，眼楮打量著他的全身，一面說。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “那很好，那很好的。這個，……听說你有些舊東西，……可以都拿來看一看，……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這也並不是別的，因為我倒要……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我對鄒七嫂說過了。都完了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “完了？”趙太爺不覺失聲的說，“那里會完得這樣快呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “那是朋友的，本來不多。他們買了些，……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “總該還有一點罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “現在，只剩了一張門幕了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “就拿門幕來看看罷。”趙太太慌忙說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “那麼，明天拿來就是，”趙太爺卻不甚熱心了。“阿Q，你以後有什麼東西的</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    時候，你盡先送來給我們看，……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “價錢決不會比別家出得少！”秀才說。秀才娘子忙一瞥阿Q的臉，看他感動了</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    沒有。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我要一件皮背心。”趙太太說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q雖然答應著，卻懶洋洋的出去了，也不知道他是否放在心上。這使趙太爺很</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    失望，氣憤而且擔心，至于停止了打呵欠。秀才對于阿Q的態度也很不平，于是說，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這忘八蛋要提防，或者不如吩咐地保，不許他住在未莊。但趙太爺以為不然，說這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也怕要結怨，況且做這路生意的大概是“老鷹不吃窩下食”，本村倒不必擔心的；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    只要自己夜里警醒點就是了。秀才听了這“庭訓”　，非常之以為然，便即刻撤消</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    了驅逐阿Q的提議，而且叮囑鄒七嫂，請伊千萬不要向人提起這一段話。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    但第二日，鄒七嫂便將那藍裙去染了皂，又將阿Q可疑之點傳揚出去了，可是確</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    沒有提起秀才要驅逐他這一節。然而這已經于阿Q很不利。最先，地保尋上門了，取</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    了他的門幕去，阿Q說是趙太太要看的，而地保也不還並且要議定每月的孝敬錢。其</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    次，是村人對于他的敬畏忽而變相了，雖然還不敢來放肆，卻很有遠避的神情，而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這神情和先前的防他來“嚓”的時候又不同，頗混著“敬而遠之”的分子了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    只有一班閑人們卻還要尋根究底的去探阿Q的底細。阿Q也並不諱飾，傲然的說</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    出他的經驗來。從此他們才知道，他不過是一個小腳色，不但不能上牆，並且不能</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    進洞，只站在洞外接東西。有一夜，他剛才接到一個包，正手再進去，不一會，只</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    听得里面大嚷起來，他便趕緊跑，連夜爬出城，逃回未莊來了，從此不敢再去做。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    然而這故事卻于阿Q更不利，村人對于阿Q的“敬而遠之”者，本因為怕結怨，誰料</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他不過是一個不敢再偷的偷兒呢？這實在是“斯亦不足畏也矣”　。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第七章革命</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    宣統三年九月十四日（　）——即阿Q將搭連賣給趙白眼的這一天——三更四點，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有一只大烏篷船到了趙府上的河埠頭。這船從黑    中蕩來，鄉下人睡得熟，都沒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有知道；出去時將近黎明，卻很有幾個看見的了。據探頭探腦的調查來的結果，知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    道那竟是舉人老爺的船！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那船便將大不安載給了未莊，不到正午，全村的人心就很動搖。船的使命，趙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    家本來是很秘密的，但茶坊酒肆里卻都說，革命黨要進城，舉人老爺到我們鄉下來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    逃難了。惟有鄒七嫂不以為然，說那不過是幾口破衣箱，舉人老爺想來寄存的，卻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    已被趙太爺回復轉去。其實舉人老爺和趙秀才素不相能，在理本不能有“共患難”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的情誼，況且鄒七嫂又和趙家是鄰居，見聞較為切近，所以大概該是伊對的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然而謠言很旺盛，說舉人老爺雖然似乎沒有親到，卻有一封長信，和趙家排了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “轉折親”。趙太爺肚里一輪，覺得于他總不會有壞處，便將箱子留下了，現就塞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在太太的床底下。至于革命黨，有的說是便在這一夜進了城，個個白盔白甲︰穿著</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    崇正皇帝的素（　）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q的耳朵里，本來早听到過革命黨這一句話，今年又親眼見過殺掉革命黨。但</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他有一種不知從那里來的意見，以為革命黨便是造反，造反便是與他為難，所以一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    向是“深惡而痛絕之”的。殊不料這卻使百里聞名的舉人老爺有這樣怕，于是他未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    免也有些“神往”了，況且未莊的一群鳥男女的慌張的神情，也使阿Q更快意。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “革命也好罷，”阿Q想，“革這伙媽媽的命，太可惡！太可恨！……便是我，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也要投降革命黨了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q近來用度窘，大約略略有些不平；加以午間喝了兩碗空肚酒，愈加醉得快，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一面想一面走，便又飄飄然起來。不知怎麼一來，忽而似乎革命黨便是自己，未莊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    人卻都是他的俘虜了。他得意之余，禁不住大聲的嚷道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “造反了！造反了！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    未莊人都用了驚懼的眼光對他看。這一種可憐的眼光，是阿Q從來沒有見過的，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一見之下，又使他舒服得如六月里喝了雪水。他更加高興的走而且喊道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “好，……我要什麼就是什麼，我歡喜誰就是誰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    得得，鏘鏘！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    悔不該，酒醉錯斬了鄭賢弟，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    悔不該，呀呀呀……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    得得，鏘鏘，得，鏘令鏘！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我手執鋼鞭將你打……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    趙府上的兩位男人和兩個真本家，也正站在大門口論革命。阿Q沒有見，昂了頭</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    直唱過去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “得得，……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “老Q，”趙太爺怯怯的迎著低聲的叫。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “鏘鏘，”阿Q料不到他的名字會和“老”字聯結起來，以為是一句別的話，與</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    己無干，只是唱。“得，鏘，鏘令鏘，鏘！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “老Q。”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “悔不該……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “阿Q！”秀才只得直呼其名了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q這才站住，歪著頭問道，“什麼？”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “老Q，……現在……”趙太爺卻又沒有話，“現在……發財麼？”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “發財？自然。要什麼就是什麼……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “阿……Q哥，像我們這樣窮朋友是不要緊的……”趙白眼惴惴的說，似乎想探</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    革命黨的口風。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “窮朋友？你總比我有錢。”阿Q說著自去了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大家都憮然，沒有話。趙太爺父子回家，晚上商量到點燈。趙白眼回家，便從</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    腰間扯下搭連來，交給他女人藏在箱底里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q飄飄然的飛了一通，回到土谷祠，酒已經醒透了。這晚上，管祠的老頭子也</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    意外的和氣，請他喝茶；阿Q便向他要了兩個餅，吃完之後，又要了一支點過的四兩</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    燭和一個樹燭台，點起來，獨自躺在自己的小屋里。他說不出的新鮮而且高興，燭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    火像元夜似的閃閃的跳，他的思想也迸跳起來了︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “造反？有趣，……來了一陣白盔白甲的革命黨，都拿著板刀，鋼鞭，炸彈，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    洋炮，三尖兩刃刀，鉤鐮槍，走過土谷祠，叫道，‘阿Q！同去同去！’于是一同去。……</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “這時未莊的一伙鳥男女才好笑哩，跪下叫道，‘阿Q，饒命！’誰听他！第一</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    個該死的是小D和趙太爺，還有秀才，還有假洋鬼子，……留幾條麼？王胡本來還可</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    留，但也不要了。……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “東西，……直走進去打開箱子來︰元寶，洋錢，洋紗衫，……秀才娘子的一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    張寧式床（　）先搬到土谷祠，此外便擺了錢家的桌椅，——或者也就用趙家的罷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    自己是不動手的了，叫小D來搬，要搬得快，搬得不快打嘴巴。……</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “趙司晨的妹子真丑。鄒七嫂的女兒過幾年再說。假洋鬼子的老婆會和沒有辮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    子的男人睡覺，嚇，不是好東西！秀才的老婆是眼胞上有疤的。……吳媽長久不見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了，不知道在那里，——可惜腳太大。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q沒有想得十分停當，已經發了鼾聲，四兩燭還只點去了小半寸，紅焰焰的光</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    照著他張開的嘴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “荷荷！”阿Q忽而大叫起來，抬了頭倉皇的四顧，待到看見四兩燭，卻又倒頭</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    睡去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第二天他起得很遲，走出街上看時，樣樣都照舊。他也仍然肚餓，他想著，想</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不起什麼來；但他忽而似乎有了主意了，慢慢的跨開步，有意無意的走到靜修庵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    庵和春天時節一樣靜，白的牆壁和漆黑的門。他想了一想，前去打門，一只狗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在里面叫。他急急拾了幾塊斷磚，再上去較為用力的打，打到黑門上生出許多麻點</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的時候，才听得有人來開門。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q連忙捏好磚頭，擺開馬步，準備和黑狗來開戰。但庵門只開了一條縫，並無</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    黑狗從中沖出，望進去只有一個老尼姑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你又來什麼事？”伊大吃一驚的說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “革命了……你知道？……”阿Q說得很含胡。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “革命革命，革過一革的，……你們要革得我們怎麼樣呢？”老尼姑兩眼通紅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “什麼？……”阿Q詫異了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你不知道，他們已經來革過了！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “誰？……”阿Q更其詫異了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “那秀才和洋鬼子！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q很出意外，不由的一錯愕；老尼姑見他失了銳氣，便飛速的關了門，阿Q再</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    推時，牢不可開，再打時，沒有回答了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那還是上午的事。趙秀才消息靈，一知道革命黨已在夜間進城，便將辮子盤在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    頂上，一早去拜訪那歷來也不相能的錢洋鬼子。這是“咸與維新”（　）的時候了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    所以他們便談得很投機，立刻成了情投意合的同志，也相約去革命。他們想而又想，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    才想出靜修庵里有一塊“皇帝萬歲萬萬歲”的龍牌，是應該趕緊革掉的，于是又立</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    刻同到庵里去革命。因為老尼姑來阻擋，說了三句話，他們便將伊當作滿政府，在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    頭上很給了不少的棍子和栗鑿。尼姑待他們走後，定了神來檢點，龍牌固然已經碎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在地上了，而且又不見了觀音娘娘座前的一個宣德爐（　）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    這事阿Q後來才知道。他頗悔自己睡著，但也深怪他們不來招呼他。他又退一步</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    想道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “難道他們還沒有知道我已經投降了革命黨麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第八章不準革命</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    未莊的人心日見其安靜了。據傳來的消息，知道革命黨雖然進了城，倒還沒有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    什麼大異樣。知縣大老爺還是原官，不過改稱了什麼，而且舉人老爺也做了什麼—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    —這些名目，未莊人都說不明白——官，帶兵的也還是先前的老把總（　）。只有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一件可怕的事是另有幾個不好的革命黨夾在里面搗亂，第二天便動手剪辮子，听說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那鄰村的航船七斤便著了道兒，弄得不像人樣子了。但這卻還不算大恐怖，因為未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    莊人本來少上城，即使偶有想進城的，也就立刻變了計，踫不著這危險。阿Q本也想</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    進城去尋他的老朋友，一得這消息，也只得作罷了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但未莊也不能說是無改革。幾天之後，將辮子盤在頂上的逐漸增加起來了，早</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    經說過，最先自然是茂才公，其次便是趙司晨和趙白眼，後來是阿Q。倘在夏天，大</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    家將辮子盤在頭頂上或者打一個結，本不算什麼稀奇事，但現在是暮秋，所以這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “秋行夏令”的情形，在盤辮家不能不說是萬分的英斷，而在未莊也不能說無關于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    改革了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    趙司晨腦後空蕩蕩的走來，看見的人大嚷說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “豁，革命黨來了！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q听到了很羨慕。他雖然早知道秀才盤辮的大新聞，但總沒有想到自己可以照</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    樣做，現在看見趙司晨也如此，才有了學樣的意思，定下實行的決心。他用一支竹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    筷將辮子盤在頭頂上，遲疑多時，這才放膽的走去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    他在街上走，人也看他，然而不說什麼話，阿Q當初很不快，後來便很不平。他</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    近來很容易鬧脾氣了；其實他的生活，倒也並不比造反之前反艱難，人見他也客氣，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    店鋪也不說要現錢。而阿Q總覺得自己太失意︰既然革了命，不應該只是這樣的。況</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    且有一回看見小D，愈使他氣破肚皮了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    小D也將辮子盤在頭頂上了，而且也居然用一支竹筷。阿Q萬料不到他也敢這樣</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    做，自己也決不準他這樣做！小D是什麼東西呢？他很想即刻揪住他，拗斷他的竹筷，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    放下他的辮子，並且批他幾個嘴巴，聊且懲罰他忘了生辰八字，也敢來做革命黨的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    罪。但他終于饒放了，單是怒目而視的吐一口唾沫道“呸！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這幾日里，進城去的只有一個假洋鬼子。趙秀才本也想靠著寄存箱子的淵源，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    親身去拜訪舉人老爺的，但因為有剪辮的危險，所以也中止了。他寫了一封“黃傘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    格”（　）的信，托假洋鬼子帶上城，而且托他給自己紹介紹介，去進自由黨。假</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    洋鬼子回來時，向秀才討還了四塊洋錢，秀才便有一塊銀桃子掛在大襟上了；未莊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    人都驚服，說這是柿油黨的頂子（　），抵得一個翰林（　）；趙太爺因此也驟然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    大闊，遠過于他兒子初雋秀才的時候，所以目空一切，見了阿Q，也就很有些不放在</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    眼里了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q正在不平，又時時刻刻感著冷落，一听得這銀桃子的傳說，他立即悟出自己</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    之所以冷落的原因了︰要革命，單說投降，是不行的；盤上辮子，也不行的；第一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    著仍然要和革命黨去結識。他生平所知道的革命黨只有兩個，城里的一個早已“嚓”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的殺掉了，現在只剩了一個假洋鬼子。他除卻趕緊去和假洋鬼子商量之外，再沒有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    別的道路了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    錢府的大門正開著，阿Q便怯怯的  進去。他一到里面，很吃了驚，只見假洋鬼</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    子正站在院子的中央，一身烏黑的大約是洋衣，身上也掛著一塊銀桃子，手里是阿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    Q曾經領教過的棍子，已經留到一尺多長的辮子都拆開了披在肩背上，蓬頭散發的像</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一個劉海仙（　）。對面挺直的站著趙白眼和三個閑人，正在必恭必敬的听說話。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q輕輕的走近了，站在趙白眼的背後，心里想招呼，卻不知道怎麼說才好︰叫</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他假洋鬼子固然是不行的了，洋人也不妥，革命黨也不妥，或者就應該叫洋先生了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    罷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    洋先生卻沒有見他，因為白著眼楮講得正起勁︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我是性急的，所以我們見面，我總是說︰洪哥（　）！我們動手罷！他卻總</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    說道No！——這是洋話，你們不懂的。否則早已成功了。然而這正是他做事小心的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    地方。他再三再四的請我上湖北，我還沒有肯。誰願意在這小縣城里做事情。……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “唔，……這個……”阿Q候他略停，終于用十二分的勇氣開口了，但不知道因</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    為什麼，又並不叫他洋先生。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    听著說話的四個人都吃驚的回顧他。洋先生也才看見︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “什麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “出去！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我要投……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “滾出去！”洋先生揚起哭喪棒來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    趙白眼和閑人們便都吆喝道︰“先生叫你滾出去，你還不听麼！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q將手向頭上一遮，不自覺的逃出門外；洋先生倒也沒有追。他快跑了六十多</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    步，這才慢慢的走，于是心里便涌起了憂愁︰洋先生不準他革命，他再沒有別的路；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    從此決不能望有白盔白甲的人來叫他，他所有的抱負，志向，希望，前程，全被一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    筆勾銷了。至于閑人們傳揚開去，給小D王胡等輩笑話，倒是還在其次的事。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他似乎從來沒有經驗過這樣的無聊。他對于自己的盤辮子，仿佛也覺得無意味，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    要侮蔑；為報仇起見，很想立刻放下辮子來，但也沒有竟放。他游到夜間，賒了兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    碗酒，喝下肚去，漸漸的高興起來了，思想里才又出現白盔白甲的碎片。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有一天，他照例的混到夜深，待酒店要關門，才踱回土谷祠去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    拍，吧……！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    他忽而听得一種異樣的聲音，又不是爆竹。阿Q本來是愛看熱鬧，愛管閑事的，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便在暗中直尋過去。似乎前面有些腳步聲；他正听，猛然間一個人從對面逃來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q一看見，便趕緊翻身跟著逃。那人轉彎，阿Q也轉彎，那人站住了，阿Q也站住。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    他看後面並無什麼，看那人便是小D。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “什麼？”阿Q不平起來了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “趙……趙家遭搶了！”小D氣喘吁吁的說。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q的心怦怦的跳了。小D說了便走；阿Q卻逃而又停的兩三回。但他究竟是做過</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這路生意”，格外膽大，于是  出路角，仔細的听，似乎有些嚷嚷，又仔細的看，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    似乎許多白盔白甲的人，絡繹的將箱子抬出了，器具抬出了，秀才娘子的寧式床也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    抬出了，但是不分明，他還想上前，兩只腳卻沒有動。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這一夜沒有月，未莊在黑暗里很寂靜，寂靜到像羲皇（　）時候一般太平。阿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    Q站著看到自己發煩，也似乎還是先前一樣，在那里來來往往的搬，箱子抬出了，器</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    具抬出了，秀才娘子的寧式床也抬出了，……抬得他自己有些不信他的眼楮了。但</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他決計不再上前，卻回到自己的祠里去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    土谷祠里更漆黑；他關好大門，摸進自己的屋子里。他躺了好一會，這才定了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    神，而且發出關于自己的思想來︰白盔白甲的人明明到了，並不來打招呼，搬了許</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    多好東西，又沒有自己的份，——這全是假洋鬼子可惡，不準我造反，否則，這次</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    何至于沒有我的份呢？阿Q越想越氣，終于禁不住滿心痛恨起來，毒毒的點一點頭︰</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “不準我造反，只準你造反？媽媽的假洋鬼子，——好，你造反！造反是殺頭的罪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    名呵，我總要告一狀，看你抓進縣里去殺頭，——滿門抄斬，——嚓！嚓！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第九章大團圓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    趙家遭搶之後，未莊人大抵很快意而且恐慌，阿Q也很快意而且恐慌。但四天之</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    後，阿Q在半夜里忽被抓進縣城里去了。那時恰是暗夜，一隊兵，一隊團丁，一隊警</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    察，五個偵探，悄悄地到了未莊，乘昏暗圍住土谷祠，正對門架好機關槍；然而阿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    Q不沖出。許多時沒有動靜，把總焦急起來了，懸了二十千的賞，才有兩個團丁冒了</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    險，逾垣進去，里應外合，一擁而入，將阿Q抓出來；直待擒出祠外面的機關槍左近，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他才有些清醒了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    到進城，已經是正午，阿Q見自己被攙進一所破衙門，轉了五六個彎，便推在一</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    間小屋里。他剛剛一蹌踉，那用整株的木料做成的柵欄門便跟著他的腳跟闔上了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    其余的三面都是牆壁，仔細看時，屋角上還有兩個人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q雖然有些忐忑，卻並不很苦悶，因為他那土谷祠里的臥室，也並沒有比這間</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    屋子更高明。那兩個也仿佛是鄉下人，漸漸和他兜搭起來了，一個說是舉人老爺要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    追他祖父欠下來的陳租，一個不知道為了什麼事。他們問阿Q，阿Q爽利的答道，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “因為我想造反。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他下半天便又被抓出柵欄門去了，到得大堂，上面坐著一個滿頭剃得精光的老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    頭子。阿Q疑心他是和尚，但看見下面站著一排兵，兩旁又站著十幾個長衫人物，也</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有滿頭剃得精光像這老頭子的，也有將一尺來長的頭發披在背後像那假洋鬼子的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都是一臉橫肉，怒目而視的看他；他便知道這人一定有些來歷，膝關節立刻自然而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然的寬松，便跪了下去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “站著說！不要跪！”長衫人物都吆喝說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q雖然似乎懂得，但總覺得站不住，身不由己的蹲了下去，而且終于趁勢改為</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    跪下了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “奴隸性！……”長衫人物又鄙夷似的說，但也沒有叫他起來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你從實招來罷，免得吃苦。我早都知道了。招了可以放你。”那光頭的老頭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    子看定了阿Q的臉，沉靜的清楚的說。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “招罷！”長衫人物也大聲說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “我本來要……來投……”阿Q胡里胡涂的想了一通，這才斷斷續續的說。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “那麼，為什麼不來的呢？”老頭子和氣的問。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “假洋鬼子不準我！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “胡說！此刻說，也遲了。現在你的同黨在那里？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “什麼？……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “那一晚打劫趙家的一伙人。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “他們沒有來叫我。他們自己搬走了。”阿Q提起來便憤憤。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “走到那里去了呢？說出來便放你了。”老頭子更和氣了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我不知道，……他們沒有來叫我……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    然而老頭子使了一個眼色，阿Q便又被抓進柵欄門里了。他第二次抓出柵欄門，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是第二天的上午。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    大堂的情形都照舊。上面仍然坐著光頭的老頭子，阿Q也仍然下了跪。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老頭子和氣的問道，“你還有什麼話說麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q一想，沒有話，便回答說，“沒有。”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    于是一個長衫人物拿了一張紙，並一支筆送到阿Q的面前，要將筆塞在他手里。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q這時很吃驚，幾乎“魂飛魄散”了︰因為他的手和筆相關，這回是初次。他正不</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    知怎樣拿；那人卻又指著一處地方教他畫花押。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “我……我……不認得字。”阿Q一把抓住了筆，惶恐而且慚愧的說。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “那麼，便宜你，畫一個圓圈！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q要畫圓圈了，那手捏著筆卻只是抖。于是那人替他將紙鋪在地上，阿Q伏下</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    去，使盡了平生的力氣畫圓圈。他生怕被人笑話，立志要畫得圓，但這可惡的筆不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但很沉重，並且不听話，剛剛一抖一抖的幾乎要合縫，卻又向外一聳，畫成瓜子模</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    樣了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q正羞愧自己畫得不圓，那人卻不計較，早已掣了紙筆去，許多人又將他第二</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    次抓進柵欄門。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他第二次進了柵欄，倒也並不十分懊惱。他以為人生天地之間，大約本來有時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    要抓進抓出，有時要在紙上畫圓圈的，惟有圈而不圓，卻是他“行狀”上的一個污</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    點。但不多時也就釋然了，他想︰孫子才畫得很圓的圓圈呢。于是他睡著了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然而這一夜，舉人老爺反而不能睡︰他和把總嘔了氣了。舉人老爺主張第一要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    追贓，把總主張第一要示眾。把總近來很不將舉人老爺放在眼里了，拍案打凳的說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    道，“懲一儆百！你看，我做革命黨還不上二十天，搶案就是十幾件，全不破案，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我的面子在那里？破了案，你又來迂。不成！這是我管的！”舉人老爺窘急了，然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而還堅持，說是倘若不追贓，他便立刻辭了幫辦民政的職務。而把總卻道，“請便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    罷！”于是舉人老爺在這一夜竟沒有睡，但幸第二天倒也沒有辭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q第三次抓出柵欄門的時候，便是舉人老爺睡不著的那一夜的明天的上午了。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    他到了大堂，上面還坐著照例的光頭老頭子；阿Q也照例的下了跪。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老頭子很和氣的問道，“你還有什麼話麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q一想，沒有話，便回答說，“沒有。”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    許多長衫和短衫人物，忽然給他穿上一件洋布的白背心，上面有些黑字。阿Q很</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    氣苦︰因為這很像是帶孝，而帶孝是晦氣的。然而同時他的兩手反縛了，同時又被</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一直抓出衙門外去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q被抬上了一輛沒有蓬的車，幾個短衣人物也和他同坐在一處。這車立刻走動</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了，前面是一班背著洋炮的兵們和團丁，兩旁是許多張著嘴的看客，後面怎樣，阿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    Q沒有見。但他突然覺到了︰這豈不是去殺頭麼？他一急，兩眼發黑，耳朵里﹝口皇﹞</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的一聲，似乎發昏了。然而他又沒有全發昏，有時雖然著急，有時卻也泰然；他意</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    思之間，似乎覺得人生天地間，大約本來有時也未免要殺頭的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他還認得路，于是有些詫異了︰怎麼不向著法場走呢？他不知道這是在游街，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在示眾。但即使知道也一樣，他不過便以為人生天地間，大約本來有時也未免要游</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    街要示眾罷了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他省悟了，這是繞到法場去的路，這一定是“嚓”的去殺頭。他惘惘的向左右</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    看，全跟著馬蟻似的人，而在無意中，卻在路旁的人叢中發見了一個吳媽。很久違，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    伊原來在城里做工了。阿Q忽然很羞愧自己沒志氣︰竟沒有唱幾句戲。他的思想仿佛</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    旋風似的在腦里一回旋︰《小孤孀上墳》欠堂皇，《龍虎斗》里的“悔不該……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也太乏，還是“手執鋼鞭將你打”罷。他同時想手一揚，才記得這兩手原來都捆著，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    于是“手執鋼鞭”也不唱了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    “過了二十年又是一個……”阿Q在百忙中，“無師自通”的說出半句從來不說</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的話。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “好！！！”從人叢里，便發出豺狼的嗥叫一般的聲音來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    車子不住的前行，阿Q在喝采聲中，輪轉眼楮去看吳媽，似乎伊一向並沒有見他，</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    卻只是出神的看著兵們背上的洋炮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    阿Q于是再看那些喝采的人們。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這剎那中，他的思想又仿佛旋風似的在腦里一回旋了。四年之前，他曾在山腳</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    下遇見一只餓狼，永是不近不遠的跟定他，要吃他的肉。他那時嚇得幾乎要死，幸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而手里有一柄斫柴刀，才得仗這壯了膽，支持到未莊；可是永遠記得那狼眼楮，又</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    凶又怯，閃閃的像兩顆鬼火，似乎遠遠的來穿透了他的皮肉。而這回他又看見從來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    沒有見過的更可怕的眼楮了，又鈍又鋒利，不但已經咀嚼了他的話，並且還要咀嚼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他皮肉以外的東西，永是不近不遠的跟他走。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這些眼楮們似乎連成一氣，已經在那里咬他的靈魂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “救命，……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    然而阿Q沒有說。他早就兩眼發黑，耳朵里嗡的一聲，覺得全身仿佛微塵似的迸</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    散了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    至于當時的影響，最大的倒反在舉人老爺，因為終于沒有追贓，他全家都號啕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了。其次是趙府，非特秀才因為上城去報官，被不好的革命黨剪了辮子，而且又破</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    費了二十千的賞錢，所以全家也號啕了。從這一天以來，他們便漸漸的都發生了遺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老的氣味。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    至于輿論，在未莊是無異議，自然都說阿Q壞，被槍斃便是他的壞的證據︰不壞</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    又何至于被槍斃呢？而城里的輿論卻不佳，他們多半不滿足，以為槍斃並無殺頭這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    般好看；而且那是怎樣的一個可笑的死囚呵，游了那麼久的街，竟沒有唱一句戲︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們白跟一趟了……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初分章發表于北京《晨報副刊》，自一九二一年十二月四日起至一九</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    二二年二月十二日止，每周或隔周刊登一次，署名巴人。作者在一九二五年曾為這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    篇小說的俄文譯本寫過一篇短序，後收在《集外集》中；一九二六年又寫過《阿Q正</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    傳的成因》一文，收在《華蓋集續編》中，都可參看。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え“立言”︰我國古代所謂“三不朽”之一。《左傳》襄公二十四年載魯國大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    夫叔孫豹的話︰“太上有立德，其次有立功，其次有立言，雖久不廢，此之謂不朽。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ“名不正則言不順”︰語見《論語•子路》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    お內傳︰小說體傳記的一種。作者在一九三一年三月三日給《阿Q正傳》日譯者</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    山上正義的校釋中說︰“昔日道士寫仙人的事多以‘內傳’題名。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か“正史”︰封建時代由官方撰修或認可的史書。清代乾隆時規定自《史記》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    至《明史》歷代二十四部紀傳體史書為“正史”。“正史”中的“列傳”部分，一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    般都是著名人物的傳記。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    が宣付國史館立“本傳”︰舊時效忠于統治階級的重要人物或所謂名人，死後</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    由政府明令褒揚，令文末常有“宣付國史館立傳”的話。歷代編纂史書的機構，名</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    稱不一，清代叫國史館。辛亥革命後，北洋軍閥及國民黨政府都曾沿用這一名稱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    き迭更司（1812—1870）︰通譯狄更斯，英國小說家。著有《大衛•科波菲爾》、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    《雙城記》等。《博徒別傳》原名《勞特奈•斯吞》，英國小說家柯南•道爾（18</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    59—1930）著。魯迅在一九二六年八月八日致韋素園信中曾說︰“《博徒別傳》是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    RodneyStone的譯名，但是C。Doyle做的。《阿Q正傳》中說是迭更司作，乃是我誤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    記。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぎ“引車賣漿者流”所用的話︰指白話文。一九三一年三月三日作者給日本山</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    上正義的校釋中說︰“‘引車賣漿’，即拉車賣豆腐漿之謂，系指蔡元培氏之父。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那時，蔡元培氏為北京大學校長，亦系主張白話者之一，故亦受到攻擊之矢。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    く不入三教九流的小說家︰三教，指儒教、佛教、道教；九流，即九家。《漢</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    書•藝文志》中分古代諸子為十家︰儒家、道家、陰陽家、法家、名家、墨家、縱</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    橫家、雜家、農家、小說家，並說︰“諸子十家，其可觀者九家而已。”“小說家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    者流，蓋出于稗官。街談巷語，道听途說者之所造也。……是以君子弗為也。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぐ《書法正傳》︰一部關于書法的書，清代馮武著，共十卷。這里的“正傳”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是“正確的傳授”的意思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　“著之竹帛”︰語出《呂氏春秋•仲春紀》︰“著乎竹帛，傳乎後世。”竹，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    竹簡；帛，絹綢。我國古代未發明造紙前曾用來書寫文字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　茂才︰即秀才。東漢時，因為避光武帝劉秀的名諱，改秀才為茂才；後來有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    時也沿用作秀才的別稱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　陳獨秀辦了《新青年》提倡洋字︰指一九一八年前後錢玄同等人在《新青年》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    雜志上開展關于廢除漢字、改用羅馬字母拼音的討論一事。一九三一年三月三日作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    者在給山上正義的校釋中說︰“主張使用羅馬字母的是錢玄同，這里說是陳獨秀，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    系茂才公之誤。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　《郡名百家姓》︰《百家姓》是以前學塾所用的識字課本之一，宋初人編纂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    為便于誦讀，將姓氏連綴為四言韻語。《郡名百家姓》則在每一姓上都附注郡（古</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    代地方區域的名稱）名，表示某姓望族曾居古代某地，如趙為“天水”、錢為“彭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    城”之類。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　胡適之（1891—1962）︰即胡適，安徽績溪人，買辦資產階級文人、政客。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他在一九二○年七月所作《〈水滸傳〉考證》中自稱“有歷史癖與考據癖”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　“行狀”︰原指封建時代記述死者世系、籍貫、生卒、事跡的文字，一般由</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    其家屬撰寫。這里泛指經歷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　土谷祠︰即土地廟。土谷，指土地神和五谷神。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　“文童”︰也稱“童生”，指科舉時代習舉業而尚未考取秀才的人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　狀元︰科舉時代，經皇帝殿試取中的第一名進士叫狀元。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　押牌寶︰一種賭博。賭局中為主的人叫“樁家”；下文的“青龍”、“天門”、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “穿堂”等都是押牌寶的用語，指押賭注的位置；“四百”、“一百五十”是押賭</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    注的錢數。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ヾ“塞翁失馬安知非福”︰據《淮南子•人間訓》︰“近塞上之人有善術者，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    馬無故亡胡中，人皆吊之。其父曰︰此何遽不能為福乎？居數月，其馬將胡駿馬而</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    歸，人皆賀之。其父曰︰此何遽不能為禍乎？家富馬良，其子好騎，墮而折髀，人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    皆吊之。其父曰︰此何遽不能為福乎？居一年，胡人大入塞，丁壯者控弦而戰，塞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    上之人死者十九，此獨以跛之故，父子相保。故福之為禍，禍之為福，化不可極，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    深不可測也。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ゝ賽神︰即迎神賽會，舊時的一種迷信習俗。以鼓樂儀仗和雜戲等迎神出廟，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    周游街巷，以酬神祈福。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ゞ《小孤孀上墳》︰當時流行的一出紹興地方戲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    々太牢︰按古代祭禮，原指牛、羊、豕三牲，但後來單稱牛為太牢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぁ皇帝已經停了考︰光緒三十一年（1905），清政府下令自丙午科起，廢止科</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    舉考試。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    あ哭喪棒︰舊時在為父母送殯時，兒子須手拄“孝杖”，以表示悲痛難支。阿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    Q因厭惡假洋鬼子，所以把他的手杖咒為“哭喪棒”。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぃ“不孝有三無後為大”︰語見《孟子•離婁》。據漢代趙岐注︰“于禮有不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    孝者三事，謂阿意曲從，陷親不義，一不孝也；家窮親老，不為祿仕，二不孝也；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不娶無子，絕先祖祀，三不孝也。三者之中，無後為大。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    い“若敖之鬼餒而”︰語出《左傳》宣公四年︰楚國令尹子良（若敖氏）的兒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    子越椒長相凶惡，子良的哥哥子文認為越椒長大後會招致滅族之禍，要子良殺死他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    子良沒有依從。子文臨死時說︰“鬼猶求食，若敖氏之鬼不其餒而。”意思是若敖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    氏以後沒有子孫供飯，鬼魂都要挨餓了。而，語尾助詞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぅ“不能收其放心”︰《尚書•畢命》︰“雖收放心，閑之維艱。”放心，心</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    無約束的意思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    う妲己︰殷紂王的妃子。下文的褒姒是周幽王的妃子。《史記》中有商因妲己</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而亡，周因褒姒而衰的記載。貂蟬是《三國演義》中王允家的一個歌妓，書中有呂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    布為爭奪她而殺死董卓的故事。作者在這里是諷刺那種把歷史上亡國敗家的原因都</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    歸罪于婦女的觀點。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　“男女之大防”︰指封建禮教對男女之間所規定的嚴格界限，如“男子居外，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    女子居內”（《禮記•內則》），“男女授受不親”（《孟子•離婁》），等等。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　“誅心”︰猶“誅意”。《後漢書•霍﹝言胥﹞傳》︰“《春秋》之義，原</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    情定過，赦事誅意。”誅心、誅意，指不問實際情形如何而主觀地推究別人的居心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　“而立”︰語出《論語•為政》︰“三十而立”。原是孔丘說他三十歲在學</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    問上有所自立的話，後來就常被用作三十歲的代詞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　小Don︰即小同。作者在《且介亭雜文•寄〈戲〉周刊編者信》中說︰“他叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    ‘小同’，大起來，和阿Q一樣。”</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　“我手執鋼鞭將你打！”︰這一句及下文的“悔不該，酒醉錯斬了鄭賢弟”，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都是當時紹興地方戲《龍虎斗》中的唱詞。這出戲演的是宋太祖趙匡胤和呼延贊交</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    戰的故事。鄭賢弟，指趙匡胤部下猛將鄭子明。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　“士別三日便當刮目相待”︰語出《三國志•吳書•呂蒙傳》裴松之注︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “士別三日，即更刮目相待。”刮目，拭目的意思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　三十二張的竹牌︰一種賭具。即牙牌或骨牌，用象牙或獸骨所制，簡陋的就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    用竹制成。下文的“麻醬”指麻雀牌，俗稱麻將，也是一種賭具。阿Q把“麻將”訛</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    為“麻醬”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　三百大錢九二串︰即“三百大錢，以九十二文作為一百”（見《華蓋集續編</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    •阿Q正傳的成因》）。舊時我國用的銅錢，中有方孔，可用繩子串在一起，每千枚</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （或每枚“當十”的大錢一百枚）為一串，稱作一吊，但實際上常不足數。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　“庭訓”︰《論語•季氏》載︰孔丘“嘗獨立，鯉（按︰即孔丘的兒子）趨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而過庭”，孔丘要他學“詩”、學“禮”。後來就常有人稱父親的教訓為“庭訓”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    或“過庭之訓”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　“斯亦不足畏也矣”︰語見《論語•子罕》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （　）宣統三年九月十四日︰這一天是公元一九一一年十一月四日，辛亥革命</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    武昌起義後的第二十五天。據《中國革命記》第三冊（一九一一年上海自由社編印）</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    記載︰辛亥九月十四日杭州府為民軍佔領，紹興府即日宣布光復。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （　）穿著崇正皇帝的素︰崇正，作品中人物對崇禎的訛稱。崇禎是明思宗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （朱由檢）的年號。明亡于清，後來有些農民起義的部隊，常用“反清復明”的口</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    號來反對清朝統治，因此直到清末還有人認為革命軍起義是替崇禎皇帝報仇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （　）寧式床︰浙江寧波一帶制作的一種比較講究的床。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （　）“咸與維新”︰語見《尚書•胤征》︰“舊染污俗，咸與維新。”原意</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是對一切受惡習影響的人都給以棄舊從新的機會。這里指辛亥革命時革命派與反對</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    勢力妥協，地主官僚等乘此投機的現象。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （　）宣德爐︰明宣宗宣德年間（1426—1435）制造的一種比較名貴的小型銅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    香爐，爐底有“大明宣德年制”字樣。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （　）把總︰清代最下一級的武官。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （　）“黃傘格”︰一種寫信格式。這樣的信表示對于對方的恭敬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （　）柿油黨的頂子︰柿油黨是“自由黨”的諧音，作者在《華蓋集續集•阿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    Q正傳的成因》中說︰“‘柿油黨’……原是‘自由黨’，鄉下人不能懂，便訛成他</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    們能懂的‘柿油黨’了。”頂子是清代官員帽頂上表示官階的帽珠。這里是未莊人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    把自由黨的徽章比作官員的“頂子”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （　）翰林︰唐代以來皇帝的文學侍從的名稱。明、清時代凡進士選入翰林院</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    供職者通稱翰林，擔任編修國史、起草文件等工作，是一種名望較高的文職官餃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （　）劉海仙︰指五代時的劉海蟾。相傳他在終南山修道成仙。流行于民間的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他的畫像，一般都是披著長發，前額覆有短發。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （　）洪哥︰大概指黎元洪。他原任清朝新軍第二十一混成協的協統（相當于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    以後的旅長），一九一一年武昌起義時，被拉出來擔任革命軍的鄂軍都督。他並未</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000001999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    參與武昌起義的籌劃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    （　）羲皇︰指伏羲氏。傳說中我國上古時代的帝王。他的時代過去曾被形容</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    為太平盛世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p> 兔和貓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    住在我們後進院子里的三太太，在夏間買了一對白兔，是給伊的孩子們看的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這一對白兔，似乎離娘並不久，雖然是異類，也可以看出他們的天真爛熳來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但也豎直了小小的通紅的長耳朵，動著鼻子，眼楮里頗現些驚疑的神色，大約究竟</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    覺得人地生疏，沒有在老家時候的安心了。這種東西，倘到廟會え日期自己出去買，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    每個至多不過兩吊錢，而三太太卻花了一元，因為是叫小使上店買來的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    孩子們自然大得意了，嚷著圍住了看；大人也都圍著看；還有一匹小狗名叫S</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    的也跑來，闖過去一嗅，打了一個噴嚏，退了幾步。三太太吆喝道，“S，听著，不</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    準你咬他！”于是在他頭上打了一拳，S便退開了，從此並不咬。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這一對兔總是關在後窗後面的小院子里的時候多，听說是因為太喜歡撕壁紙，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也常常啃木器腳。這小院子里有一株野桑樹，桑子落地，他們最愛吃，便連喂他們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的菠菜也不吃了。烏鴉喜鵲想要下來時，他們便躬著身子用後腳在地上使勁的一彈，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    砉的一聲直跳上來，像飛起了一團雪，鴉鵲嚇得趕緊走，這樣的幾回，再也不敢近</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來了。三太太說，鴉鵲到不打緊，至多也不過搶吃一點食料，可惡的是一匹大黑貓，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    常在矮牆上惡狠狠的看，這卻要防的，幸而S和貓是對頭，或者還不至于有什麼罷。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    孩子們時時捉他們來玩耍；他們很和氣，豎起耳朵，動著鼻子，馴良的站在小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    手的圈子里，但一有空，卻也就溜開去了。他們夜里的臥榻是一個小木箱，里面鋪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    些稻草，就在後窗的房檐下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這樣的幾個月之後，他們忽而自己掘土了，掘得非常快，前腳一抓，後腳一踢，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不到半天，已經掘成一個深洞。大家都奇怪，後來仔細看時，原來一個的肚子比別</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一個的大得多了。他們第二天便將干草和樹葉餃進洞里去，忙了大半天。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大家都高興，說又有小兔可看了；三太太便對孩子們下了戒嚴令，從此不許再</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    去捉。我的母親也很喜歡他們家族的繁榮，還說待生下來的離了乳，也要去討兩匹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來養在自己的窗外面。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們從此便住在自造的洞府里，有時也出來吃些食，後來不見了，可不知道他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    們是預先運糧存在里面呢還是竟不吃。過了十多天，三太太對我說，那兩匹又出來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了，大約小兔是生下來又都死掉了，因為雌的一匹的奶非常多，卻並不見有進去哺</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    養孩子的形跡。伊言語之間頗氣憤，然而也沒有法。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有一天，太陽很溫暖，也沒有風，樹葉都不動，我忽听得許多人在那里笑，尋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    聲看時，卻見許多人都靠著三太太的後窗看︰原來有一個小兔，在院子里跳躍了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這比他的父母買來的時候還小得遠，但也已經能用後腳一彈地，迸跳起來了。孩子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    們爭著告訴我說，還看見一個小兔到洞口來探一探頭，但是即刻便縮回去了，那該</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是他的弟弟罷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那小的也撿些草葉吃，然而大的似乎不許他，往往夾口的搶去了，而自己並不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    吃。孩子們笑得響，那小的終于吃驚了，便跳著鑽進洞里去；大的也跟到洞門口，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    用前腳推著他的孩子的脊梁，推進之後，又爬開泥土來封了洞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    從此小院子里更熱鬧，窗口也時時有人窺探了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然而竟又全不見了那小的和大的。這時是連日的陰天，三太太又慮到遭了那大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    黑貓的毒手的事去。我說不然，那是天氣冷，當然都躲著，太陽一出，一定出來的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    太陽出來了，他們卻都不見。于是大家就忘卻了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    惟有三太太是常在那里喂他們菠菜的，所以常想到。伊有一回走進窗後的小院</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    子去，忽然在牆角上發見了一個別的洞，再看舊洞口，卻依稀的還見有許多爪痕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這爪痕倘說是大兔的，爪該不會有這樣大，伊又疑心到那常在牆上的大黑貓去了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    伊于是也就不能不定下發掘的決心了。伊終于出來取了鋤子，一路掘下去，雖然疑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    心，卻也希望著意外的見了小白兔的，但是待到底，卻只見一堆爛草夾些兔毛，怕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    還是臨蓐時候所鋪的罷，此外是冷清清的，全沒有什麼雪白的小兔的蹤跡，以及他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那只一探頭未出洞外的弟弟了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    氣憤和失望和淒涼，使伊不能不再掘那牆角上的新洞了。一動手，那大的兩匹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便先竄出洞外面。伊以為他們搬了家了，很高興，然而仍然掘，待見底，那里面也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    鋪著草葉和兔毛，而上面卻睡著七個很小的兔，遍身肉紅色，細看時，眼楮全都沒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有開。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一切都明白了，三太太先前的預料果不錯。伊為預防危險起見，便將七個小的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都裝在木箱中，搬進自己的房里，又將大的也捺進箱里面，勒令伊去哺乳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    三太太從此不但深恨黑貓，而且頗不以大兔為然了。據說當初那兩個被害之先，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    死掉的該還有，因為他們生一回，決不至于只兩個，但為了哺乳不勻，不能爭食的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    就先死了。這大概也不錯的，現在七個之中，就有兩個很瘦弱。所以三太太一有閑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    空，便捉住母兔，將小兔一個一個輪流的擺在肚子上來喝奶，不準有多少。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    母親對我說，那樣麻煩的養兔法，伊歷來連听也未曾听到過，恐怕是可以收入</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    《無雙譜》ぉ的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    白兔的家族更繁榮；大家也又都高興了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但自此之後，我總覺得淒涼。夜半在燈下坐著想，那兩條小性命，竟是人不知</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    鬼不覺的早在不知什麼時候喪失了，生物史上不著一些痕跡，並S也不叫一聲。我于</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是記起舊事來，先前我住在會館里，清早起身，只見大槐樹下一片散亂的鴿子毛，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這明明是膏于鷹吻的了，上午長班お來一打掃，便什麼都不見，誰知道曾有一個生</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    命斷送在這里呢？我又曾路過西四牌樓，看見一匹小狗被馬車軋得快死，待回來時，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    什麼也不見了，搬掉了罷，過往行人憧憧的走著，誰知道曾有一個生命斷送在這里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    呢？夏夜，窗外面，常听到蒼蠅的悠長的吱吱的叫聲，這一定是給蠅虎咬住了，然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而我向來無所容心于其間，而別人並且不听到……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    假使造物也可以責備，那麼，我以為他實在將生命造得太濫了，毀得太濫了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    嗥的一聲，又是兩條貓在窗外打起架來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “迅兒！你又在那里打貓了？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “不，他們自己咬。他那里會給我打呢。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我的母親是素來很不以我的虐待貓為然的，現在大約疑心我要替小兔抱不平，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    下什麼辣手，便起來探問了。而我在全家的口碑上，卻的確算一個貓敵。我曾經害</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    過貓，平時也常打貓，尤其是在他們配合的時候。但我之所以打的原因並非因為他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    們配合，是因為他們嚷，嚷到使我睡不著，我以為配合是不必這樣大嚷而特嚷的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    況且黑貓害了小兔，我更是“師出有名”的了。我覺得母親實在太修善，于是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不由的就說出模稜的近乎不以為然的答話來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    造物太胡鬧，我不能不反抗他了，雖然也許是倒是幫他的忙……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那黑貓是不能久在矮牆上高視闊步的了，我決定的想，于是又不由的一瞥那藏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在書箱里的一瓶青酸鉀か。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一九二二年十月。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九二二年十月十日北京《晨報副刊》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え廟會︰又稱“廟市”，舊時在節日或規定的日子，設在寺廟或其附近的集市。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ《無雙譜》︰清代金古良編繪，內收從漢到宋四十個行為獨特人物的畫像，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    並各附一詩。這里借用來形容獨一無二。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お長班︰舊時官員的隨身僕人，也用以稱一般的“听差”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か青酸鉀︰即氰酸鉀，一種劇毒的化學品。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ﹝《吶喊》﹞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    打字︰諸葛不亮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p> 社戲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我在倒數上去的二十年中，只看過兩回中國戲，前十年是絕不看，因為沒有看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    戲的意思和機會，那兩回全在後十年，然而都沒有看出什麼來就走了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第一回是民國元年我初到北京的時候，當時一個朋友對我說，北京戲最好，你</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不去見見世面麼？我想，看戲是有味的，而況在北京呢。于是都興致勃勃的跑到什</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    麼園，戲文已經開場了，在外面也早听到冬冬地響。我們挨進門，幾個紅的綠的在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我的眼前一閃爍，便又看見戲台下滿是許多頭，再定神四面看，卻見中間也還有幾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    個空座，，擠過去要坐時，又有人對我發議論，我因為耳朵已經諾南熳帕耍　昧</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    心，才听到他是說“有人，不行！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我們退到後面，一個辮子很光的卻來領我們到了側面，指出一個地位來。這所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    謂地位者，原來是一條長凳，然而他那坐板比我的上腿要狹到四分之三，他的腳比</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我的下腿要長過三分之二。我先是沒有爬上去的勇氣，接著便聯想到私刑拷打的刑</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    具，不由的毛骨悚然的走出了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    走了許多路，忽听得我的朋友的聲音道，“究竟怎的？”我回過臉去，原來他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也被我帶出來了。他很詫異的說，“怎麼總是走，不答應？”我說，“朋友，對不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    起，我耳朵只在冬冬?  諾南歟　　揮刑  僥愕幕啊！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    後來我每一想到，便很以為奇怪，似乎這戲太不好，——否則便是我近來在戲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    台下不適于生存了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第二回忘記了那一年，總之是募集湖北水災捐而譚叫天え還沒有死。捐法是兩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    元錢買一張戲票，可以到第一舞台去看戲，扮演的多是名角，其一就是小叫天。我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    買了一張票，本是對于勸募人聊以塞責的，然而似乎又有好事家乘機對我說了些叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    天不可不看的大法要了。我于是忘了前幾年的冬冬?  胖　鄭　溝降諞晃杼ㄈХ耍</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但大約一半也因為重價購來的寶票，總得使用了才舒服。我打听得叫天出台是遲的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而第一舞台卻是新式構造，用不著爭座位，便放了心，延宕到九點鐘才去，誰料照</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    例，人都滿了，連立足也難，我只得擠在遠處的人叢中看一個老旦在台上唱。那老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    旦嘴邊插著兩個點火的紙捻子，旁邊有一個鬼卒，我費盡思量，才疑心他或者是目</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    連ぉ的母親，因為後來又出來了一個和尚。然而我又不知道那名角是誰，就去問擠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    小在我的左邊的一位胖紳士。他很看不起似的斜瞥了我一眼，說道，“龔雲甫お！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我深愧淺陋而且粗疏，臉上一熱，同時腦里也制出了決不再問的定章，于是看小旦</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    唱，看花旦唱，看老生唱，看不知什麼角色唱，看一大班人亂打，看兩三個人互打，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    從九點多到十點，從十點到十一點，從十一點到十一點半，從十一點半到十二點，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ——然而叫天竟還沒有來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我向來沒有這樣忍耐的等待過什麼事物，而況這身邊的胖紳士的吁吁的喘氣，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這台上的冬冬?  諾那麼潁　旌　搪痰幕蔚矗　又　允　  悖　齠  刮沂　蟺皆謖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    里不適于生存了。我同時便機械的擰轉身子，用力往外只一擠，覺得背後便已滿滿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的，大約那彈性的胖紳士早在我的空處胖開了他的右半身了。我後無回路，自然擠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而又擠2，終于出了大門。街上除了專等看客的車輛之外，幾乎沒有什麼行人了，大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    門口卻還有十幾個人昂著頭看戲目，別有一堆人站著並不看什麼，我想︰他們大概</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是看散戲之後出來的女人們的，而叫天卻還沒有來……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然而夜氣很清爽，真所謂“沁人心脾”，我在北京遇著這樣的好空氣，仿佛這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是第一遭了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這一夜，就是我對于中國戲告了別的一夜，此後再沒有想到他，即使偶而經過</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    戲園，我們也漠不相關，精神上早已一在天之南一在地之北了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但是前幾天，我忽在無意之中看到一本日本文的書，可惜忘記了書名和著者，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    總之是關于中國戲的。其中有一篇，大意仿佛說，中國戲是大敲，大叫，大跳，使</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    看客頭昏腦眩，很不適于劇場，但若在野外散漫的所在，遠遠的看起來，也自有他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的風致。我當時覺著這正是說了在我意中而未曾想到的話，因為我確記得在野外看</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    過很好的戲，到北京以後的連進兩回戲園去，也許還是受了那時的影響哩。可惜我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不知道怎麼一來，竟將書名忘卻了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    至于我看好戲的時候，卻實在已經是“遠哉遙遙”的了，其時恐怕我還不過十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一二歲。我們魯鎮的習慣，本來是凡有出嫁的女兒，倘自己還未當家，夏間便大抵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    回到母家去消夏。那時我的祖母雖然還康建，但母親也已分擔了些家務，所以夏期</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便不能多日的歸省了，只得在掃墓完畢之後，抽空去住幾天，這時我便每年跟了我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的母親住在外祖母的家里。那地方叫平橋村，是一個離海邊不遠，極偏僻的，臨河</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的小村莊；住戶不滿三十家，都種田，打魚，只有一家很小的雜貨店。但在我是樂</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    土︰因為我在這里不但得到優待，又可以免念“秩秩斯干幽幽南山”か了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    和我一同玩的是許多小朋友，因為有了遠客，他們也都從父母那里得了減少工</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    作的許可，伴我來游戲。在小村里，一家的客，幾乎也就是公共的。我們年紀都相</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    仿，但論起行輩來，卻至少是叔子，有幾個還是太公，因為他們合村都同姓，是本</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    家。然而我們是朋友，即使偶而吵鬧起來，打了太公，一村的老老少少，也決沒有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一個會想出“犯上”這兩個字來，而他們也百分之九十九不識字。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我們每天的事情大概是掘蚯蚓，掘來穿在銅絲做的小鉤上，伏在河沿上去釣蝦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    蝦是水世界里的呆子，決不憚用了自己的兩個鉗捧著鉤尖送到嘴里去的，所以不半</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    天便可以釣到一大碗。這蝦照例是歸我吃的。其次便是一同去放牛，但或者因為高</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    等動物了的緣故罷，黃牛水牛都欺生，敢于欺侮我，因此我也總不敢走近身，只好</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    遠遠地跟著，站著。這時候，小朋友們便不再原諒我會讀“秩秩斯干”，卻全都嘲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    笑起來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    至于我在那里所第一盼望的，卻在到趙莊去看戲。趙莊是離平橋村五里的較大</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的村莊；平橋村太小，自己演不起戲，每年總付給趙莊多少錢，算作合做的。當時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我並不想到他們為什麼年年要演戲。現在想，那或者是春賽，是社戲が了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    就在我十一二歲時候的這一年，這日期也看看等到了。不料這一年真可惜，在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    早上就叫不到船。平橋村只有一只早出晚歸的航船是大船，決沒有留用的道理。其</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    余的都是小船，不合用；央人到鄰村去問，也沒有，早都給別人定下了。外祖母很</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    氣惱，怪家里的人不早定，絮叨起來。母親便寬慰伊，說我們魯鎮的戲比小村里的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    好得多，一年看幾回，今天就算了。只有我急得要哭，母親卻竭力的囑咐我，說萬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不能裝模裝樣，怕又招外祖母生氣，又不準和別人一同去，說是怕外祖母要擔心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    總之，是完了。到下午，我的朋友都去了，戲已經開場了，我似乎听到鑼鼓的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    聲音，而且知道他們在戲台下買豆漿喝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這一天我不釣蝦，東西也少吃。母親很為難，沒有法子想。到晚飯時候，外祖</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    母也終于覺察了，並且說我應當不高興，他們太怠慢，是待客的禮數里從來沒有的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    吃飯之後，看過戲的少年們也都聚攏來了，高高興興的來講戲。只有我不開口；他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    們都嘆息而且表同情。忽然間，一個最聰明的雙喜大悟似的提議了，他說，“大船？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    八叔的航船不是回來了麼？”十幾個別的少年也大悟，立刻攛掇起來，說可以坐了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這航船和我一同去。我高興了。然而外祖母又怕都是孩子，不可靠；母親又說是若</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    叫大人一同去，他們白天全有工作，要他熬夜，是不合情理的。在這遲疑之中，雙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    喜可又看出底細來了，便又大聲的說道，“我寫包票！船又大；迅哥兒向來不亂跑；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我們又都是識水性的！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    誠然！這十多個少年，委實沒有一個不會鳧水的，而且兩三個還是弄潮的好手。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    外祖母和母親也相信，便不再駁回，都微笑了。我們立刻一哄的出了門。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我的很重的心忽而輕松了，身體也似乎舒展到說不出的大。一出門，便望見月</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    下的平橋內泊著一只白篷的航船，大家跳下船，雙喜拔前篙，阿發拔後篙，年幼的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都陪我坐在艙中，較大的聚在船尾。母親送出來吩咐“要小心”的時候，我們已經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    點開船，在橋石上一磕，退後幾尺，即又上前出了橋。于是架起兩支櫓，一支兩人，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一里一換，有說笑的，有嚷的，夾著潺潺的船頭激水的聲音，在左右都是碧綠的豆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    麥田地的河流中，飛一般徑向趙莊前進了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    兩岸的豆麥和河底的水草所發散出來的清香，夾雜在水氣中撲面的吹來；月色</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便朦朧在這水氣里。淡黑的起伏的連山，仿佛是踴躍的鐵的獸脊似的，都遠遠的向</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    船尾跑去了，但我卻還以為船慢。他們換了四回手，漸望見依稀的趙莊，而且似乎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    听到歌吹了，還有幾點火，料想便是戲台，但或者也許是漁火。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那聲音大概是橫笛，宛轉，悠揚，使我的心也沉靜，然而又自失起來，覺得要</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    和他彌散在含著豆麥蘊藻之香的夜氣里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那火接近了，果然是漁火；我才記得先前望見的也不是趙莊。那是正對船頭的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一叢松柏林，我去年也曾經去游玩過，還看見破的石馬倒在地下，一個石羊蹲在草</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    里呢。過了那林，船便彎進了叉港，于是趙莊便真在眼前了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    最惹眼的是屹立在莊外臨河的空地上的一座戲台，模胡在遠處的月夜中，和空</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    間幾乎分不出界限，我疑心畫上見過的仙境，就在這里出現了。這時船走得更快，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不多時，在台上顯出人物來，紅紅綠綠的動，近台的河里一望烏黑的是看戲的人家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的船篷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “近台沒有什麼空了，我們遠遠的看罷。”阿發說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這時船慢了，不久就到，果然近不得台旁，大家只能下了篙，比那正對戲台的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    神棚還要遠。其實我們這白篷的航船，本也不願意和烏篷的船在一處，而況沒有空</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    地呢……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在停船的匆忙中，看見台上有一個黑的長胡子的背上插著四張旗，捏著長槍，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    和一群赤膊的人正打仗。雙喜說，那就是有名的鐵頭老生，能連翻八十四個筋斗，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他日里親自數過的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我們便都擠在船頭上看打仗，但那鐵頭老生卻又並不翻筋斗，只有幾個赤膊的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    人翻，翻了一陣，都進去了，接著走出一個小旦來，咿咿呀呀的唱。雙喜說，“晚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    上看客少，鐵頭老生也懈了，誰肯顯本領給白地看呢？”我相信這話對，因為其時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    台下已經不很有人，鄉下人為了明天的工作，熬不得夜，早都睡覺去了，疏疏朗朗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的站著的不過是幾十個本村和鄰村的閑漢。烏篷船里的那些土財主的家眷固然在，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然而他們也不在乎看戲，多半是專到戲台下來吃糕餅水果和瓜子的。所以簡直可以</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    算白地。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然而我的意思卻也並不在乎看翻筋斗。我最願意看的是一個人蒙了白布，兩手</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在頭上捧著一支棒似的蛇頭的蛇精，其次是套了黃布衣跳老虎。但是等了許多時都</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不見，小旦雖然進去了，立刻又出來了一個很老的小生。我有些疲倦了，托桂生買</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    豆漿去。他去了一刻，回來說，“沒有。賣豆漿的聾子也回去了。日里倒有，我還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    喝了兩碗呢。現在去舀一瓢水來給你喝罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我不喝水，支撐著仍然看，也說不出見了些什麼，只覺得戲子的臉都漸漸的有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    些稀奇了，那五官漸不明顯，似乎融成一片的再沒有什麼高低。年紀小的幾個多打</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    呵欠了，大的也各管自己談話。忽而一個紅衫的小丑被綁在台柱子上，給一個花白</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    胡子的用馬鞭打起來了，大家才又振作精神的笑著看。在這一夜里，我以為這實在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    要算是最好的一折。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然而老旦終于出台了。老旦本來是我所最怕的東西，尤其是怕他坐下了唱。這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    時候，看見大家也都很掃興，才知道他們的意見是和我一致的。那老旦當初還只是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    踱來踱去的唱，後來竟在中間的一把交椅上坐下了。我很擔心；雙喜他們卻就破口</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    喃喃的罵。我忍耐的等著，許多工夫，只見那老旦將手一抬，我以為就要站起來了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不料他卻又慢慢的放下在原地方，仍舊唱。全船里幾個人不住的吁氣，其余的也打</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    起哈欠來。雙喜終于熬不住了，說道，怕他會唱到天明還不完，還是我們走的好罷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大家立刻都贊成，和開船時候一樣踴躍，三四人徑奔船尾，拔了篙，點退幾丈，回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    轉船頭，駕起櫓，罵著老旦，又向那松柏林前進了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    月還沒有落，仿佛看戲也並不很久似的，而一離趙莊，月光又顯得格外的皎潔。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    回望戲台在燈火光中，卻又如初來未到時候一般，又漂渺得像一座仙山樓閣，滿被</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    紅霞罩著了。吹到耳邊來的又是橫笛，很悠揚；我疑心老旦已經進去了，但也不好</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002236": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002236",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    意思說再回去看。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002237": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002237",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不多久，松柏林早在船後了，船行也並不慢，但周圍的黑暗只是濃，可知已經</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002238": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002238",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    到了深夜。他們一面議論著戲子，或罵，或笑，一面加緊的搖船。這一次船頭的激</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002239": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002239",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    水聲更其響亮了，那航船，就像一條大白魚背著一群孩子在浪花里躥，連夜漁的幾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002240": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002240",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    個老漁父，也停了艇子看著喝采起來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002241": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    離平橋村還有一里模樣，船行卻慢了，搖船的都說很疲乏，因為太用力，而且</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002242": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002242",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    許久沒有東西吃。這回想出來的是桂生，說是羅漢豆き正旺相，柴火又現成，我們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002243": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002243",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    可以偷一點來煮吃。大家都贊成，立刻近岸停了船；岸上的田里，烏油油的都是結</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002244": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002244",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    實的羅漢豆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002245": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002245",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “阿阿，阿發，這邊是你家的，這邊是老六一家的，我們偷那一邊的呢？”雙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002246": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002246",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    喜先跳下去了，在岸上說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002247": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002247",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我們也都跳上岸。阿發一面跳，一面說道，“且慢，讓我來看一看罷，”他于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002248": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002248",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是往來的摸了一回，直起身來說道，“偷我們的罷，我們的大得多呢。”一聲答應，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002249": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002249",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大家便散開在阿發家的豆田里，各摘了一大捧，拋入船艙中。雙喜以為再多偷，倘</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002250": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002250",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    給阿發的娘知道是要哭罵的，于是各人便到六一公公的田里又各偷了一大捧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002251": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002251",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我們中間幾個年長的仍然慢慢的搖著船，幾個到後艙去生火，年幼的和我都剝</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002252": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002252",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    豆。不久豆熟了，便任憑航船浮在水面上，都圍起來用手撮著吃。吃完豆，又開船，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002253": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002253",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一面洗器具，豆莢豆殼全拋在河水里，什麼痕跡也沒有了。雙喜所慮的是用了八公</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002254": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002254",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    公船上的鹽和柴，這老頭子很細心，一定要知道，會罵的。然而大家議論之後，歸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002255": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002255",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    結是不怕。他如果罵，我們便要他歸還去年在岸邊拾去的一枝枯　樹，而且當面叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002256": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002256",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他“八癩子”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002257": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002257",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “都回來了！那里會錯。我原說過寫包票的！”雙喜在船頭上忽而大聲的說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002258": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002258",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我向船頭一望，前面已經是平橋。橋腳上站著一個人，卻是我的母親，雙喜便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002259": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002259",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是對伊說著話。我走出前艙去，船也就進了平橋了，停了船，我們紛紛都上岸。母</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002260": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002260",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    親頗有些生氣，說是過了三更了，怎麼回來得這樣遲，但也就高興了，笑著邀大家</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002261": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002261",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    去吃炒米。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002262": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002262",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大家都說已經吃了點心，又渴睡，不如及早睡的好，各自回去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002263": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002263",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第二天，我向午才起來，並沒有听到什麼關系八公公鹽柴事件的糾葛，下午仍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002264": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002264",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然去釣蝦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002265": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002265",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “雙喜，你們這班小鬼，昨天偷了我的豆了罷？又不肯好好的摘，蹋壞了不少。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002266": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002266",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我抬頭看時，是六一公公棹著小船，賣了豆回來了，船肚里還有剩下的一堆豆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002267": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002267",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “是的。我們請客。我們當初還不要你的呢。你看，你把我的蝦嚇跑了！”雙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002268": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002268",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    喜說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002269": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002269",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    六一公公看見我，便停了楫，笑道，“請客？——這是應該的。”于是對我說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “迅哥兒，昨天的戲可好麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我點一點頭，說道，“好。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “豆可中吃呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我又點一點頭，說道，“很好。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不料六一公公竟非常感激起來，將大拇指一翹，得意的說道，“這真是大市鎮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    里出來的讀過書的人才識貨！我的豆種是粒粒挑選過的，鄉下人不識好歹，還說我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的豆比不上別人的呢。我今天也要送些給我們的姑奶奶嘗嘗去……”他于是打著楫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    子過去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    待到母親叫我回去吃晚飯的時候，桌上便有一大碗煮熟了的羅漢豆，就是六一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    公公送給母親和我吃的。听說他還對母親極口夸獎我，說“小小年紀便有見識，將</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來一定要中狀元。姑奶奶，你的福氣是可以寫包票的了。”但我吃了豆，卻並沒有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    昨夜的豆那麼好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    真的，一直到現在，我實在再沒有吃到那夜似的好豆，——也不再看到那夜似</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的好戲了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一九二二年十月。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九二二年十二月上海《小說月報》第十三卷第十二號。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え譚叫天（1847—1917）︰即譚鑫培，又稱小叫天，當時的京劇演員，擅長老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    生戲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ目連︰釋迦牟尼的弟子。據《盂蘭盆經》說，目連的母親因生前違犯佛教戒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    律，墮入地獄，他曾入地獄救母。《目連救母》一劇，舊時在民間很流行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お龔雲甫（1862—1932）︰當時的京劇演員，擅長老旦戲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か“秩秩斯干幽幽南山”︰語見《詩經•小雅•斯干》。據漢代鄭玄注︰“秩</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    秩，流行也；干，澗也；幽幽，深遠也。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    が社戲︰“社”原指土地神或土地廟。在紹興，社是一種區域名稱，社戲就是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    社中每年所演的“年規戲”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    き羅漢豆︰即蠶豆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ﹝《吶喊》﹞</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    打字︰諸葛不亮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p> 風波</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    臨河的土場上，太陽漸漸的收了他通黃的光線了。場邊靠河的烏　樹葉，干巴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    巴的才喘過氣來，幾個花腳蚊子在下面哼著飛舞。面河的農家的煙突里，逐漸減少</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了炊煙，女人孩子們都在自己門口的土場上波些水，放下小桌子和矮凳；人知道，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這已經是晚飯的時候了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老人男人坐在矮凳上，搖著大芭蕉扇閑談，孩子飛也似的跑，或者蹲在烏　樹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    下賭玩石子。女人端出烏黑的蒸干菜和松花黃的米飯，熱蓬蓬冒煙。河里駛過文人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的酒船，文豪見了，大發詩興，說，“無思無慮，這真是田家樂呵！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但文豪的話有些不合事實，就因為他們沒有听到九斤老太的話。這時候，九斤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老太正在大怒，拿破芭蕉扇敲著凳腳說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我活到七十九歲了，活夠了，不願意眼見這些敗家相，——還是死的好。立</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    刻就要吃飯了，還吃炒豆子，吃窮了一家子！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    伊的曾孫女兒六斤捏著一把豆，正從對面跑來，見這情形，便直奔河邊，藏在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    烏　樹後，伸出雙丫角的小頭，大聲說，“這老不死的！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    九斤老太雖然高壽，耳朵卻還不很聾，但也沒有听到孩子的話，仍舊自己說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這真是一代不如一代！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這村莊的習慣有點特別，女人生下孩子，多喜歡用秤稱了輕重，便用斤數當作</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    小名。九斤老太自從慶祝了五十大壽以後，便漸漸的變了不平家，常說伊年青的時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    候，天氣沒有現在這般熱，豆子也沒有現在這般硬；總之現在的時世是不對了。何</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    況六斤比伊的曾祖，少了三斤，比伊父親七斤，又少了一斤，這真是一條顛撲不破</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的實例。所以伊又用勁說，“這真是一代不如一代！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    伊的兒媳え七斤嫂子正捧著飯籃走到桌邊，便將飯籃在桌上一摔，憤憤的說，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你老人家又這麼說了。六斤生下來的時候，不是六斤五兩麼？你家的秤又是私秤，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    加重稱，十八兩秤；用了準十六，我們的六斤該有七斤多哩。我想便是太公和公公，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也不見得正是九斤八斤十足，用的秤也許是十四兩……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “一代不如一代！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤嫂還沒有答話，忽然看見七斤從小巷口轉出，便移了方向，對他嚷道，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你這死尸怎麼這時候才回來，死到那里去了！不管人家等著你開飯！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤雖然住在農村，卻早有些飛黃騰達的意思。從他的祖父到他，三代不捏鋤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    頭柄了；他也照例的幫人撐著航船，每日一回，早晨從魯鎮進城，傍晚又回到魯鎮，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    因此很知道些時事︰例如什麼地方，雷公劈死了蜈蚣精；什麼地方，閨女生了一個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    夜叉之類。他在村人里面，的確已經是一名出場人物了。但夏天吃飯不點燈，卻還</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    守著農家習慣，所以回家太遲，是該罵的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤一手捏著象牙嘴白銅斗六尺多長的湘妃竹煙管，低著頭，慢慢地走來，坐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在矮凳上。六斤也趁勢溜出，坐在他身邊，叫他爹爹。七斤沒有應。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “一代不如一代！”九斤老太說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤慢慢地抬起頭來，嘆一口氣說，“皇帝坐了龍庭了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤嫂呆了一刻，忽而恍然大悟的道，“這可好了，這不是又要皇恩大赦了麼！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤又嘆一口氣，說，“我沒有辮子。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “皇帝要辮子麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “皇帝要辮子。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你怎麼知道呢？”七斤嫂有些著急，趕忙的問。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “咸亨酒店里的人，都說要的。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤嫂這時從直覺上覺得事情似乎有些不妙了，因為咸亨酒店是消息靈通的所</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在。伊一轉眼瞥見七斤的光頭，便忍不住動怒，怪他恨他怨他；忽然又絕望起來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    裝好一碗飯，搡在七斤的面前道，“還是趕快吃你的飯罷！哭喪著臉，就會長出辮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    子來麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    太陽收盡了他最末的光線了，水面暗暗地回復過涼氣來；土場上一片碗筷聲響，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    人人的脊梁上又都吐出汗粒。七斤嫂吃完三碗飯，偶然抬起頭，心坎里便禁不住突</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    突地發跳。伊透過烏　葉，看見又矮又胖的趙七爺正從獨木橋上走來，而且穿著寶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    藍色竹布的長衫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    趙七爺是鄰村茂源酒店的主人，又是這三十里方圓以內的唯一的出色人物兼學</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    問家；因為有學問，所以又有些遺老的臭味。他有十多本金聖嘆批評的《三國志》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ，時常坐著一個字一個字的讀；他不但能說出五虎將姓名，甚而至于還知道黃忠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    表字漢升和馬超表字孟起。革命以後，他便將辮子盤在頂上，像道士一般；常常嘆</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    息說，倘若趙子龍在世，天下便不會亂到這地步了。七斤嫂眼楮好，早望見今天的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    趙七爺已經不是道士，卻變成光滑頭皮，烏黑發頂；伊便知道這一定是皇帝坐了龍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    庭，而且一定須有辮子，而且七斤一定是非常危險。因為趙七爺的這件竹布長衫，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    輕易是不常穿的，三年以來，只穿過兩次︰一次是和他嘔氣的麻子阿四病了的時候，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一次是曾經砸爛他酒店的魯大爺死了的時候；現在是第三次了，這一定又是于他有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    慶，于他的仇家有殃了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤嫂記得，兩年前七斤喝醉了酒，曾經罵過趙七爺是“賤胎”，所以這時便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    立刻直覺到七斤的危險，心坎里突突地發起跳來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    趙七爺一路走來，坐著吃飯的人都站起身，拿筷子點著自己的飯碗說，“七爺，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    請在我們這里用飯！”七爺也一路點頭，說道“請請”，卻一徑走到七斤家的桌旁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤們連忙招呼，七爺也微笑著說“請請”，一面細細的研究他們的飯菜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “好香的菜干，——听到了風聲了麼？”趙七爺站在七斤的後面七斤嫂的對面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “皇帝坐了龍庭了。”七斤說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤嫂看著七爺的臉，竭力陪笑道，“皇帝已經坐了龍庭，幾時皇恩大赦呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “皇恩大赦？——大赦是慢慢的總要大赦罷。”七爺說到這里，聲色忽然嚴厲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    起來，“但是你家七斤的辮子呢，辮子？這倒是要緊的事。你們知道︰長毛時候，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    留發不留頭，留頭不留發，……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤和他的女人沒有讀過書，不很懂得這古典的奧妙，但覺得有學問的七爺這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    麼說，事情自然非常重大，無可挽回，便仿佛受了死刑宣告似的，耳朵里嗡的一聲，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    再也說不出一句話。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “一代不如一代，——”九斤老太正在不平，趁這機會，便對趙七爺說，“現</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在的長毛，只是剪人家的辮子，僧不僧，道不道的。從前的長毛，這樣的麼？我活</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    到七十九歲了，活夠了。從前的長毛是——整匹的紅緞子裹頭，拖下去，拖下去，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一直拖到腳跟；王爺是黃緞子，拖下去，黃緞子；紅緞子，黃緞子，——我活夠了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七十九歲了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤嫂站起身，自言自語的說，“這怎麼好呢？這樣的一班老小，都靠他養活</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的人，……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    趙七爺搖頭道，“那也沒法。沒有辮子，該當何罪，書上都一條一條明明白白</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    寫著的。不管他家里有些什麼人。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤嫂听到書上寫著，可真是完全絕望了；自己急得沒法，便忽然又恨到七斤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    伊用筷子指著他的鼻尖說，“這死尸自作自受！造反的時候，我本來說，不要撐船</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了，不要上城了。他偏要死進城去，滾進城去，進城便被人剪去了辮子。從前是絹</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    光烏黑的辮子，現在弄得僧不僧道不道的。這囚徒自作自受，帶累了我們又怎麼說</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    呢？這活死尸的囚徒……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    村人看見趙七爺到村，都趕緊吃完飯，聚在七斤家飯桌的周圍。七斤自己知道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是出場人物，被女人當大眾這樣辱罵，很不雅觀，便只得抬起頭，慢慢地說道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你今天說現成話，那時你……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你這活死尸的囚徒……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    看客中間，八一嫂是心腸最好的人，抱著伊的兩周歲的遺腹子，正在七斤嫂身</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    邊看熱鬧；這時過意不去，連忙解勸說，“七斤嫂，算了罷。人不是神仙，誰知道</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    未來事呢？便是七斤嫂，那時不也說，沒有辮子倒也沒有什麼丑麼？況且衙門里的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大老爺也還沒有告示，……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤嫂沒有听完，兩個耳朵早通紅了；便將筷子轉過向來，指著八一嫂的鼻子，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    說，“阿呀，這是什麼話呵！八一嫂，我自己看來倒還是一個人，會說出這樣昏誕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    胡涂話麼？那時我是，整整哭了三天，誰都看見；連六斤這小鬼也都哭，……”六</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    斤剛吃完一大碗飯，拿了空碗，伸手去嚷著要添。七斤嫂正沒好氣，便用筷子在伊</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的雙丫角中間，直扎下去，大喝道，“誰要你來多嘴！你這偷漢的小寡婦！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    撲的一聲，六斤手里的空碗落在地上了，恰巧又踫著一塊磚角，立刻破成一個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    很大的缺口。七斤直跳起來，撿起破碗，合上檢查一回，也喝道，“入娘的！”一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    巴掌打倒了六斤。六斤躺著哭，九斤老太拉了伊的手，連說著“一代不如一代”，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一同走了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    八一嫂也發怒，大聲說，“七斤嫂，你‘恨棒打人’……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    趙七爺本來是笑著旁觀的；但自從八一嫂說了“衙門里的大老爺沒有告示”這</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    話以後，卻有些生氣了。這時他已經繞出桌旁，接著說，“‘恨棒打人’，算什麼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    呢。大兵是就要到的。你可知道，這回保駕的是張大帥お，張大帥就是燕人張翼德</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的後代，他一支丈八蛇矛，就有萬夫不當之勇，誰能抵擋他，”他兩手同時捏起空</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    拳，仿佛握著無形的蛇矛模樣，向八一嫂搶進幾步道，“你能抵擋他麼！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    八一嫂正氣得抱著孩子發抖，忽然見趙七爺滿臉油汗，瞪著眼，準對伊沖過來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便十分害怕，不敢說完話，回身走了。趙七爺也跟著走去，眾人一面怪八一嫂多事，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一面讓開路，幾個剪過辮子重新留起的便趕快躲在人叢後面，怕他看見。趙七爺也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不細心察訪，通過人叢，忽然轉入烏　樹後，說道“你能抵擋他麼！”跨上獨木橋，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    揚長去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    村人們呆呆站著，心里計算，都覺得自己確乎抵不住張翼德，因此也決定七斤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便要沒有性命。七斤既然犯了皇法，想起他往常對人談論城中的新聞的時候，就不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    該含著長煙管顯出那般驕傲模樣，所以對七斤的犯法，也覺得有些暢快。他們也仿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    佛想發些議論，卻又覺得沒有什麼議論可發。嗡嗡的一陣亂嚷，蚊子都撞過赤膊身</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    子，闖到烏　樹下去做市；他們也就慢慢地走散回家，關上門去睡覺。七斤嫂咕噥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    著，也收了家伙和桌子矮凳回家，關上門睡覺了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    七斤將破碗拿回家里，坐在門檻上吸煙；但非常憂愁，忘卻了吸煙，象牙嘴六</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    尺多長湘妃竹煙管的白銅斗里的火光，漸漸發黑了。他心里但覺得事情似乎十分危</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    急，也想想些方法，想些計畫，但總是非常模糊，貫穿不得︰“辮子呢辮子？丈八</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    蛇矛。一代不如一代！皇帝坐龍庭。破的碗須得上城去釘好。誰能抵擋他？書上一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    條一條寫著。入娘的！……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第二日清晨，七斤依舊從魯鎮撐航船進城，傍晚回到魯鎮，又拿著六尺多長的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    湘妃竹煙管和一個飯碗回村。他在晚飯席上，對九斤老太說，這碗是在城內釘合的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    因為缺口大，所以要十六個銅釘，三文一個，一總用了四十八文小錢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    九斤老太很不高興的說，“一代不如一代，我是活夠了。三文錢一個釘；從前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的釘，這樣的麼？從前的釘是……我活了七十九歲了，——”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    此後七斤雖然是照例日日進城，但家景總有些黯淡，村人大抵回避著，不再來</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    听他從城內得來的新聞。七斤嫂也沒有好聲氣，還時常叫他“囚徒”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    過了十多日，七斤從城內回家，看見他的女人非常高興，問他說，“你在城里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    可听到些什麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “沒有听到些什麼。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “皇帝坐了龍庭沒有呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “他們沒有說。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “咸亨酒店里也沒有人說麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “也沒人說。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我想皇帝一定是不坐龍庭了。我今天走過趙七爺的店前，看見他又坐著念書</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了，辮子又盤在頂上了，也沒有穿長衫。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “…………”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你想，不坐龍庭了罷？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我想，不坐了罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    現在的七斤，是七斤嫂和村人又都早給他相當的尊敬，相當的待遇了。到夏天，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們仍舊在自家門口的土場上吃飯；大家見了，都笑嘻嘻的招呼。九斤老太早已做</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    過八十大壽，仍然不平而且健康。六斤的雙丫角，已經變成一支大辮子了；伊雖然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    新近裹腳，卻還能幫同七斤嫂做事，捧著十八個銅釘か的飯碗，在土場上一瘸一拐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的往來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一九二○年十月。が</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九二○年九月《新青年》第八卷第一號。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え伊的兒媳︰從上下文看，這里的“兒媳”應是“孫媳”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ金聖嘆批評的《三國志》︰指小說《三國演義》。金聖嘆（1609—1661），</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    明末清初文人，曾批注《水滸》、《西廂記》等書，他把所加的序文、讀法和評語</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    等稱為“聖嘆外書”。《三國演義》是元末明初羅貫中所著，後經清代毛宗崗改編，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    附加評語，卷首有假托為金聖嘆所作的序，首回前亦有“聖嘆外書”字樣，通常就</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都把這評語認為金聖嘆所作。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お張大帥︰指張勛（1854—1923），江西奉新人，北洋軍閥之一。原為清朝軍</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    官，辛亥革命後，他和所部官兵仍留著辮子，表示忠于清王朝，被稱為辮子軍。一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    九一七年七月一日他在北京扶持清廢帝溥儀復闢，七月十二日即告失敗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か十八個銅釘︰據上文應是“十六個”。作者在一九二六年十一月二十三日致</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    李霽野的信中曾說︰“六斤家只有這一個釘過的碗，釘是十六或十八，我也記不清</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了。總之兩數之一是錯的，請改成一律。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    が據《魯迅日記》，本篇當作于一九二○年八月五日。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    輸入︰諸葛不亮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p> 頭發的故事</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    星期日的早晨，我揭去一張隔夜的日歷，向著新的那一張上看了又看的說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “阿，十月十日，——今天原來正是雙十節え。這里卻一點沒有記載！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    我的一位前輩先生N，正走到我的寓里來談閑天，一听這話，便很不高興的對我</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “他們對！他們不記得，你怎樣他；你記得，又怎樣呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    這位N先生本來脾氣有點乖張，時常生些無謂的氣，說些不通世故的話。當這時</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    候，我大抵任他自言自語，不贊一辭；他獨自發完議論，也就算了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我最佩服北京雙十節的情形。早晨，警察到門，吩咐道‘掛旗！’‘是，掛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    旗！’各家大半懶洋洋的踱出一個國民來，撅起一塊斑駁陸離的洋布ぉ。這樣一直</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    到夜，——收了旗關門；幾家偶然忘卻的，便掛到第二天的上午。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “他們忘卻了紀念，紀念也忘卻了他們！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我也是忘卻了紀念的一個人。倘使紀念起來，那第一個雙十節前後的事，便</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    都上我的心頭，使我坐立不穩了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “多少故人的臉，都浮在我眼前。幾個少年辛苦奔走了十多年，暗地里一顆彈</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    丸要了他的性命；幾個少年一擊不中，在監牢里身受一個多月的苦刑；幾個少年懷</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    著遠志，忽然蹤影全無，連尸首也不知那里去了。——</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “他們都在社會的冷笑惡罵迫害傾陷里過了一生；現在他們的墳墓也早在忘卻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    里漸漸平塌下去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我不堪紀念這些事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我們還是記起一點得意的事來談談罷。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    N忽然現出笑容，伸手在自己頭上一摸，高聲說︰</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我最得意的是自從第一個雙十節以後，我在路上走，不再被人笑罵了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “老兄，你可知道頭發是我們中國人的寶貝和冤家，古今來多少人在這上頭吃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    些毫無價值的苦呵！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我們的很古的古人，對于頭發似乎也還看輕。據刑法看來，最要緊的自然是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    腦袋，所以大闢是上刑；次要便是生殖器了，所以宮刑和幽閉也是一件嚇人的罰；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    至于髡，那是微乎其微了，お然而推想起來，正不知道曾有多少人們因為光著頭皮</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便被社會踐踏了一生世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我們講革命的時候，大談什麼揚州三日，嘉定屠城か，其實也不過一種手段；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老實說︰那時中國人的反抗，何嘗因為亡國，只是因為拖辮子が。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “頑民殺盡了，遺老都壽終了，辮子早留定了，洪楊き又鬧起來了。我的祖母</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    曾對我說，那時做百姓才難哩，全留著頭發的被官兵殺，還是辮子的便被長毛殺！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我不知道有多少中國人只因為這不痛不癢的頭發而吃苦，受難，滅亡。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    N兩眼望著屋梁，似乎想些事，仍然說︰</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “誰知道頭發的苦輪到我了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我出去留學，便剪掉了辮子，這並沒有別的奧妙，只為他不太便當罷了。不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    料有幾位辮子盤在頭頂上的同學們便很厭惡我；監督也大怒，說要停了我的官費，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    送回中國去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “不幾天，這位監督卻自己被人剪去辮子逃走了。去剪的人們里面，一個便是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    做《革命軍》的鄒容ぎ，這人也因此不能再留學，回到上海來，後來死在西牢里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    你也早忘卻了罷？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “過了幾年，我的家景大不如前了，非謀點事做便要受餓，只得也回到中國來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我一到上海，便買定一條假辮子，那時是二元的市價，帶著回家。我的母親倒也不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    說什麼，然而旁人一見面，便都首先研究這辮子，待到知道是假，就一聲冷笑，將</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我擬為殺頭的罪名；有一位本家，還預備去告官，但後來因為恐怕革命黨的造反或</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    者要成功，這才中止了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我想，假的不如真的直截爽快，我便索性廢了假辮子，穿著西裝在街上走。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “一路走去，一路便是笑罵的聲音，有的還跟在後面罵︰‘這冒失鬼！’‘假</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    洋鬼子！’</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我于是不穿洋服了，改了大衫，他們罵得更利害。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “在這日暮途窮的時候，我的手里才添出一支手杖來，拚命的打了幾回，他們</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    漸漸的不罵了。只是走到沒有打過的生地方還是罵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這件事很使我悲哀，至今還時時記得哩。我在留學的時候，曾經看見日報上</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    登載一個游歷南洋和中國的本多博士く的事；這位博士是不懂中國和馬來語的，人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    問他，你不懂話，怎麼走路呢？他拿起手杖來說，這便是他們的話，他們都懂！我</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    因此氣憤了好幾天，誰知道我竟不知不覺的自己也做了，而且那些人都懂了。……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “宣統初年，我在本地的中學校做監學ぐ，同事是避之惟恐不遠，官僚是防之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    惟恐不嚴，我終日如坐在冰窖子里，如站在刑場旁邊，其實並非別的，只因為缺少</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了一條辮子！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “有一日，幾個學生忽然走到我的房里來，說，‘先生，我們要剪辮子了。’</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我說，‘不行！’‘有辮子好呢，沒有辮子好呢？’‘沒有辮子好……’‘你怎麼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    說不行呢？’‘犯不上，你們還是不剪上算，——等一等罷。’他們不說什麼，撅</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    著嘴唇走出房去，然而終于剪掉了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “呵！不得了了，人言嘖嘖了；我卻只裝作不知道，一任他們光著頭皮，和許</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    多辮子一齊上講堂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “然而這剪辮病傳染了；第三天，師範學堂的學生忽然也剪下了六條辮子，晚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    上便開除了六個學生。這六個人，留校不能，回家不得，一直挨到第一個雙十節之</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    後又一個多月，才消去了犯罪的火烙印。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我呢？也一樣，只是元年冬天到北京，還被人罵過幾次，後來罵我的人也被</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    警察剪去了辮子，我就不再被人辱罵了；但我沒有到鄉間去。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    N顯出非常得意模樣，忽而又沉下臉來︰</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “現在你們這些理想家，又在那里嚷什麼女子剪發了，又要造出許多毫無所得</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而痛苦的人！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “現在不是已經有剪掉頭發的女人，因此考不進學校去，或者被學校除了名麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “改革麼，武器在那里？工讀麼，工廠在那里？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “仍然留起，嫁給人家做媳婦去︰忘卻了一切還是幸福，倘使伊記著些平等自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    由的話，便要苦痛一生世！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我要借了阿爾志跋綏夫　的話問你們︰你們將黃金時代的出現豫約給這些人</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    們的子孫了，但有什麼給這些人們自己呢？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “阿，造物的皮鞭沒有到中國的脊梁上時，中國便永遠是這一樣的中國，決不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    肯自己改變一支毫毛！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你們的嘴里既然並無毒牙，何以偏要在額上帖起‘蝮蛇’兩個大字，引乞丐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來打殺？……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><h5>    N愈說愈離奇了，但一見到我不很願听的神情，便立刻閉了口，站起來取帽子。</h5></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我說，“回去麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他答道，“是的，天要下雨了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    我默默的送他到門口。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他戴上帽子說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “再見！請你恕我打攪，好在明天便不是雙十節，我們統可以忘卻了。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一九二○年十月。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九二○年十月十日上海《時事新報•學燈》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え雙十節︰一九一一年十月十日孫中山領導的革命黨舉行了武昌起義（即辛亥</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    革命），次年一月一日建立中華民國，九月二十八日臨時參議院議決十月十日為國</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    慶紀念日，又稱“雙十節”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ斑駁陸離的洋布︰指辛亥革命後至一九二七年這一時期舊中國的國旗，也叫</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    五色旗（紅黃藍白黑五色橫列）。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お關于我國古代刑法，據《尚書•呂刑》及相關的注解，分為五等︰一是墨刑，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    即“先刻其面，以墨窒之”；二是劓刑，即“截鼻”；三是﹝非}﹞刑，即“斷足”；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    四是宮刑，即“男子割勢，婦人幽閉”（按︰指破壞生殖器官）；五是大闢，即斬</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    首。“去發”的髡刑不在五刑之內，但也是一種刑罰，自隋、唐以後已廢止。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か揚州十日，嘉定屠城︰前者指清順治二年（1645）清軍攻破揚州後進行的十</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    天大屠殺；後者指同年清軍佔領嘉定（今屬上海市）後進行的多次屠殺。清代王秀</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    楚著《揚州十日記》、朱子素著《嘉定屠城記略》，分別記載了當時清兵在這兩地</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    屠殺的情況。辛亥革命前，革命者曾大量翻印這些書籍，為推翻清王朝作輿論準備。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    が拖辮子︰我國滿族舊俗，男子剃發垂辮（剃去頭頂前部頭發，後部結辮垂于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    腦後）。一六四四年清世祖進入北京以後，幾次下令強迫人民遵從滿族發式，這一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    措施曾引起漢族人民的強烈反抗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    き洪楊︰洪，指洪秀全（1814—1864），廣東花縣人；楊，指楊秀清（1820？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    —1856），廣西桂平人。二人都是太平天國的領袖。他們領導的起義軍都留發而不</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    結辮，被稱為“長毛”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぎ鄒容（1885—1905）︰字蔚丹，四川巴縣人，清末革命家。一九○二年留學</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    日本，積極宣傳反清革命思想；一九○三年回國後，著《革命軍》一書鼓吹革命。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    同年七月被清政府勾結上海英租界當局拘捕，判處監禁二年，一九○五年四月死于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    獄中。關于鄒容等剪留學生監督辮子一事，據章太炎所著《鄒容傳》記載︰鄒容在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    日本留學時，“陸軍學生監督姚甲有奸私事，容偕五人排闥入其邸中，榜頰數十，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    持剪刀斷其辮發。事覺，潛歸上海。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    く本多博士︰即本多靜六（1866—1952），日本林學博士，著有《造林學》等</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    書。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぐ監學︰清末學校中負責管理學生的職員，一般也兼任教學工作。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    　阿爾志跋綏夫（1878—1927）︰俄國小說家。十月革命後逃亡國外，死于波</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    蘭華沙。這里所引的話，見他的中篇小說《工人綏惠略夫》第九章。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p> 明天</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “沒有聲音，——小東西怎了？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    紅鼻子老拱手里擎了一碗黃酒，說著，向間壁努一努嘴。藍皮阿五便放下酒碗，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在他脊梁上用死勁的打了一掌，含含糊糊嚷道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “你……你你又在想心思……。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    原來魯鎮是僻靜地方，還有些古風︰不上一更，大家便都關門睡覺。深更半夜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    沒有睡的只有兩家︰一家是咸亨酒店，幾個酒肉朋友圍著櫃台，吃喝得正高興；一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    家便是間壁的單四嫂子，他自從前年守了寡，便須專靠著自己的一雙手紡出綿紗來，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    養活他自己和他三歲的兒子，所以睡的也遲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這幾天，確鑿沒有紡紗的聲音了。但夜深沒有睡的既然只有兩家，這單四嫂子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    家有聲音，便自然只有老拱們听到，沒有聲音，也只有老拱們听到。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老拱挨了打，仿佛很舒服似的喝了一大口酒，嗚嗚的唱起小曲來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這時候，單四嫂子正抱著他的寶兒，坐在床沿上，紡車靜靜的立在地上。黑沉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    沉的燈光，照著寶兒的臉，緋紅里帶一點青。單四嫂子心里計算︰神簽也求過了，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    願心也許過了，單方也吃過了，要是還不見效，怎麼好？——那只有去診何小仙了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但寶兒也許是日輕夜重，到了明天，太陽一出，熱也會退，氣喘也會平的︰這實在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是病人常有的事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    單四嫂子是一個粗笨女人，不明白這“但”字的可怕︰許多壞事固然幸虧有了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他才變好，許多好事卻也因為有了他都弄糟。夏天夜短，老拱們嗚嗚的唱完了不多</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    時，東方已經發白；不一會，窗縫里透進了銀白色的曙光。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    單四嫂子等候天明，卻不像別人這樣容易，覺得非常之慢，寶兒的一呼吸，幾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    乎長過一年。現在居然明亮了；天的明亮，壓倒了燈光，——看見寶兒的鼻翼，已</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    經一放一收的扇動。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    單四嫂子知道不妙，暗暗叫一聲“阿呀！”心里計算︰怎麼好？只有去診何小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    仙這一條路了。他雖然是粗笨女人，心里卻有決斷，便站起身，從木櫃子里掏出每</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    天節省下來的十三個小銀元和一百八十銅錢，都裝在衣袋里，鎖上門，抱著寶兒直</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    向何家奔過去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    天氣還早，何家已經坐著四個病人了。他摸出四角銀元，買了號簽，第五個輪</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    到寶兒。何小仙伸開兩個指頭按脈，指甲足有四寸多長，單四嫂子暗地納罕，心里</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    計算︰寶兒該有活命了。但總免不了著急，忍不住要問，便局局促促的說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “先生，——我家的寶兒什麼病呀？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “他中焦塞著え。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “不妨事麼？他……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “先去吃兩帖。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “他喘不過氣來，鼻翅子都扇著呢。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這是火克金ぉ……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    何小仙說了半句話，便閉上眼楮；單四嫂子也不好意思再問。在何小仙對面坐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    著的一個三十多歲的人，此時已經開好一張藥方，指著紙角上的幾個字說道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這第一味保嬰活命丸，須是賈家濟世老店才有！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    單四嫂子接過藥方，一面走，一面想。他雖是粗笨女人，卻知道何家與濟世老</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    店與自己的家，正是一個三角點；自然是買了藥回去便宜了。于是又徑向濟世老店</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    奔過去。店伙也翹了長指甲慢慢的看方，慢慢的包藥。單四嫂子抱了寶兒等著；寶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    兒忽然擎起小手來，用力拔他散亂著的一綹頭發，這是從來沒有的舉動，單四嫂子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    怕得發怔。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    太陽早出了。單四嫂子抱了孩子，帶著藥包，越走覺得越重；孩子又不住的掙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    扎，路也覺得越長。沒奈何坐在路旁一家公館的門檻上，休息了一會，衣服漸漸的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    冰著肌膚，才知道自己出了一身汗；寶兒卻仿佛睡著了。他再起來慢慢地走，仍然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    支撐不得，耳朵邊忽然听得人說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “單四嫂子，我替你抱勃羅！”似乎是藍皮阿五的聲音。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他抬頭看時，正是藍皮阿五，睡眼朦朧的跟著他走。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    單四嫂子在這時候，雖然很希望降下一員天將，助他一臂之力，卻不願是阿五。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但阿五有些俠氣，無論如何，總是偏要幫忙，所以推讓了一會，終于得了許可了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他便伸開臂膊，從單四嫂子的乳房和孩子之間，直伸下去，抱去了孩子。單四嫂子</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便覺乳房上發了一條熱，剎時間直熱到臉上和耳根。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們兩人離開了二尺五寸多地，一同走著。阿五說些話，單四嫂子卻大半沒有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    答。走了不多時候，阿五又將孩子還給他，說是昨天與朋友約定的吃飯時候到了；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    單四嫂子便接了孩子。幸而不遠便是家，早看見對門的王九媽在街邊坐著，遠遠地</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    說話︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “單四嫂子，孩子怎了？——看過先生了麼？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “看是看了。——王九媽，你有年紀，見的多，不如請你老法眼お看一看，怎</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    樣……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “唔……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “怎樣……？”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “唔……”王九媽端詳了一番，把頭點了兩點，搖了兩搖。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    寶兒吃下藥，已經是午後了。單四嫂子留心看他神情，似乎仿佛平穩了不少；</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    到得下午，忽然睜開眼叫一聲“媽！”又仍然合上眼，像是睡去了。他睡了一刻，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    額上鼻尖都沁出一粒一粒的汗珠，單四嫂子輕輕一摸，膠水般粘著手；慌忙去摸胸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    口，便禁不住嗚咽起來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    寶兒的呼吸從平穩到沒有，單四嫂子的聲音也就從嗚咽變成號啕。這時聚集了</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    幾堆人︰門內是王九媽藍皮阿五之類，門外是咸亨的掌櫃和紅鼻老拱之類。王九媽</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便發命令，燒了一串紙錢；又將兩條板凳和五件衣服作抵，替單四嫂子借了兩塊洋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    錢，給幫忙的人備飯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第一個問題是棺木。單四嫂子還有一副銀耳環和一支裹金的銀簪，都交給了咸</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    亨的掌櫃，托他作一個保，半現半賒的買一具棺木。藍皮阿五也伸出手來，很願意</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    自告奮勇；王九媽卻不許他，只準他明天抬棺材的差使，阿五罵了一聲“老畜生”，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    怏怏的努了嘴站著。掌櫃便自去了；晚上回來，說棺木須得現做，後半夜才成功。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    掌櫃回來的時候，幫忙的人早吃過飯；因為魯鎮還有些古風，所以不上一更，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    便都回家睡覺了。只有阿五還靠著咸亨的櫃台喝酒，老拱也嗚嗚的唱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這時候，單四嫂子坐在床沿上哭著，寶兒在床上躺著，紡車靜靜的在地上立著。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    許多工夫，單四嫂子的眼淚宣告完結了，眼楮張得很大，看看四面的情形，覺得奇</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    怪︰所有的都是不會有的事。他心里計算︰不過是夢罷了，這些事都是夢。明天醒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    過來，自己好好的睡在床上，寶兒也好好的睡在自己身邊。他也醒過來，叫一聲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “媽”，生龍活虎似的跳去玩了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    老拱的歌聲早經寂靜，咸亨也熄了燈。單四嫂子張著眼，總不信所有的事。—</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    —雞也叫了；東方漸漸發白，窗縫里透進了銀白色的曙光。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    銀白的曙光又漸漸顯出緋紅，太陽光接著照到屋脊。單四嫂子張著眼，呆呆坐</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    著；听得打門聲音，才吃了一嚇，跑出去開門。門外一個不認識的人，背了一件東</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    西；後面站著王九媽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    哦，他們背了棺材來了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    下半天，棺木才合上蓋︰因為單四嫂子哭一回，看一回，總不肯死心塌地的蓋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    上；幸虧王九媽等得不耐煩，氣憤憤的跑上前，一把拖開他，才七手八腳的蓋上了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但單四嫂子待他的寶兒，實在已經盡了心，再沒有什麼缺陷。昨天燒過一串紙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    錢，上午又燒了四十九卷《大悲咒》か；收斂的時候，給他穿上頂新的衣裳，平日</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    喜歡的玩意兒，——一個泥人，兩個小木碗，兩個玻璃瓶，——都放在枕頭旁邊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    後來王九媽掐著指頭子細推敲，也終于想不出一些什麼缺陷。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這一日里，藍皮阿五簡直整天沒有到；咸亨掌櫃便替單四嫂子雇了兩名腳夫，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    每名二百另十個大錢，抬棺木到義冢地上安放。王九媽又幫他煮了飯，凡是動過手</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    開過口的人都吃了飯。太陽漸漸顯出要落山的顏色；吃過飯的人也不覺都顯出要回</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    家的顏色，——于是他們終于都回了家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    單四嫂子很覺得頭眩，歇息了一會，倒居然有點平穩了。但他接連著便覺得很</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    異樣︰遇到了平生沒有遇到過的事，不像會有的事，然而的確出現了。他越想越奇，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    又感到一件異樣的事——這屋子忽然太靜了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他站起身，點上燈火，屋子越顯得靜。他昏昏的走去關上門，回來坐在床沿上，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    紡車靜靜的立在地上。他定一定神，四面一看，更覺得坐立不得，屋子不但太靜，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而且也太大了，東西也太空了。太大的屋子四面包圍著他，太空的東西四面壓著他，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    叫他喘氣不得。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他現在知道他的寶兒確乎死了；不願意見這屋子，吹熄了燈，躺著。他一面哭，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一面想︰想那時候，自己紡著棉紗，寶兒坐在身邊吃茴香豆，瞪著一雙小黑眼楮想</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了一刻，便說，“媽！爹賣餛飩，我大了也賣餛飩，賣許多許多錢，——我都給你。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    那時候，真是連紡出的棉紗，也仿佛寸寸都有意思，寸寸都活著。但現在怎麼了？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    現在的事，單四嫂子卻實在沒有想到什麼。——我早經說過︰他是粗笨女人。他能</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    想出什麼呢？他單覺得這屋子太靜，太大，太空罷了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但單四嫂子雖然粗笨，卻知道還魂是不能有的事，他的寶兒也的確不能再見了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    嘆一口氣，自言自語的說，“寶兒，你該還在這里，你給我夢里見見罷。”于是合</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    上眼，想趕快睡去，會他的寶兒，苦苦的呼吸通過了靜和大和空虛，自己听得明白。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    單四嫂子終于朦朦朧朧的走入睡鄉，全屋子都很靜。這時紅鼻子老拱的小曲，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    也早經唱完；蹌蹌踉踉出了咸亨，卻又提尖了喉嚨，唱道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “我的冤家呀！——可憐你，——孤另另的……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    藍皮阿五便伸手揪住了老拱的肩頭，兩個人七歪八斜的笑著擠著走去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    單四嫂子早睡著了，老拱們也走了，咸亨也關上門了。這時的魯鎮，便完全落</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在寂靜里。只有那暗夜為想變成明天，卻仍在這寂靜里奔波；另有幾條狗，也躲在</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    暗地里嗚嗚的叫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九一九年十月北京《新潮》月刊第二卷第一號。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え中焦塞著︰中醫用語。指消化不良一類的病癥。中醫學以胃的上口至咽喉，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    包括心、肺、食管等為上焦；脾、胃為中焦；腎、大小腸和膀胱為下焦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ火克金︰中醫用語。中醫學用古代五行相生相克的說法來解釋病理，認為心、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    肺、肝、脾、腎五髒與火、金、木、土、水五行相應。火克金，是說“心火”克制</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了“肺金”，引起了呼吸系統的疾病。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お法眼︰佛家語。原指菩薩洞察一切的智慧，這里是稱許對方有鑒定能力的客</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    氣話。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    か《大悲咒》︰即佛教《觀世音菩薩大悲心陀羅尼經》中的咒文。迷信認為給</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    死者念誦或燒化這種咒文，可以使他在“陰間”消除災難，往生“樂土”。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    が據《魯迅日記》，本篇寫作時間當為一九一九年六月末或七月初。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p> 白光</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    陳士成看過縣考的榜，回到家里的時候，已經是下午了。他去得本很早，一見</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    榜，便先在這上面尋陳字。陳字也不少，似乎也都爭先恐後的跳進他眼楮里來，然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而接著的卻全不是士成這兩個字。他于是重新再在十二張榜的圓圖え里細細地搜尋，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    看的人全已散盡了，而陳士成在榜上終于沒有見，單站在試院的照壁的面前。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    涼風雖然拂拂的吹動他斑白的短發，初冬的太陽卻還是很溫和的來曬他。但他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    似乎被太陽曬得頭暈了，臉色越加變成灰白，從勞乏的紅腫的兩眼里，發出古怪的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    閃光。這時他其實早已不看到什麼牆上的榜文了，只見有許多烏黑的圓圈，在眼前</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    泛泛的游走。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    雋了秀才，上省去鄉試，一徑聯捷上去，……紳士們既然千方百計的來攀親，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    人們又都像看見神明似的敬畏，深悔先前的輕薄，發昏，……趕走了租住在自己破</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    宅門里的雜姓——那是不勞說趕，自己就搬的，——屋宇全新了，門口是旗竿和扁</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    額，……要清高可以做京官，否則不如謀外放。……他平日安排停當的前程，這時</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    候又像受潮的糖塔一般，剎時倒塌，只剩下一堆碎片了。他不自覺的旋轉了覺得渙</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    散了身軀，惘惘的走向歸家的路。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他剛到自己的房門口，七個學童便一齊放開喉嚨，吱的念起書來。他大吃一驚，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    耳朵邊似乎敲了一聲磬，只見七個頭拖了小辮子在眼前幌，幌得滿房，黑圈子也夾</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    著跳舞。他坐下了，他們送上晚課來，臉上都顯出小覷他的神色。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “回去罷。”他遲疑了片時，這才悲慘的說。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他們胡亂的包了書包，挾著，一溜煙跑走了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    陳士成還看見許多小頭夾著黑圓圈在眼前跳舞，有時雜亂，有時也擺成異樣的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    陣圖，然而漸漸的減少了，模胡了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這回又完了！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他大吃一驚，直跳起來，分明就在耳邊的話，回過頭去卻並沒有什麼人，仿佛</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    又听得嗡的敲了一聲磬，自己的嘴也說道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這回又完了！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他忽而舉起一只手來，屈指計數著想，十一，十三回，連今年是十六回，竟沒</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    有一個考官懂得文章，有眼無珠，也是可憐的事，便不由嘻嘻的失了笑。然而他憤</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    然了，驀地從書包布底下抽出謄真的制藝和試帖ぉ來，拿著往外走，剛近房門，卻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    看見滿眼都明亮，連一群雞也正在笑他，便禁不住心頭突突的狂跳，只好縮回里面</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他又就了坐，眼光格外的閃爍；他目睹著許多東西，然而很模胡，——是倒塌</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了的糖塔一般的前程躺在他面前，這前程又只是廣大起來，阻住了他的一切路。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    別家的炊煙早消歇了，碗筷也洗過了，而陳士成還不去做飯。寓在這里的雜姓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是知道老例的，凡遇到縣考的年頭，看見發榜後的這樣的眼光，不如及早關了門，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    不要多管事。最先就絕了人聲，接著是陸續的熄了燈火，獨有月亮，卻緩緩的出現</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    在寒夜的空中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    空中青碧到如一片海，略有些浮雲，仿佛有誰將粉筆洗在筆洗里似的搖曳。月</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    亮對著陳士成注下寒冷的光波來，當初也不過像是一面新磨的鐵鏡罷了，而這鏡卻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    詭秘的照透了陳士成的全身，就在他身上映出鐵的月亮的影。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他還在房外的院子里徘徊，眼里頗清靜了，四近也寂靜。但這寂靜忽又無端的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    紛擾起來，他耳邊又確鑿听到急促的低聲說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “左彎右彎……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他聳然了，傾耳听時，那聲音卻又提高的復述道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “右彎！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他記得了。這院子，是他家還未如此雕零的時候，一到夏天的夜間，夜夜和他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    的祖母在此納涼的院子。那時他不過十歲有零的孩子，躺在竹榻上，祖母便坐在榻</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    旁邊，講給他有趣的故事听。伊說是曾經听得伊的祖母說，陳氏的祖宗是巨富的，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    這屋子便是祖基，祖宗埋著無數的銀子，有福氣的子孫一定會得到的罷，然而至今</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    還沒有現。至于處所，那是藏在一個謎語的中間︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “左彎右彎，前走後走，量金量銀不論斗。”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    對于這謎語，陳士成便在平時，本也常常暗地里加以揣測的，可惜大抵剛以為</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    可以通，卻又立刻覺得不合了。有一回，他確有把握，知道這是在租給唐家的房底</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    下的了，然而總沒有前去發掘的勇氣；過了幾時，可又覺得太不相像了。至于他自</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    己房子里的幾個掘過的舊痕跡，那卻全是先前幾回下第以後的發了怔忡的舉動，後</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    來自己一看到，也還感到慚愧而且羞人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    但今天鐵的光罩住了陳士成，又軟軟的來勸他了，他或者偶一遲疑，便給他正</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    經的證明，又加上陰森的摧逼，使他不得不又向自己的房里轉過眼光去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    白光如一柄白團扇，搖搖擺擺的閃起在他房里了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “也終于在這里！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他說著，獅子似的趕快走進那房里去，但跨進里面的時候，便不見了白光的影</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    蹤，只有莽蒼蒼的一間舊房，和幾個破書桌都沒在昏暗里。他爽然的站著，慢慢的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    再定楮，然而白光卻分明的又起來了，這回更廣大，比硫黃火更白淨，比朝霧更霏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    微，而且便在靠東牆的一張書桌下。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    陳士成獅子似的奔到門後邊，伸手去摸鋤頭，撞著一條黑影。他不知怎的有些</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    怕了，張惶的點了燈，看鋤頭無非倚著。他移開桌子，用鋤頭一氣掘起四塊大方磚，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    蹲身一看，照例是黃澄澄的細沙，揎了袖爬開細沙，便露出下面的黑土來。他極小</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    心的，幽靜的，一鋤一鋤往下掘，然而深夜究竟太寂靜了，尖鐵觸土的聲音，總是</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    鈍重的不肯瞞人的發響。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    土坑深到二尺多了，並不見有甕口，陳士成正心焦，一聲脆響，頗震得手腕痛，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    鋤尖踫到什麼堅硬的東西了；他急忙拋下鋤頭，摸索著看時，一塊大方磚在下面。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他的心抖得很利害，聚精會神的挖起那方磚來，下面也滿是先前一樣的黑土，爬松</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    了許多土，下面似乎還無窮。但忽而又觸著堅硬的小東西了，圓的，大約是一個</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    銅錢；此外也還有幾片破碎的磁片。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    陳士成心里仿佛覺得空虛了，渾身流汗，急躁的只爬搔；這其間，心在空中一</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    抖動，又觸著一種古怪的小東西了，這似乎約略有些馬掌形的，但觸手很松脆。他</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    又聚精會神的挖起那東西來，謹慎的撮著，就燈光下仔細看時，那東西斑斑剝剝的</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    像是爛骨頭，上面還帶著一排零落不全的牙齒。他已經誤到這許是下巴骨了，而那</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    下巴骨也便在他手里索索的動彈起來，而且笑吟吟的顯出笑影，終于听得他開口道︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這回又完了！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他栗然的發了大冷，同時也放了手，下巴骨輕飄飄的回到坑底里不多久，他也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    就逃到院子里了。他偷看房里面，燈火如此輝煌，下巴骨如此嘲笑，異乎尋常的怕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    人，便再不敢向那邊看。他躲在遠處的檐下的陰影里，覺得較為安全了；但在這平</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    安中，忽而耳朵邊又听得竊竊的低聲說︰</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “這里沒有……到山里去……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    陳士成似乎記得白天在街上也曾听得有人說這種話，他不待再听完，已經恍然</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    大悟了。他突然仰面向天，月亮已向西高峰這方面隱去，遠想離城三十五里的西高</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    峰正在眼前，朝笏お一般黑    的挺立著，周圍便放出浩大閃爍的白光來。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    而且這白光又遠遠的就在前面了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “是的，到山里去！”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    他決定的想，慘然的奔出去了。幾回的開門之後，門里面便再不聞一些聲息。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    燈火結了大燈花照著空屋和坑洞，畢畢剝剝的炸了幾聲之後，便漸漸的縮小以至于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    無有，那是殘油已經燒盡了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    “開城門來……”</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    含著大希望的恐怖的悲聲，游絲似的在西關門前的黎明中，戰戰兢兢的叫喊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    第二天的日中，有人在離西門十五里的萬流湖里看見一個浮尸，當即傳揚開去，</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    終于傳到地保的耳朵里了，便叫鄉下人撈將上來。那是一個男尸，五十多歲，“身</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    中面白無須”，渾身也沒有什麼衣褲。或者說這就是陳士成。但鄰居懶得去看，也</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    並無尸親認領，于是經縣委員相驗之後，便由地保埋了。至于死因，那當然是沒有</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    問題的，剝取死尸的衣服本來是常有的事，夠不上疑心到謀害去︰而且仵作也證明</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    是生前的落水，因為他確鑿曾在水底里掙命，所以十個指甲里都滿嵌著河底泥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    一九二二年六月。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    □注釋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぇ本篇最初發表于一九二二年七月十日上海《東方雜志》第十九卷第十三號。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    え圓圖︰科舉時代縣考初試公布的名榜，也叫圖榜。一般不計名次。為了便于</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    計算，將每五十名考取者的姓名寫成一個圓圖；開始一名以較大的字提高寫，其次</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    沿時針方向自右至左寫去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    ぉ制藝和試帖︰科舉考試規定的公式化的詩文。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    お朝笏︰古代臣子朝見皇帝時所執狹長而稍彎的手板，按品級不同，分別用玉、</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p>    象牙或竹制成，將要奏的事書記其上，以免遺忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1cff6a1acb2ecb42/text/000002837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-f09fcd twpub-1cff6a1acb2ecb42-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">End of the Project Gutenberg EBook of Na Han, by Xun Lu</p></div>"
        },
